WITH TEMP1 AS (SELECT LEFT_OPERAND, LEFT_VALUE, OPERATOR, RIGHT_OPERAND, VALUE RIGHT_VALUE FROM (SELECT LEFT_OPERAND, VALUE LEFT_VALUE, OPERATOR, RIGHT_OPERAND FROM EXPRESSIONS E LEFT JOIN VARIABLES V ON E.LEFT_OPERAND = V.NAME) TEMP LEFT JOIN VARIABLES V ON TEMP.RIGHT_OPERAND = V.NAME) SELECT LEFT_OPERAND, OPERATOR, RIGHT_OPERAND, CASE WHEN OPERATOR = '>' AND LEFT_VALUE > RIGHT_VALUE THEN 'true' WHEN OPERATOR = '<' AND LEFT_VALUE < RIGHT_VALUE THEN 'true' WHEN OPERATOR = '=' AND LEFT_VALUE = RIGHT_VALUE THEN 'true' ELSE 'false' END VALUE FROM TEMP1

WITH VARAIBLES_X_Y AS ( SELECT A.NAME AS NAME_A, A.VALUE AS VALUE_A, B.NAME AS NAME_B, B.VALUE AS VALUE_B FROM VARIABLES AS A JOIN VARIABLES AS B ) SELECT E.LEFT_OPERAND, E.OPERATOR, E.RIGHT_OPERAND, CASE WHEN E.OPERATOR = '>' AND V.VALUE_A > V.VALUE_B THEN 'true' WHEN E.OPERATOR = '=' AND V.VALUE_A = V.VALUE_B THEN 'true' WHEN E.OPERATOR = '<' AND V.VALUE_A < V.VALUE_B THEN 'true' ELSE 'false' END AS VALUE FROM EXPRESSIONS AS E LEFT JOIN VARAIBLES_X_Y AS V ON E.LEFT_OPERAND = V.NAME_A AND E.RIGHT_OPERAND = V.NAME_B

SELECT LEFT_OPERAND, OPERATOR, RIGHT_OPERAND, CASE WHEN OPERATOR = '>' THEN IF(V.VALUE>V2.VALUE, 'true', 'false') WHEN OPERATOR = '<' THEN IF(V.VALUE<V2.VALUE, 'true', 'false') WHEN OPERATOR = '=' THEN IF(V.VALUE=V2.VALUE, 'true', 'false') END AS VALUE FROM EXPRESSIONS E JOIN VARIABLES V ON E.LEFT_OPERAND = V.NAME JOIN VARIABLES V2 ON E.RIGHT_OPERAND = V2.NAME

SELECT LEFT_OPERAND, OPERATOR, RIGHT_OPERAND,(CASE WHEN OPERATOR = '>' AND V1.VALUE > V2.VALUE THEN 'true' WHEN OPERATOR = '<' AND V1.VALUE < V2.VALUE THEN 'true' WHEN OPERATOR = '=' AND V1.VALUE = V2.VALUE THEN 'true' ELSE 'false' END ) AS VALUE FROM EXPRESSIONS E JOIN VARIABLES V1 ON E.LEFT_OPERAND = V1.NAME JOIN VARIABLES V2 ON E.RIGHT_OPERAND = V2.NAME

SELECT E.LEFT_OPERAND, E.OPERATOR, E.RIGHT_OPERAND, CASE WHEN E.OPERATOR='>' AND V.VALUE>V2.VALUE THEN 'true' WHEN E.OPERATOR='<' AND V.VALUE<V2.VALUE THEN 'true' WHEN E.OPERATOR='=' AND V.VALUE=V2.VALUE THEN 'true' ELSE 'false' END AS VALUE FROM EXPRESSIONS E JOIN VARIABLES V ON V.NAME=E.LEFT_OPERAND JOIN VARIABLES V2 ON V2.NAME=E.RIGHT_OPERAND

SELECT E.*, CASE WHEN OPERATOR='>' THEN IF(V1.VALUE > V2.VALUE,'true','false') WHEN OPERATOR='<' THEN IF(V1.VALUE < V2.VALUE,'true','false') WHEN OPERATOR='=' THEN IF(V1.VALUE = V2.VALUE,'true','false') END AS VALUE FROM EXPRESSIONS E JOIN VARIABLES V1 ON E.LEFT_OPERAND=V1.NAME JOIN VARIABLES V2 ON E.RIGHT_OPERAND=V2.NAME

SELECT V1.NAME AS LEFT_OPERAND, OPERATOR, V2.NAME AS RIGHT_OPERAND, CASE WHEN OPERATOR ='>' THEN IF(V1.VALUE > V2.VALUE, 'true', 'false') WHEN OPERATOR ='=' THEN IF(V1.VALUE = V2.VALUE, 'true', 'false') WHEN OPERATOR ='<' THEN IF(V1.VALUE < V2.VALUE, 'true', 'false') END AS VALUE FROM EXPRESSIONS E LEFT JOIN VARIABLES V1 ON E.LEFT_OPERAND = V1.NAME LEFT JOIN VARIABLES V2 ON E.RIGHT_OPERAND = V2.NAME

WITH CTE AS (SELECT LEFT_OPERAND,OPERATOR,RIGHT_OPERAND,V.VALUE AS L_VALUE FROM EXPRESSIONS E, VARIABLES V WHERE E.LEFT_OPERAND=V.NAME) ,C2 AS (SELECT LEFT_OPERAND,OPERATOR,RIGHT_OPERAND,L_VALUE,V.VALUE AS R_VALUE FROM CTE, VARIABLES V WHERE CTE.RIGHT_OPERAND=V.NAME) SELECT LEFT_OPERAND,OPERATOR,RIGHT_OPERAND, CASE WHEN L_VALUE<R_VALUE AND OPERATOR='<'THEN 'true' WHEN L_VALUE>R_VALUE AND OPERATOR='>'THEN 'true' WHEN L_VALUE=R_VALUE AND OPERATOR='='THEN 'true' ELSE 'false' END AS VALUE FROM C2

WITH TMP AS( SELECT B.NAME AS LEFT_OPERAND , B.VALUE AS LEFT_VAL , A.OPERATOR , C.NAME AS RIGHT_OPERAND , C.VALUE AS RIGHT_VAL , CASE WHEN OPERATOR='=' THEN B.VALUE = C.VALUE WHEN OPERATOR = '>' THEN B.VALUE > C.VALUE WHEN OPERATOR = '<' THEN B.VALUE < C.VALUE ELSE NULL END AS RESULT FROM EXPRESSIONS A JOIN VARIABLES B ON A.LEFT_OPERAND = B.NAME JOIN VARIABLES C ON A.RIGHT_OPERAND = C.NAME ) SELECT LEFT_OPERAND, OPERATOR, RIGHT_OPERAND , CASE WHEN RESULT = 1 THEN 'true' ELSE 'false' END AS VALUE FROM TMP

SELECT LEFT_OPERAND, OPERATOR, RIGHT_OPERAND, CASE WHEN OPERATOR= '<' THEN CASE WHEN (B.VALUE<C.VALUE) = 0 THEN 'false' ELSE 'true' END WHEN OPERATOR = '>' THEN CASE WHEN (B.VALUE >C.VALUE) = 0 THEN 'false' ELSE 'true' END ELSE CASE WHEN (B.VALUE =C.VALUE) = 0 THEN 'false' ELSE 'true' END END AS VALUE FROM EXPRESSIONS A LEFT JOIN VARIABLES B ON A.LEFT_OPERAND = B.NAME LEFT JOIN VARIABLES C ON A.RIGHT_OPERAND = C.NAME

SELECT LEFT_OPERAND, OPERATOR, RIGHT_OPERAND, CASE WHEN OPERATOR = '>' AND LEFT_VALUE > RIGHT_VALUE THEN 'true' WHEN OPERATOR = '=' AND LEFT_VALUE = RIGHT_VALUE THEN 'true' WHEN OPERATOR = '<' AND LEFT_VALUE < RIGHT_VALUE THEN 'true' ELSE 'false' END AS VALUE FROM (SELECT A.*, B.VALUE AS LEFT_VALUE, C.VALUE AS RIGHT_VALUE FROM EXPRESSIONS A LEFT JOIN VARIABLES B ON A.LEFT_OPERAND = B.NAME LEFT JOIN VARIABLES C ON A.RIGHT_OPERAND = C.NAME) SUB

SELECT LEFT_OPERAND, OPERATOR, RIGHT_OPERAND, CASE WHEN OPERATOR = '>' THEN IF(V1.VALUE > V2.VALUE, 'true', 'false') WHEN OPERATOR = '<' THEN IF(V1.VALUE < V2.VALUE, 'true', 'false') WHEN OPERATOR = '=' THEN IF(V1.VALUE = V2.VALUE, 'true', 'false') END AS VALUE FROM EXPRESSIONS E JOIN VARIABLES V1 ON E.LEFT_OPERAND = V1.NAME JOIN VARIABLES V2 ON E.RIGHT_OPERAND = V2.NAME

SELECT LEFT_OPERAND, OPERATOR, RIGHT_OPERAND, CASE WHEN OPERATOR LIKE '>' AND V1.VALUE > V2.VALUE THEN 'true' WHEN OPERATOR LIKE '<' AND V1.VALUE < V2.VALUE THEN 'true' WHEN OPERATOR LIKE '=' AND V1.VALUE = V2.VALUE THEN 'true' ELSE 'false' END AS VALUE FROM EXPRESSIONS INNER JOIN VARIABLES V1 ON V1.NAME = LEFT_OPERAND INNER JOIN VARIABLES V2 ON V2.NAME = RIGHT_OPERAND

SELECT A.LEFT_OPERAND,A.OPERATOR,A.RIGHT_OPERAND, (CASE WHEN OPERATOR ='<' AND B.VALUE < C.VALUE THEN 'true' WHEN OPERATOR ='=' AND B.VALUE = C.VALUE THEN 'true' WHEN OPERATOR ='>' AND B.VALUE > C.VALUE THEN 'true' ELSE 'false' END ) AS VALUE FROM EXPRESSIONS A LEFT JOIN VARIABLES B ON B.NAME=A.LEFT_OPERAND LEFT JOIN VARIABLES C ON C.NAME=A.RIGHT_OPERAND

SELECT LEFT_OPERAND,OPERATOR,RIGHT_OPERAND, CASE WHEN OPERATOR = '>' AND B.VALUE > C.VALUE THEN 'true' WHEN OPERATOR = '=' AND B.VALUE = C.VALUE THEN 'true' WHEN OPERATOR = '<' AND B.VALUE < C.VALUE THEN 'true' ELSE 'false' END AS VALUE FROM EXPRESSIONS A LEFT JOIN VARIABLES B ON A.LEFT_OPERAND = B.NAME LEFT JOIN VARIABLES C ON A.RIGHT_OPERAND = C.NAME

SELECT LEFT_OPERAND, OPERATOR, RIGHT_OPERAND, CASE WHEN LV > RV AND OPERATOR = '>' THEN 'true' WHEN LV < RV AND OPERATOR = '<' THEN 'true' WHEN LV = RV AND OPERATOR = '=' THEN 'true' ELSE 'false' END AS VALUE FROM (SELECT LEFT_OPERAND, V1.VALUE AS LV, OPERATOR, V2.VALUE AS RV, RIGHT_OPERAND FROM EXPRESSIONS AS E, VARIABLES AS V1, VARIABLES AS V2 WHERE E.LEFT_OPERAND = V1.NAME AND E.RIGHT_OPERAND = V2.NAME) AS T

SELECT LEFT_OPERAND, OPERATOR, RIGHT_OPERAND, CASE WHEN OPERATOR = '=' THEN IF(LV = RV, 'true', 'false') WHEN OPERATOR = '>' THEN IF(LV > RV, 'true', 'false') ELSE IF(LV < RV, 'true', 'false') END AS VALUE FROM (SELECT LV, A.OPERATOR, VALUE AS RV, A.LEFT_OPERAND, RIGHT_OPERAND FROM (SELECT LEFT_OPERAND, VALUE AS LV, OPERATOR, RIGHT_OPERAND FROM EXPRESSIONS E LEFT JOIN VARIABLES V1 ON LEFT_OPERAND = NAME) A LEFT JOIN VARIABLES V2 ON RIGHT_OPERAND = NAME) NEW

SELECT LEFT_OPERAND, OPERATOR, RIGHT_OPERAND, CASE WHEN OPERATOR='>' AND V1.VALUE>V2.VALUE THEN 'true' WHEN OPERATOR='>' AND V1.VALUE<=V2.VALUE THEN 'false' WHEN OPERATOR='<' AND V1.VALUE<V2.VALUE THEN 'true' WHEN OPERATOR='<' AND V1.VALUE>=V2.VALUE THEN 'false' WHEN OPERATOR='=' AND V1.VALUE=V2.VALUE THEN 'true' WHEN OPERATOR='=' AND V1.VALUE!=V2.VALUE THEN 'false' END AS VALUE FROM EXPRESSIONS E JOIN VARIABLES V1 ON E.LEFT_OPERAND=V1.NAME JOIN VARIABLES V2 ON E.RIGHT_OPERAND=V2.NAME

SELECT LEFT_OPERAND, OPERATOR, RIGHT_OPERAND, CASE WHEN VALUE=1 THEN 'true' ELSE 'false' END AS VALUE FROM ( SELECT A.*, CASE WHEN OPERATOR='>' THEN B.VALUE>C.VALUE WHEN OPERATOR='=' THEN B.VALUE=C.VALUE WHEN OPERATOR='<' THEN B.VALUE<C.VALUE END AS VALUE FROM EXPRESSIONS A JOIN VARIABLES B ON A.LEFT_OPERAND=B.NAME JOIN VARIABLES C ON A.RIGHT_OPERAND=C.NAME )TEMP

SELECT LEFT_OPERAND, OPERATOR, RIGHT_OPERAND, CASE WHEN OPERATOR = '=' THEN IF(V1.VALUE = V2.VALUE,'true','false') WHEN OPERATOR = '>' THEN IF(V1.VALUE > V2.VALUE,'true','false') WHEN OPERATOR = '<' THEN IF(V1.VALUE < V2.VALUE,'true','false') ELSE NULL END AS VALUE FROM EXPRESSIONS E LEFT JOIN VARIABLES V1 ON V1.NAME = LEFT_OPERAND LEFT JOIN VARIABLES V2 ON V2.NAME = RIGHT_OPERAND

SELECT E.*, CASE WHEN V1.VALUE=V2.VALUE AND OPERATOR='=' THEN 'true' WHEN V1.VALUE>V2.VALUE AND OPERATOR='>' THEN 'true' WHEN V1.VALUE<V2.VALUE AND OPERATOR='<' THEN 'true' ELSE 'false' END AS VALUE FROM EXPRESSIONS E JOIN VARIABLES V1 ON E.LEFT_OPERAND = V1.NAME JOIN VARIABLES V2 ON E.RIGHT_OPERAND = V2.NAME

SELECT A.*, CASE WHEN A.OPERATOR = '>' THEN IF(B.VALUE>C.VALUE,'true','false') WHEN A.OPERATOR = '<' THEN IF(B.VALUE<C.VALUE,'true','false') ELSE IF(B.VALUE=C.VALUE,'true','false') END AS VALUE FROM EXPRESSIONS A, VARIABLES B, VARIABLES C WHERE A.LEFT_OPERAND=B.NAME AND A.RIGHT_OPERAND=C.NAME

SELECT E.LEFT_OPERAND , E.OPERATOR , E.RIGHT_OPERAND , CASE WHEN (CASE WHEN E.OPERATOR = '>' THEN L.VALUE > R.VALUE WHEN E.OPERATOR = '<' THEN L.VALUE < R.VALUE ELSE L.VALUE = R.VALUE END) = 1 THEN 'true' ELSE 'false' END AS VALUE FROM EXPRESSIONS E LEFT OUTER JOIN VARIABLES L ON E.LEFT_OPERAND = L.NAME LEFT OUTER JOIN VARIABLES R ON E.RIGHT_OPERAND = R.NAME

SELECT E.*, CASE WHEN (OPERATOR = '<' AND L.VALUE < R.VALUE) THEN 'true' WHEN (OPERATOR = '>' AND L.VALUE > R.VALUE) THEN 'true' WHEN (OPERATOR = '=' AND L.VALUE = R.VALUE) THEN 'true' ELSE 'false' END AS VALUE FROM EXPRESSIONS E JOIN VARIABLES L ON E.LEFT_OPERAND = L.NAME JOIN VARIABLES R ON E.RIGHT_OPERAND = R.NAME

SELECT A.LEFT_OPERAND, A.OPERATOR, A.RIGHT_OPERAND, CASE WHEN B.VALUE > C.VALUE AND A.OPERATOR = '>' THEN 'true' WHEN B.VALUE = C.VALUE AND A.OPERATOR = '=' THEN 'true' WHEN B.VALUE < C.VALUE AND A.OPERATOR = '<' THEN 'true' ELSE 'false' END AS VALUE FROM EXPRESSIONS A JOIN VARIABLES B ON A.LEFT_OPERAND = B.NAME JOIN VARIABLES C ON A.RIGHT_OPERAND = C.NAME

SELECT LEFT_OPERAND, OPERATOR, RIGHT_OPERAND, ( CASE WHEN OPERATOR = '>' AND V1.VALUE > V2.VALUE THEN 'true' WHEN OPERATOR = '<' AND V1.VALUE < V2.VALUE THEN 'true' WHEN OPERATOR = '=' AND V1.VALUE = V2.VALUE THEN 'true' ELSE 'false' END ) AS VALUE FROM EXPRESSIONS AS E JOIN VARIABLES AS V1 ON V1.NAME = E.LEFT_OPERAND JOIN VARIABLES V2 ON V2.NAME = E.RIGHT_OPERAND

SELECT LEFT_OPERAND, OPERATOR, RIGHT_OPERAND, (CASE WHEN OPERATOR = '=' THEN IF(V1.VALUE = V2.VALUE, 'true', 'false') WHEN OPERATOR = '>' THEN IF(V1.VALUE > V2.VALUE, 'true', 'false') WHEN OPERATOR = '<' THEN IF(V1.VALUE < V2.VALUE, 'true', 'false') END) AS VALUE FROM EXPRESSIONS LEFT JOIN VARIABLES V1 ON V1.NAME = LEFT_OPERAND LEFT JOIN VARIABLES V2 ON V2.NAME = RIGHT_OPERAND

SELECT E.LEFT_OPERAND, E.OPERATOR, E.RIGHT_OPERAND, CASE WHEN (CASE WHEN (V1.VALUE - V2.VALUE) > 0 THEN '>' WHEN (V1.VALUE - V2.VALUE) < 0 THEN '<' ELSE '=' END) = E.OPERATOR THEN 'true' ELSE 'false' END AS VALUE FROM EXPRESSIONS E LEFT JOIN VARIABLES V1 ON E.LEFT_OPERAND = V1.NAME LEFT JOIN VARIABLES V2 ON E.RIGHT_OPERAND = V2.NAME

WITH A AS (SELECT E.LEFT_OPERAND, E.OPERATOR, E.RIGHT_OPERAND, V.VALUE AS VALUE1, V1.VALUE AS VALUE2 FROM EXPRESSIONS E LEFT JOIN VARIABLES V ON E.LEFT_OPERAND=V.NAME RIGHT JOIN VARIABLES V1 ON E.RIGHT_OPERAND=V1.NAME), B AS (SELECT LEFT_OPERAND, OPERATOR, RIGHT_OPERAND, CASE WHEN OPERATOR='>' THEN VALUE1>VALUE2 WHEN OPERATOR='<' THEN VALUE1<VALUE2 WHEN OPERATOR='=' THEN VALUE1=VALUE2 END AS VALUE FROM A) SELECT DISTINCT LEFT_OPERAND, OPERATOR, RIGHT_OPERAND, CASE WHEN VALUE=1 THEN 'true' WHEN VALUE=0 THEN 'false' END AS VALUE FROM B WHERE OPERATOR IS NOT NULL

SELECT E.LEFT_OPERAND, E.OPERATOR, E.RIGHT_OPERAND, CASE WHEN OPERATOR = '>' THEN IF(V.VALUE > V2.VALUE, 'true', 'false') WHEN OPERATOR = '<' THEN IF(V.VALUE < V2.VALUE, 'true', 'false') ELSE IF(V.VALUE = V2.VALUE,'true', 'false') END AS VALUE FROM EXPRESSIONS E JOIN VARIABLES V ON E.LEFT_OPERAND = V.NAME JOIN VARIABLES V2 ON E.RIGHT_OPERAND = V2.NAME

SELECT E.LEFT_OPERAND, E.OPERATOR, E.RIGHT_OPERAND, (CASE WHEN E.OPERATOR = '<' THEN IF(V1.VALUE < V2.VALUE, 'true', 'false') WHEN E.OPERATOR = '>' THEN IF(V1.VALUE > V2.VALUE, 'true', 'false') WHEN E.OPERATOR = '=' THEN IF(V1.VALUE = V2.VALUE, 'true', 'false') END) AS VALUE FROM EXPRESSIONS E JOIN VARIABLES V1 ON E.LEFT_OPERAND = V1.NAME JOIN VARIABLES V2 ON E.RIGHT_OPERAND = V2.NAME

SELECT LEFT_OPERAND, OPERATOR, RIGHT_OPERAND, CASE WHEN OPERATOR = RELATIONSHIP THEN 'true' ELSE 'false' END AS VALUE FROM(SELECT LEFT_OPERAND, OPERATOR, RIGHT_OPERAND, CASE WHEN V1.VALUE > V2.VALUE THEN '>' WHEN V1.VALUE = V2.VALUE THEN '=' ELSE '<' END AS RELATIONSHIP FROM EXPRESSIONS E JOIN VARIABLES V1 ON E.LEFT_OPERAND = V1.NAME JOIN VARIABLES V2 ON E.RIGHT_OPERAND = V2.NAME) TEMP

SELECT E.LEFT_OPERAND, E.OPERATOR, E.RIGHT_OPERAND, CASE WHEN E.OPERATOR = '>' THEN (CASE WHEN L.VALUE > R.VALUE THEN 'true' ELSE 'false' END) WHEN E.OPERATOR = '<' THEN (CASE WHEN L.VALUE < R.VALUE THEN 'true' ELSE 'false' END) WHEN E.OPERATOR = '=' THEN (CASE WHEN L.VALUE = R.VALUE THEN 'true' ELSE 'false' END) ELSE NULL END AS VALUE FROM EXPRESSIONS E JOIN VARIABLES L ON E.LEFT_OPERAND = L.NAME JOIN VARIABLES R ON E.RIGHT_OPERAND = R.NAME

SELECT A.LEFT_OPERAND, A.OPERATOR, A.RIGHT_OPERAND, CASE A.OPERATOR WHEN '>' THEN CASE WHEN B.VALUE > C.VALUE THEN 'true' ELSE 'false' END WHEN '=' THEN CASE WHEN B.VALUE = C.VALUE THEN 'true' ELSE 'false' END WHEN '<' THEN CASE WHEN B.VALUE < C.VALUE THEN 'true' ELSE 'false' END END AS VALUE FROM EXPRESSIONS A INNER JOIN VARIABLES B ON B.NAME = A.LEFT_OPERAND INNER JOIN VARIABLES C ON C.NAME = A.RIGHT_OPERAND

SELECT E.*, IF(E.OPERATOR = '>' AND VL.VALUE > VR.VALUE, 'true', IF(E.OPERATOR = '=' AND VL.VALUE = VR.VALUE, 'true', IF(E.OPERATOR = '<' AND VL.VALUE < VR.VALUE, 'true', 'false'))) AS VALUE FROM EXPRESSIONS AS E LEFT JOIN VARIABLES AS VL ON E.LEFT_OPERAND = VL.NAME LEFT JOIN VARIABLES AS VR ON E.RIGHT_OPERAND = VR.NAME

SELECT LEFT_OPERAND, OPERATOR, RIGHT_OPERAND, CASE WHEN OPERATOR = '>' THEN (CASE WHEN V1.VALUE > V2.VALUE THEN 'true' ELSE 'false' END) WHEN OPERATOR = '=' THEN (CASE WHEN V1.VALUE = V2.VALUE THEN 'true' ELSE 'false' END) ELSE (CASE WHEN V1.VALUE < V2.VALUE THEN 'true' ELSE 'false' END) END AS VALUE FROM EXPRESSIONS JOIN VARIABLES V1 ON LEFT_OPERAND = V1.NAME JOIN VARIABLES V2 ON RIGHT_OPERAND = V2.NAME

SELECT LEFT_OPERAND ,OPERATOR ,RIGHT_OPERAND , CASE WHEN (OPERATOR = '>' AND L.VALUE > R.VALUE) OR (OPERATOR = '<' AND L.VALUE < R.VALUE) OR (OPERATOR = '=' AND L.VALUE = R.VALUE) THEN 'true' ELSE 'false' END AS VALUE FROM EXPRESSIONS E LEFT JOIN VARIABLES L ON L.NAME = E.LEFT_OPERAND LEFT JOIN VARIABLES R ON R.NAME = E.RIGHT_OPERAND

SELECT E.LEFT_OPERAND, E.OPERATOR, E.RIGHT_OPERAND, CASE WHEN E.OPERATOR = '<' THEN CASE WHEN V1.VALUE < V2.VALUE THEN 'true' ELSE 'false' END WHEN E.OPERATOR = '=' THEN CASE WHEN V1.VALUE = V2.VALUE THEN 'true' ELSE 'false' END ELSE CASE WHEN V1.VALUE > V2.VALUE THEN 'true' ELSE 'false' END END AS VALUE FROM EXPRESSIONS E JOIN VARIABLES V1 ON E.LEFT_OPERAND = V1.NAME JOIN VARIABLES V2 ON E.RIGHT_OPERAND = V2.NAME

SELECT E.LEFT_OPERAND, E.OPERATOR, E.RIGHT_OPERAND, CASE WHEN E.OPERATOR = '>' THEN IF(A.VALUE>B.VALUE, 'true', 'false') WHEN E.OPERATOR = '<' THEN IF(A.VALUE<B.VALUE, 'true', 'false') WHEN E.OPERATOR = '=' THEN IF(A.VALUE=B.VALUE, 'true', 'false') END AS VALUE FROM EXPRESSIONS E LEFT JOIN VARIABLES A ON A.NAME=E.LEFT_OPERAND LEFT JOIN VARIABLES B ON B.NAME=E.RIGHT_OPERAND

SELECT E.LEFT_OPERAND, E.OPERATOR, E.RIGHT_OPERAND, CASE WHEN (OPERATOR = '>' AND V1.VALUE > V2.VALUE) THEN 'true' WHEN (OPERATOR = '=' AND V1.VALUE = V2.VALUE) THEN 'true' WHEN (OPERATOR = '<' AND V1.VALUE < V2.VALUE) THEN 'true' ELSE 'false' END AS VALUE FROM EXPRESSIONS E JOIN VARIABLES V1 ON E.LEFT_OPERAND = V1.NAME JOIN VARIABLES V2 ON E.RIGHT_OPERAND = V2.NAME

SELECT A.LEFT_OPERAND, A.OPERATOR, A.RIGHT_OPERAND , CASE A.OPERATOR WHEN '=' THEN IF(B.VALUE = C.VALUE, 'true', 'false') WHEN '>' THEN IF(B.VALUE > C.VALUE, 'true', 'false') WHEN '<' THEN IF(B.VALUE < C.VALUE, 'true', 'false') ELSE 'false' END AS VALUE FROM EXPRESSIONS A LEFT JOIN VARIABLES B ON A.LEFT_OPERAND = B.NAME LEFT JOIN VARIABLES C ON A.RIGHT_OPERAND = C.NAME

SELECT LEFT_OPERAND, OPERATOR, RIGHT_OPERAND, (CASE WHEN OPERATOR = '<' AND V1.VALUE < V2.VALUE THEN 'true' WHEN OPERATOR = '>' AND V1.VALUE > V2.VALUE THEN 'true' WHEN OPERATOR = '=' AND V1.VALUE = V2.VALUE THEN 'true' ELSE 'false' END) VALUE FROM EXPRESSIONS E JOIN VARIABLES V1 ON E.LEFT_OPERAND = V1.NAME JOIN VARIABLES V2 ON E.RIGHT_OPERAND = V2.NAME

WITH CTE AS (SELECT LEFT_OPERAND ,OPERATOR,RIGHT_OPERAND , V.VALUE AS LEFT_OPERAND_V, E.OPERATOR AS OPERATOR_V , V1.VALUE AS RIGHT_OPERAND_V FROM EXPRESSIONS E LEFT JOIN VARIABLES V ON E.LEFT_OPERAND = V.NAME LEFT JOIN VARIABLES V1 ON E.RIGHT_OPERAND = V1.NAME ) SELECT LEFT_OPERAND ,OPERATOR,RIGHT_OPERAND , CASE WHEN OPERATOR_V = '>' THEN ( CASE WHEN LEFT_OPERAND_V>RIGHT_OPERAND_V THEN 'true' ELSE 'false' END) WHEN OPERATOR_V = '<' THEN ( CASE WHEN LEFT_OPERAND_V<RIGHT_OPERAND_V THEN 'true' ELSE 'false' END) WHEN OPERATOR_V = '=' THEN ( CASE WHEN LEFT_OPERAND_V=RIGHT_OPERAND_V THEN 'true' ELSE 'false' END) ELSE NULL END AS VALUE FROM CTE

SELECT E.LEFT_OPERAND, E.OPERATOR, E.RIGHT_OPERAND, CASE WHEN E.OPERATOR = '>' THEN IF(V1.VALUE > V2.VALUE, 'true', 'false') WHEN E.OPERATOR = '<' THEN IF(V1.VALUE < V2.VALUE, 'true', 'false') WHEN E.OPERATOR = '=' THEN IF(V1.VALUE = V2.VALUE, 'true', 'false') END AS VALUE FROM EXPRESSIONS E JOIN VARIABLES AS V1 ON E.LEFT_OPERAND = V1.NAME JOIN VARIABLES AS V2 ON E.RIGHT_OPERAND = V2.NAME

SELECT E.LEFT_OPERAND,E.OPERATOR,E.RIGHT_OPERAND, CASE WHEN OPERATOR='>' AND V1.VALUE>V2.VALUE THEN 'true' WHEN OPERATOR='<' AND V1.VALUE<V2.VALUE THEN 'true' WHEN OPERATOR='=' AND V1.VALUE=V2.VALUE THEN 'true' ELSE 'false' END AS VALUE FROM EXPRESSIONS E JOIN VARIABLES V1 ON E.LEFT_OPERAND=V1.NAME JOIN VARIABLES V2 ON E.RIGHT_OPERAND=V2.NAME

SELECT E.LEFT_OPERAND, E.OPERATOR, E.RIGHT_OPERAND, CASE WHEN E.OPERATOR='=' AND V1.VALUE=V2.VALUE THEN 'true' WHEN E.OPERATOR='>' AND V1.VALUE>V2.VALUE THEN 'true' WHEN E.OPERATOR='<' AND V1.VALUE<V2.VALUE THEN 'true' ELSE 'false' END AS VALUE FROM EXPRESSIONS E LEFT JOIN VARIABLES V1 ON E.LEFT_OPERAND = V1.NAME LEFT JOIN VARIABLES V2 ON E.RIGHT_OPERAND = V2.NAME

SELECT E.*, CASE E.OPERATOR WHEN '=' THEN IF(V1.VALUE = V2.VALUE, 'true', 'false') WHEN '>' THEN IF(V1.VALUE > V2.VALUE, 'true', 'false') WHEN '<' THEN IF(V1.VALUE < V2.VALUE, 'true', 'false') END AS VALUE FROM EXPRESSIONS AS E, VARIABLES AS V1, VARIABLES AS V2 WHERE E.LEFT_OPERAND = V1.NAME AND E.RIGHT_OPERAND = V2.NAME

SELECT E.LEFT_OPERAND, E.OPERATOR, E.RIGHT_OPERAND, CASE WHEN E.OPERATOR = '>' AND V.VALUE > V1.VALUE THEN 'true' WHEN E.OPERATOR = '<' AND V.VALUE < V1.VALUE THEN 'true' WHEN E.OPERATOR = '=' AND V.VALUE = V1.VALUE THEN 'true' ELSE 'false' END AS VALUE FROM EXPRESSIONS E INNER JOIN VARIABLES V ON E.LEFT_OPERAND = V.NAME INNER JOIN VARIABLES V1 ON E.RIGHT_OPERAND = V1.NAME

SELECT LEFT_OPERAND, OPERATOR, RIGHT_OPERAND, CASE WHEN LV < RV AND OPERATOR = '<' THEN 'true' WHEN LV = RV AND OPERATOR = '=' THEN 'true' WHEN LV > RV AND OPERATOR = '>' THEN 'true' ELSE 'false' END AS VALUE FROM (SELECT V1.VALUE AS LV, LEFT_OPERAND, OPERATOR, RIGHT_OPERAND, V2.VALUE AS RV FROM VARIABLES V1 JOIN EXPRESSIONS E ON V1.NAME = E.LEFT_OPERAND JOIN VARIABLES V2 ON E.RIGHT_OPERAND = V2.NAME) T

SELECT LEFT_OPERAND, OPERATOR, RIGHT_OPERAND, CASE WHEN V.VALUE < V2.VALUE AND E.OPERATOR = '<' THEN 'true' WHEN V.VALUE > V2.VALUE AND E.OPERATOR = '>' THEN 'true' WHEN V.VALUE = V2.VALUE AND E.OPERATOR = '=' THEN 'true' ELSE 'false' END AS VALUE FROM VARIABLES V JOIN EXPRESSIONS E ON V.NAME = E.LEFT_OPERAND JOIN VARIABLES V2 ON V2.NAME = E.RIGHT_OPERAND

SELECT E.LEFT_OPERAND, E.OPERATOR, E.RIGHT_OPERAND, CASE WHEN E.OPERATOR = '>' THEN IF(V1.VALUE>V2.VALUE, 'true', 'false') WHEN E.OPERATOR = '=' THEN IF(V1.VALUE=V2.VALUE, 'true', 'false') WHEN E.OPERATOR = '<' THEN IF(V1.VALUE<V2.VALUE, 'true', 'false') END AS VALUE FROM EXPRESSIONS E JOIN VARIABLES V1 ON E.LEFT_OPERAND = V1.NAME JOIN VARIABLES V2 ON E.RIGHT_OPERAND = V2.NAME

SELECT LEFT_OPERAND, OPERATOR, RIGHT_OPERAND, CASE WHEN OPERATOR='>' THEN IF(V1.VALUE>V2.VALUE,'true','false') WHEN OPERATOR='=' THEN IF(V1.VALUE=V2.VALUE,'true','false') WHEN OPERATOR='<' THEN IF(V1.VALUE<V2.VALUE,'true','false') END AS VALUE FROM EXPRESSIONS JOIN VARIABLES V1 JOIN VARIABLES V2 ON V1.NAME=LEFT_OPERAND AND V2.NAME=RIGHT_OPERAND

SELECT E.LEFT_OPERAND, E.OPERATOR, E.RIGHT_OPERAND, (CASE WHEN E.OPERATOR = '>' AND V1.VALUE > V2.VALUE THEN 'true' WHEN E.OPERATOR = '=' AND V1.VALUE = V2.VALUE THEN 'true' WHEN E.OPERATOR = '<' AND V1.VALUE < V2.VALUE THEN 'true' ELSE 'false' END) VALUE FROM EXPRESSIONS E LEFT JOIN VARIABLES V1 ON V1.NAME = E.LEFT_OPERAND LEFT JOIN VARIABLES V2 ON V2.NAME = E.RIGHT_OPERAND

WITH AA AS (SELECT L, LEFT_OPERAND, OPERATOR,RIGHT_OPERAND, R FROM (SELECT VALUE AS L,LEFT_OPERAND,RIGHT_OPERAND,OPERATOR FROM VARIABLES JOIN EXPRESSIONS ON NAME=LEFT_OPERAND) A JOIN (SELECT LEFT_OPERAND,OPERATOR,VALUE AS R,RIGHT_OPERAND FROM VARIABLES JOIN EXPRESSIONS ON NAME=RIGHT_OPERAND) B USING(LEFT_OPERAND,OPERATOR,RIGHT_OPERAND)) SELECT LEFT_OPERAND, OPERATOR,RIGHT_OPERAND, CASE WHEN VALUE =1 THEN 'true' ELSE 'false' END AS VALUE FROM (SELECT LEFT_OPERAND, OPERATOR,RIGHT_OPERAND, CASE WHEN OPERATOR='>' THEN L>R WHEN OPERATOR ='<' THEN L<R ELSE L=R END AS VALUE FROM AA) BB

SELECT LEFT_OPERAND,OPERATOR,RIGHT_OPERAND, CASE WHEN VALUE1 > VALUE2 AND OPERATOR = '>' THEN 'true' WHEN VALUE1 > VALUE2 AND OPERATOR = '<' THEN 'false' WHEN VALUE1 > VALUE2 AND OPERATOR = '=' THEN 'false' WHEN VALUE1 < VALUE2 AND OPERATOR = '>' THEN 'false' WHEN VALUE1 < VALUE2 AND OPERATOR = '<' THEN 'true' WHEN VALUE1 < VALUE2 AND OPERATOR = '=' THEN 'false' WHEN VALUE1 = VALUE2 AND OPERATOR = '=' THEN 'true' WHEN VALUE1 = VALUE2 AND OPERATOR = '>' THEN 'false' WHEN VALUE1 = VALUE2 AND OPERATOR = '<' THEN 'false' END VALUE FROM (SELECT LEFT_OPERAND,OPERATOR,RIGHT_OPERAND,V1.VALUE VALUE1,V2.VALUE VALUE2 FROM VARIABLES V1 RIGHT JOIN EXPRESSIONS E1 ON V1.NAME = E1.LEFT_OPERAND LEFT JOIN VARIABLES V2 ON E1.RIGHT_OPERAND = V2.NAME) A

SELECT LEFT_OPERAND, OPERATOR, RIGHT_OPERAND, CASE WHEN OPERATOR = '>' AND VALUE1 > VALUE2 THEN 'true' WHEN OPERATOR = '=' AND VALUE1 = VALUE2 THEN 'true' WHEN OPERATOR = '<' AND VALUE1 < VALUE2 THEN 'true' ELSE 'false' END AS VALUE FROM (SELECT LEFT_OPERAND, OPERATOR, RIGHT_OPERAND, V1.VALUE AS VALUE1, V2.VALUE AS VALUE2 FROM EXPRESSIONS AS E JOIN VARIABLES AS V1 ON V1.NAME = E.LEFT_OPERAND JOIN VARIABLES AS V2 ON V2.NAME = E.RIGHT_OPERAND) AS A

SELECT B.LEFT_OPERAND, B.OPERATOR, B.RIGHT_OPERAND, CASE WHEN B.OPERATOR='<' AND A.VALUE<C.VALUE THEN 'true' WHEN B.OPERATOR='>' AND A.VALUE>C.VALUE THEN 'true' WHEN B.OPERATOR='=' AND A.VALUE=C.VALUE THEN 'true' ELSE 'false' END AS VALUE FROM VARIABLES A JOIN EXPRESSIONS B ON A.NAME=B.LEFT_OPERAND JOIN VARIABLES C ON C.NAME=B.RIGHT_OPERAND

SELECT E.LEFT_OPERAND, E.OPERATOR, E.RIGHT_OPERAND, CASE WHEN E.OPERATOR = '=' AND V.VALUE = V2.VALUE THEN 'true' WHEN E.OPERATOR = '>' AND V.VALUE > V2.VALUE THEN 'true' WHEN E.OPERATOR = '<' AND V.VALUE < V2.VALUE THEN 'true' ELSE 'false' END AS VALUE FROM EXPRESSIONS E JOIN VARIABLES V ON E.LEFT_OPERAND = V.NAME JOIN VARIABLES V2 ON E.RIGHT_OPERAND = V2.NAME

SELECT LEFT_OPERAND, OPERATOR, RIGHT_OPERAND, CASE OPERATOR WHEN '>' THEN IF(L.VALUE > R.VALUE, 'true', 'false') WHEN '=' THEN IF(L.VALUE = R.VALUE, 'true', 'false') ELSE IF(L.VALUE < R.VALUE, 'true', 'false') END AS VALUE FROM EXPRESSIONS E JOIN VARIABLES L ON E.LEFT_OPERAND = L.NAME JOIN VARIABLES R ON E.RIGHT_OPERAND = R.NAME

SELECT A.*, CASE WHEN B.VALUE>C.VALUE AND OPERATOR='>' THEN 'true' WHEN B.VALUE=C.VALUE AND OPERATOR='=' THEN 'true' WHEN B.VALUE<C.VALUE AND OPERATOR='<' THEN 'true' ELSE 'false' END AS VALUE FROM EXPRESSIONS A JOIN VARIABLES B ON A.LEFT_OPERAND=B.NAME JOIN VARIABLES C ON A.RIGHT_OPERAND=C.NAME

SELECT LEFT_OPERAND, OPERATOR, RIGHT_OPERAND, ( CASE WHEN OPERATOR = '>' AND A.VALUE > B.VALUE THEN 'true' WHEN OPERATOR = '<' AND A.VALUE < B.VALUE THEN 'true' WHEN OPERATOR = '=' AND A.VALUE = B.VALUE THEN 'true' ELSE 'false' END) AS VALUE FROM EXPRESSIONS E LEFT JOIN VARIABLES A ON E.LEFT_OPERAND = A.NAME LEFT JOIN VARIABLES B ON E.RIGHT_OPERAND = B.NAME

WITH TMP AS (SELECT LEFT_OPERAND, OPERATOR, RIGHT_OPERAND, V1.VALUE L, V2.VALUE R FROM EXPRESSIONS E INNER JOIN VARIABLES V1 ON E.LEFT_OPERAND = V1.NAME INNER JOIN VARIABLES V2 ON E.RIGHT_OPERAND = V2.NAME) SELECT LEFT_OPERAND, OPERATOR, RIGHT_OPERAND, CASE WHEN OPERATOR = '>' THEN IF(L > R, 'true', 'false') WHEN OPERATOR = '=' THEN IF(L = R, 'true', 'false') ELSE IF(L < R, 'true', 'false') END VALUE FROM TMP

WITH CTE AS (SELECT LEFT_OPERAND, B.VALUE AS L_VALUE, OPERATOR, RIGHT_OPERAND FROM EXPRESSIONS A LEFT JOIN VARIABLES B ON A.LEFT_OPERAND = B.NAME), CTE2 AS (SELECT A.*, B.VALUE AS R_VALUE FROM CTE A LEFT JOIN VARIABLES B ON A.RIGHT_OPERAND = B.NAME) SELECT LEFT_OPERAND, OPERATOR, RIGHT_OPERAND, CASE WHEN OPERATOR = '<' AND L_VALUE < R_VALUE THEN 'true' WHEN OPERATOR = '=' AND L_VALUE = R_VALUE THEN 'true' WHEN OPERATOR = '>' AND L_VALUE > R_VALUE THEN 'true' ELSE 'false' END VALUE FROM CTE2

SELECT E.LEFT_OPERAND, E.OPERATOR, E.RIGHT_OPERAND, (CASE WHEN OPERATOR = '>' AND V1.VALUE > V2.VALUE THEN 'true' WHEN OPERATOR = '<' AND V1.VALUE < V2.VALUE THEN 'true' WHEN OPERATOR = '=' AND V1.VALUE = V2.VALUE THEN 'true' ELSE 'false' END ) AS VALUE FROM EXPRESSIONS E JOIN VARIABLES V1 ON E.LEFT_OPERAND = V1.NAME JOIN VARIABLES V2 ON E.RIGHT_OPERAND = V2.NAME

SELECT E.LEFT_OPERAND, E.OPERATOR, E.RIGHT_OPERAND, CASE WHEN E.OPERATOR = '>' AND V1.VALUE > V2.VALUE THEN 'true' WHEN E.OPERATOR = '<' AND V1.VALUE < V2.VALUE THEN 'true' WHEN E.OPERATOR = '=' AND V1.VALUE = V2.VALUE THEN 'true' ELSE 'false' END AS VALUE FROM EXPRESSIONS E LEFT JOIN VARIABLES V1 ON E.LEFT_OPERAND = V1.NAME LEFT JOIN VARIABLES V2 ON E.RIGHT_OPERAND = V2.NAME

SELECT LEFT_OPERAND, OPERATOR, RIGHT_OPERAND, CASE OPERATOR WHEN '>' THEN IF(LFT.VALUE > RGT.VALUE, 'true', 'false') WHEN '<' THEN IF(LFT.VALUE < RGT.VALUE, 'true', 'false') ELSE IF(LFT.VALUE = RGT.VALUE, 'true', 'false') END AS VALUE FROM EXPRESSIONS E JOIN VARIABLES LFT ON E.LEFT_OPERAND = LFT.NAME JOIN VARIABLES RGT ON E.RIGHT_OPERAND = RGT.NAME

SELECT LEFT_OPERAND, OPERATOR, RIGHT_OPERAND, CASE WHEN OPERATOR = '>' AND LEFT_VALUE > RIGHT_VALUE THEN 'true' WHEN OPERATOR = '<' AND LEFT_VALUE < RIGHT_VALUE THEN 'true' WHEN OPERATOR = '=' AND LEFT_VALUE = RIGHT_VALUE THEN 'true' ELSE 'false' END AS VALUE FROM (SELECT A.*, B.VALUE AS LEFT_VALUE, C.VALUE AS RIGHT_VALUE FROM EXPRESSIONS A LEFT JOIN VARIABLES B ON A.LEFT_OPERAND = B.NAME LEFT JOIN VARIABLES C ON A.RIGHT_OPERAND = C.NAME) D

SELECT LEFT_OPERAND, OPERATOR, RIGHT_OPERAND, (CASE WHEN T1.VALUE > T2.VALUE AND OPERATOR = '>' THEN 'true' WHEN T1.VALUE < T2.VALUE AND OPERATOR = '<' THEN 'true' WHEN T1.VALUE = T2.VALUE AND OPERATOR = '=' THEN 'true' ELSE 'false' END) AS VALUE FROM EXPRESSIONS E JOIN VARIABLES T1 ON E.LEFT_OPERAND = T1.NAME JOIN VARIABLES T2 ON E.RIGHT_OPERAND = T2.NAME

SELECT E.*, (CASE WHEN OPERATOR = '>' AND V1.VALUE > V2.VALUE THEN 'true' WHEN OPERATOR = '<' AND V1.VALUE < V2.VALUE THEN 'true' WHEN OPERATOR = '=' AND V1.VALUE = V2.VALUE THEN 'true' ELSE 'false' END) AS VALUE FROM EXPRESSIONS E LEFT JOIN VARIABLES V1 ON V1.NAME = E.LEFT_OPERAND LEFT JOIN VARIABLES V2 ON V2.NAME = E.RIGHT_OPERAND

SELECT E.*, ( CASE WHEN E.OPERATOR = '=' AND V1.VALUE = V2.VALUE THEN 'true' WHEN E.OPERATOR = '>' AND V1.VALUE > V2.VALUE THEN 'true' WHEN E.OPERATOR = '<' AND V1.VALUE < V2.VALUE THEN 'true' ELSE 'false' END ) VALUE FROM EXPRESSIONS E JOIN VARIABLES V1 ON V1.NAME = E.LEFT_OPERAND JOIN VARIABLES V2 ON V2.NAME = E.RIGHT_OPERAND

SELECT E.LEFT_OPERAND, E.OPERATOR, E.RIGHT_OPERAND, IF((CASE WHEN OPERATOR = '>' THEN V1.VALUE > V2.VALUE WHEN OPERATOR = '<' THEN V1.VALUE < V2.VALUE ELSE V1.VALUE = V2.VALUE END) = 1, 'true', 'false') AS VALUE FROM EXPRESSIONS E LEFT JOIN VARIABLES V1 ON E.LEFT_OPERAND = V1.NAME LEFT JOIN VARIABLES V2 ON E.RIGHT_OPERAND = V2.NAME

SELECT E.LEFT_OPERAND, E.OPERATOR, E.RIGHT_OPERAND, (CASE WHEN OPERATOR = '>' AND V1.VALUE > V2.VALUE THEN 'true' WHEN OPERATOR = '>' AND V1.VALUE < V2.VALUE THEN 'false' WHEN OPERATOR = '<' AND V1.VALUE > V2.VALUE THEN 'false' WHEN OPERATOR = '<' AND V1.VALUE < V2.VALUE THEN 'true' WHEN OPERATOR = '=' AND V1.VALUE = V2.VALUE THEN 'true' ELSE 'false' END) AS VALUE FROM EXPRESSIONS E, VARIABLES V1, VARIABLES V2 WHERE E.LEFT_OPERAND = V1.NAME AND E.RIGHT_OPERAND = V2.NAME

SELECT E.* ,CASE WHEN E.OPERATOR = '>' THEN IF(L.VALUE > R.VALUE,'true', 'false') WHEN E.OPERATOR = '=' THEN IF(L.VALUE = R.VALUE,'true', 'false') WHEN E.OPERATOR = '<' THEN IF(L.VALUE < R.VALUE,'true', 'false') END AS VALUE FROM EXPRESSIONS E JOIN VARIABLES L ON E.LEFT_OPERAND = L.NAME JOIN VARIABLES R ON E.RIGHT_OPERAND = R.NAME

SELECT LEFT_OPERAND,OPERATOR,RIGHT_OPERAND, CASE WHEN OPERATOR='>' THEN IF(LEFT_VALUE>VALUE,'true','false') WHEN OPERATOR='=' THEN IF(LEFT_VALUE=VALUE,'true','false') WHEN OPERATOR='<' THEN IF(LEFT_VALUE<VALUE,'true','false') END AS VALUE FROM( (SELECT LEFT_OPERAND,OPERATOR,RIGHT_OPERAND,VALUE AS LEFT_VALUE FROM EXPRESSIONS JOIN VARIABLES ON EXPRESSIONS.LEFT_OPERAND = VARIABLES.NAME) AS TMP1 JOIN VARIABLES ON TMP1.RIGHT_OPERAND = VARIABLES.NAME)

SELECT LEFT_OPERAND, OPERATOR, RIGHT_OPERAND, CASE WHEN OPERATOR = '<' AND V1.VALUE < V2.VALUE THEN 'true' WHEN OPERATOR = '>' AND V1.VALUE > V2.VALUE THEN 'true' WHEN OPERATOR = '=' AND V1.VALUE = V2.VALUE THEN 'true' ELSE 'false' END AS VALUE FROM VARIABLES V1 JOIN EXPRESSIONS E ON V1.NAME = E.LEFT_OPERAND JOIN VARIABLES V2 ON E.RIGHT_OPERAND = V2.NAME

SELECT LEFT_OPERAND, OPERATOR, RIGHT_OPERAND, CASE WHEN OPERATOR = '>' AND V1.VALUE > V2.VALUE THEN 'true' WHEN OPERATOR = '=' AND V1.VALUE = V2.VALUE THEN 'true' WHEN OPERATOR = '<' AND V1.VALUE < V2.VALUE THEN 'true' ELSE 'false' END AS VALUE FROM EXPRESSIONS JOIN VARIABLES V1 ON LEFT_OPERAND = V1.NAME JOIN VARIABLES V2 ON RIGHT_OPERAND = V2.NAME

WITH CTE AS ( SELECT V.VALUE AS LEFTV, V2.VALUE AS RIGHTV, LEFT_OPERAND, OPERATOR, RIGHT_OPERAND FROM EXPRESSIONS E JOIN VARIABLES V ON E.LEFT_OPERAND = V.NAME JOIN VARIABLES V2 ON E.RIGHT_OPERAND = V2.NAME ) SELECT LEFT_OPERAND, OPERATOR, RIGHT_OPERAND, (CASE WHEN OPERATOR = '>' AND LEFTV > RIGHTV THEN 'true' WHEN OPERATOR = '<' AND LEFTV < RIGHTV THEN 'true' WHEN OPERATOR = '=' AND LEFTV = RIGHTV THEN 'true' ELSE 'false' END) AS VALUE FROM CTE

SELECT B.LEFT_OPERAND,B.OPERATOR,B.RIGHT_OPERAND, CASE WHEN B.OPERATOR= '>' THEN IF(A.VALUE>C.VALUE,'true','false') WHEN B.OPERATOR= '<' THEN IF(A.VALUE<C.VALUE,'true','false') WHEN B.OPERATOR= '=' THEN IF(A.VALUE=C.VALUE,'true','false') END AS VALUE FROM VARIABLES A JOIN EXPRESSIONS B ON A.NAME = B.LEFT_OPERAND JOIN VARIABLES C ON C.NAME=B.RIGHT_OPERAND

SELECT E.LEFT_OPERAND, E.OPERATOR, E.RIGHT_OPERAND, CASE WHEN CASE WHEN OPERATOR='>' THEN V1.VALUE>V2.VALUE WHEN OPERATOR='<' THEN V1.VALUE<V2.VALUE WHEN OPERATOR='=' THEN V1.VALUE=V2.VALUE END=1 THEN 'true' ELSE 'false' END AS VALUE FROM EXPRESSIONS E JOIN VARIABLES V1 ON E.LEFT_OPERAND=V1.NAME JOIN VARIABLES V2 ON E.RIGHT_OPERAND=V2.NAME

SELECT LEFT_OPERAND, OPERATOR, RIGHT_OPERAND, CASE WHEN OPERATOR='>' AND V1.VALUE>V2.VALUE THEN 'true' WHEN OPERATOR='=' AND V1.VALUE=V2.VALUE THEN 'true' WHEN OPERATOR='<' AND V1.VALUE<V2.VALUE THEN 'true' ELSE 'false' END AS VALUE FROM EXPRESSIONS E JOIN VARIABLES V1 ON V1.NAME=E.LEFT_OPERAND JOIN VARIABLES V2 ON V2.NAME=E.RIGHT_OPERAND

SELECT LEFT_OPERAND, OPERATOR, RIGHT_OPERAND, (CASE WHEN OPERATOR = '=' AND V1.VALUE = V2.VALUE THEN 'true' WHEN OPERATOR = '>' AND V1.VALUE > V2.VALUE THEN 'true' WHEN OPERATOR = '<' AND V1.VALUE < V2.VALUE THEN 'true' ELSE 'false' END ) VALUE FROM EXPRESSIONS E JOIN VARIABLES V1 ON E.LEFT_OPERAND = V1.NAME JOIN VARIABLES V2 ON E.RIGHT_OPERAND = V2.NAME

SELECT LEFT_OPERAND, OPERATOR, RIGHT_OPERAND, CASE WHEN OPERATOR='>' THEN IF(V1.VALUE > V2.VALUE,'true','false') WHEN OPERATOR='<' THEN IF(V1.VALUE < V2.VALUE,'true','false') WHEN OPERATOR='=' THEN IF(V1.VALUE = V2.VALUE,'true','false') END AS VALUE FROM EXPRESSIONS JOIN VARIABLES V1 ON V1.NAME = LEFT_OPERAND JOIN VARIABLES V2 ON V2.NAME = RIGHT_OPERAND

SELECT E.*, ( CASE WHEN OPERATOR = '>' AND L.VALUE > R.VALUE THEN 'true' WHEN OPERATOR = '<' AND L.VALUE < R.VALUE THEN 'true' WHEN OPERATOR = '=' AND L.VALUE = R.VALUE THEN 'true' ELSE 'false' END ) AS VALUE FROM EXPRESSIONS E JOIN VARIABLES L ON E.LEFT_OPERAND = L.NAME JOIN VARIABLES R ON E.RIGHT_OPERAND = R.NAME

SELECT LEFT_OPERAND, OPERATOR, RIGHT_OPERAND, CASE WHEN OPERATOR = '=' THEN IF(RIGHT_VALUE = LEFT_VALUE, 'true', 'false') WHEN OPERATOR = '>' THEN IF(RIGHT_VALUE > LEFT_VALUE, 'true', 'false') WHEN OPERATOR = '<' THEN IF(RIGHT_VALUE < LEFT_VALUE, 'true', 'false') END AS VALUE FROM ( SELECT LEFT_OPERAND, LEFT_VALUE, OPERATOR, RIGHT_OPERAND , VALUE AS RIGHT_VALUE FROM ( SELECT T1.LEFT_OPERAND, VALUE AS LEFT_VALUE, OPERATOR, RIGHT_OPERAND FROM ( SELECT * FROM EXPRESSIONS )T1 LEFT JOIN ( SELECT * FROM VARIABLES )T2 ON T1.LEFT_OPERAND = T2.NAME )TT1 LEFT JOIN ( SELECT * FROM VARIABLES )TT2 ON TT1.RIGHT_OPERAND = TT2.NAME )T

SELECT LEFT_OPERAND, OPERATOR, RIGHT_OPERAND, (CASE WHEN OPERATOR = R THEN 'true' ELSE 'false' END) AS VALUE FROM (SELECT LEFT_OPERAND, OPERATOR, RIGHT_OPERAND, (CASE WHEN V1.VALUE > V2.VALUE THEN '>' WHEN V1.VALUE = V2.VALUE THEN '=' ELSE '<' END) AS R FROM EXPRESSIONS E JOIN VARIABLES V1 ON V1.NAME = LEFT_OPERAND JOIN VARIABLES V2 ON V2.NAME = RIGHT_OPERAND) TEMP

SELECT LEFT_OPERAND, OPERATOR, RIGHT_OPERAND, CASE WHEN OPERATOR = RESULT THEN 'true' ELSE 'false' END AS VALUE FROM (SELECT E.LEFT_OPERAND, E.OPERATOR ,E.RIGHT_OPERAND, CASE WHEN V.VALUE - V2.VALUE > 0 THEN '>' WHEN V.VALUE - V2.VALUE = 0 THEN '=' WHEN V.VALUE - V2.VALUE < 0 THEN '<' END AS RESULT FROM EXPRESSIONS AS E LEFT JOIN VARIABLES AS V ON E.LEFT_OPERAND = V.NAME LEFT JOIN VARIABLES AS V2 ON E.RIGHT_OPERAND = V2.NAME) AS T1

SELECT LEFT_OPERAND, OPERATOR, RIGHT_OPERAND, CASE WHEN OPERATOR = '>' AND V1.VALUE > V2.VALUE THEN 'true' WHEN OPERATOR = '<' AND V1.VALUE < V2.VALUE THEN 'true' WHEN OPERATOR = '=' AND V1.VALUE = V2.VALUE THEN 'true' ELSE 'false' END AS VALUE FROM EXPRESSIONS E JOIN VARIABLES V1 ON LEFT_OPERAND = V1.NAME JOIN VARIABLES V2 ON RIGHT_OPERAND = V2.NAME

SELECT E.*, CASE WHEN OPERATOR='>' AND V1.VALUE>V2.VALUE THEN 'true' WHEN OPERATOR='<' AND V1.VALUE<V2.VALUE THEN 'true' WHEN OPERATOR='=' AND V1.VALUE=V2.VALUE THEN 'true' ELSE 'false' END AS VALUE FROM EXPRESSIONS E JOIN VARIABLES V1 ON V1.NAME=E.LEFT_OPERAND JOIN VARIABLES V2 ON V2.NAME=E.RIGHT_OPERAND

SELECT LEFT_OPERAND, OPERATOR, RIGHT_OPERAND, CASE WHEN OPERATOR='>' THEN (CASE WHEN V1.VALUE>V2.VALUE=1 THEN 'true' ELSE 'false' END) WHEN OPERATOR='=' THEN (CASE WHEN V1.VALUE=V2.VALUE=1 THEN 'true' ELSE 'false' END) WHEN OPERATOR='<' THEN (CASE WHEN V1.VALUE<V2.VALUE=1 THEN 'true' ELSE 'false' END) END AS VALUE FROM EXPRESSIONS JOIN VARIABLES V1 JOIN VARIABLES V2 ON V1.NAME=LEFT_OPERAND AND V2.NAME=RIGHT_OPERAND

SELECT E.LEFT_OPERAND, E.OPERATOR, E.RIGHT_OPERAND, (CASE WHEN E.OPERATOR = '>' THEN IF(V1.VALUE > V2.VALUE, 'true', 'false') WHEN E.OPERATOR = '=' THEN IF(V1.VALUE = V2.VALUE, 'true', 'false') WHEN E.OPERATOR = '<' THEN IF(V1.VALUE > V2.VALUE, 'true', 'false') END) AS VALUE FROM EXPRESSIONS E JOIN VARIABLES V1 ON V1.NAME = E.LEFT_OPERAND JOIN VARIABLES V2 ON V2.NAME = E.RIGHT_OPERAND

SELECT LEFT_OPERAND, OPERATOR, RIGHT_OPERAND, CASE E.OPERATOR WHEN '>' THEN CASE WHEN VL.VALUE > VR.VALUE THEN 'true' ELSE 'false' END WHEN '<' THEN CASE WHEN VL.VALUE < VR.VALUE THEN 'true' ELSE 'false' END WHEN '=' THEN CASE WHEN VL.VALUE = VR.VALUE THEN 'true' ELSE 'false' END END AS VALUE FROM EXPRESSIONS E JOIN VARIABLES VL ON E.LEFT_OPERAND = VL.NAME JOIN VARIABLES VR ON E.RIGHT_OPERAND = VR.NAME

SELECT E.LEFT_OPERAND, E.OPERATOR, E.RIGHT_OPERAND ,IF((CASE WHEN OPERATOR = '>' THEN (L.VALUE > R.VALUE) WHEN OPERATOR = '<' THEN (L.VALUE < R.VALUE) WHEN OPERATOR = '=' THEN (L.VALUE = R.VALUE) END )=1,'true','false') VALUE FROM EXPRESSIONS E LEFT JOIN VARIABLES L ON E.LEFT_OPERAND = L.NAME LEFT JOIN VARIABLES R ON E.RIGHT_OPERAND = R.NAME

SELECT LEFT_OPERAND, OPERATOR, RIGHT_OPERAND, CASE WHEN OPERATOR = '<' THEN IF (V1.VALUE < V2.VALUE, 'true', 'false') WHEN OPERATOR = '>' THEN IF (V1.VALUE > V2.VALUE, 'true', 'false') WHEN OPERATOR = '=' THEN IF (V1.VALUE = V2.VALUE, 'true', 'false') END AS VALUE FROM EXPRESSIONS E LEFT JOIN VARIABLES V1 ON E.LEFT_OPERAND = V1.NAME LEFT JOIN VARIABLES V2 ON E.RIGHT_OPERAND = V2.NAME

SELECT LEFT_OPERAND, OPERATOR, RIGHT_OPERAND, CASE WHEN OPERATOR = '>' AND A.VALUE > B.VALUE THEN 'true' WHEN OPERATOR = '<' AND A.VALUE < B.VALUE THEN 'true' WHEN OPERATOR = '=' AND A.VALUE = B.VALUE THEN 'true' ELSE 'false' END AS VALUE FROM EXPRESSIONS C LEFT JOIN VARIABLES A ON C.LEFT_OPERAND = A.NAME LEFT JOIN VARIABLES B ON C.RIGHT_OPERAND = B.NAME

SELECT A.LEFT_OPERAND, A.OPERATOR, A.RIGHT_OPERAND, ( CASE WHEN A.OPERATOR = '=' AND A.LEFT_VAL = A.RIGHT_VAL THEN 'true' WHEN A.OPERATOR = '<' AND A.LEFT_VAL < A.RIGHT_VAL THEN 'true' WHEN A.OPERATOR = '>' AND A.LEFT_VAL > A.RIGHT_VAL THEN 'true' ELSE 'false' END ) AS VALUE FROM ( SELECT A.LEFT_OPERAND, A.OPERATOR, A.RIGHT_OPERAND, B.VALUE AS LEFT_VAL, C.VALUE AS RIGHT_VAL FROM EXPRESSIONS AS A LEFT JOIN VARIABLES AS B ON A.LEFT_OPERAND = B.NAME LEFT JOIN VARIABLES AS C ON A.RIGHT_OPERAND = C.NAME ) AS A

SELECT LEFT_OPERAND, OPERATOR,RIGHT_OPERAND, CASE WHEN OPERATOR = '>' AND A.VALUE > B.VALUE THEN 'true' WHEN OPERATOR = '>' AND A.VALUE <= B.VALUE THEN 'false' WHEN OPERATOR = '=' AND A.VALUE = B.VALUE THEN 'true' WHEN OPERATOR = '=' AND A.VALUE != B.VALUE THEN 'false' WHEN OPERATOR = '<' AND A.VALUE < B.VALUE THEN 'true' WHEN OPERATOR = '<' AND A.VALUE >= B.VALUE THEN 'false' ELSE NULL END AS VALUE FROM EXPRESSIONS JOIN VARIABLES A ON EXPRESSIONS.LEFT_OPERAND = A.NAME JOIN VARIABLES B ON EXPRESSIONS.RIGHT_OPERAND = B.NAME

SELECT E.*, CASE WHEN OPERATOR = '>' THEN IF(V1.VALUE > V2.VALUE,'true','false') WHEN OPERATOR = '=' THEN IF(V1.VALUE = V2.VALUE,'true','false') ELSE IF(V1.VALUE < V2.VALUE,'true','false') END AS VALUE FROM EXPRESSIONS E JOIN VARIABLES V1 ON E.LEFT_OPERAND = V1.NAME JOIN VARIABLES V2 ON E.RIGHT_OPERAND = V2.NAME

SELECT E.LEFT_OPERAND, E.OPERATOR, E.RIGHT_OPERAND, CASE WHEN E.OPERATOR = '=' THEN IF(LEFT_V.VALUE = RIGHT_V.VALUE, 'true', 'false') WHEN E.OPERATOR = '<' THEN IF(LEFT_V.VALUE < RIGHT_V.VALUE, 'true', 'false') WHEN E.OPERATOR = '>' THEN IF(LEFT_V.VALUE > RIGHT_V.VALUE, 'true', 'false') END VALUE FROM EXPRESSIONS E JOIN VARIABLES LEFT_V ON E.LEFT_OPERAND = LEFT_V.NAME JOIN VARIABLES RIGHT_V ON E.RIGHT_OPERAND = RIGHT_V.NAME

WITH T AS (SELECT LEFT_OPERAND, OPERATOR, RIGHT_OPERAND, VL.VALUE AS LEFT_OPERAND_VALUE , VR.VALUE AS RIGHT_OPERAND_VALUE FROM EXPRESSIONS E LEFT JOIN VARIABLES VL ON E.LEFT_OPERAND = VL.NAME LEFT JOIN VARIABLES VR ON E.RIGHT_OPERAND = VR.NAME) SELECT LEFT_OPERAND, OPERATOR, RIGHT_OPERAND, (CASE WHEN OPERATOR = '>' AND LEFT_OPERAND_VALUE > RIGHT_OPERAND_VALUE THEN 'true' WHEN OPERATOR = '<' AND LEFT_OPERAND_VALUE < RIGHT_OPERAND_VALUE THEN 'true' WHEN OPERATOR = '=' AND LEFT_OPERAND_VALUE = RIGHT_OPERAND_VALUE THEN 'true' ELSE 'false' END) AS VALUE FROM T

WITH TEMP AS ( SELECT LEFT_OPERAND, COALESCE(L.VALUE,0) AS LEFT_VAL, OPERATOR, RIGHT_OPERAND, COALESCE(R.VALUE,0) AS RIGHT_VAL FROM EXPRESSIONS E LEFT JOIN VARIABLES L ON E.LEFT_OPERAND = L.NAME LEFT JOIN VARIABLES R ON E.RIGHT_OPERAND = R.NAME ) SELECT LEFT_OPERAND, OPERATOR, RIGHT_OPERAND, CASE WHEN OPERATOR = '>' THEN (CASE WHEN LEFT_VAL > RIGHT_VAL THEN 'true' ELSE 'false' END) WHEN OPERATOR = '<' THEN (CASE WHEN LEFT_VAL < RIGHT_VAL THEN 'true' ELSE 'false' END) WHEN OPERATOR = '=' THEN (CASE WHEN LEFT_VAL = RIGHT_VAL THEN 'true' ELSE 'false' END) END AS VALUE FROM TEMP

WITH T1 AS( SELECT E.*, V1.VALUE L, V2.VALUE R FROM EXPRESSIONS E LEFT JOIN VARIABLES V1 ON E.LEFT_OPERAND=V1.NAME LEFT JOIN VARIABLES V2 ON E.RIGHT_OPERAND=V2.NAME ), T2 AS( SELECT LEFT_OPERAND, OPERATOR, RIGHT_OPERAND, (CASE WHEN OPERATOR='>' THEN L>R WHEN OPERATOR='=' THEN L=R WHEN OPERATOR='<' THEN L<R END) VALUE FROM T1 ) SELECT LEFT_OPERAND, OPERATOR, RIGHT_OPERAND, (CASE WHEN VALUE=0 THEN 'false' ELSE 'true' END) VALUE FROM T2

WITH CTE1 AS (SELECT LEFT_OPERAND, OPERATOR, RIGHT_OPERAND, V.VALUE L FROM EXPRESSIONS E LEFT JOIN VARIABLES V ON E.LEFT_OPERAND=V.NAME), CTE2 AS (SELECT LEFT_OPERAND, OPERATOR, RIGHT_OPERAND, L, V.VALUE R FROM CTE1 C LEFT JOIN VARIABLES V ON C.RIGHT_OPERAND=V.NAME) SELECT LEFT_OPERAND, OPERATOR, RIGHT_OPERAND, CASE WHEN OPERATOR='<' AND L<R THEN 'true' WHEN OPERATOR='=' AND L=R THEN 'true' WHEN OPERATOR='>' AND L>R THEN 'true' ELSE 'false' END VALUE FROM CTE2

SELECT LEFT_OPERAND, OPERATOR, RIGHT_OPERAND, (CASE WHEN OPERATOR = '>' AND V1.VALUE > V2.VALUE THEN 'true' WHEN OPERATOR = '=' AND V1.VALUE = V2.VALUE THEN 'true' WHEN OPERATOR = '<' AND V1.VALUE < V2.VALUE THEN 'true' ELSE 'false' END) AS VALUE FROM EXPRESSIONS E JOIN VARIABLES V1 ON V1.NAME = E.LEFT_OPERAND JOIN VARIABLES V2 ON V2.NAME = E.RIGHT_OPERAND

SELECT LEFT_OPERAND, OPERATOR, RIGHT_OPERAND, (CASE WHEN OPERATOR = '>' THEN IF(VAR1.VALUE > VAR2.VALUE, 'true', 'false') WHEN OPERATOR = '=' THEN IF(VAR1.VALUE = VAR2.VALUE, 'true', 'false') WHEN OPERATOR = '<' THEN IF(VAR1.VALUE < VAR2.VALUE, 'true', 'false') END) AS VALUE FROM EXPRESSIONS EXP JOIN VARIABLES VAR1 ON EXP.LEFT_OPERAND = VAR1.NAME JOIN VARIABLES VAR2 ON EXP.RIGHT_OPERAND = VAR2.NAME

SELECT E.LEFT_OPERAND, E.OPERATOR, E.RIGHT_OPERAND, IF(CASE WHEN E.OPERATOR = '=' THEN V.VALUE = V2.VALUE WHEN E.OPERATOR = '<' THEN V.VALUE < V2.VALUE WHEN E.OPERATOR = '>' THEN V.VALUE > V2.VALUE END, 'true', 'false') AS VALUE FROM EXPRESSIONS E LEFT JOIN VARIABLES V ON E.LEFT_OPERAND = V.NAME LEFT JOIN VARIABLES V2 ON E.RIGHT_OPERAND = V2.NAME

SELECT LEFT_OPERAND, OPERATOR, RIGHT_OPERAND, CASE WHEN OPERATOR='>' THEN IF(V1.VALUE > V2.VALUE,'true','false') WHEN OPERATOR='<' THEN IF(V1.VALUE < V2.VALUE,'true','false') WHEN OPERATOR='=' THEN IF(V1.VALUE = V2.VALUE,'true','false') END AS VALUE FROM EXPRESSIONS JOIN VARIABLES V1 ON LEFT_OPERAND=V1.NAME JOIN VARIABLES V2 ON RIGHT_OPERAND=V2.NAME

SELECT E.*, CASE WHEN E.OPERATOR = '>' THEN CASE WHEN L.VALUE > R.VALUE THEN 'true' ELSE 'false' END WHEN E.OPERATOR = '=' THEN CASE WHEN L.VALUE = R.VALUE THEN 'true' ELSE 'false' END WHEN E.OPERATOR = '<' THEN CASE WHEN L.VALUE < R.VALUE THEN 'true' ELSE 'false' END END AS VALUE FROM EXPRESSIONS E JOIN VARIABLES L ON E.LEFT_OPERAND=L.NAME JOIN VARIABLES R ON E.RIGHT_OPERAND=R.NAME

SELECT LEFT_OPERAND , OPERATOR , RIGHT_OPERAND , CASE WHEN OPERATOR = '>' AND V1.VALUE > V2.VALUE THEN 'true' WHEN OPERATOR = '=' AND V1.VALUE = V2.VALUE THEN 'true' WHEN OPERATOR = '<' AND V1.VALUE < V2.VALUE THEN 'true' ELSE 'false' END AS VALUE FROM EXPRESSIONS E JOIN VARIABLES V1 ON E.LEFT_OPERAND = V1.NAME JOIN VARIABLES V2 ON E.RIGHT_OPERAND = V2.NAME

SELECT LEFT_OPERAND, OPERATOR, RIGHT_OPERAND, CASE WHEN OPERATOR = '<' THEN IF(VL.VALUE < VR.VALUE, 'true', 'false') WHEN OPERATOR = '>' THEN IF(VL.VALUE > VR.VALUE, 'true', 'false') WHEN OPERATOR = '=' THEN IF(VL.VALUE = VR.VALUE, 'true', 'false') END VALUE FROM EXPRESSIONS E JOIN VARIABLES VL ON E.LEFT_OPERAND = VL.NAME JOIN VARIABLES VR ON E.RIGHT_OPERAND = VR.NAME

SELECT LEFT_OPERAND, OPERATOR, RIGHT_OPERAND, (CASE WHEN OPERATOR='>' THEN IF(V1.VALUE > V2.VALUE, 'true', 'false') WHEN OPERATOR='<' THEN IF(V1.VALUE < V2.VALUE, 'true', 'false') WHEN V1.VALUE=V2.VALUE THEN IF(V1.VALUE = V2.VALUE, 'true', 'false') ELSE 'false' END) AS VALUE FROM VARIABLES V1 INNER JOIN EXPRESSIONS E ON V1.NAME=E.LEFT_OPERAND INNER JOIN VARIABLES V2 ON E.RIGHT_OPERAND=V2.NAME

SELECT LEFT_OPERAND, OPERATOR, RIGHT_OPERAND, CASE WHEN OPERATOR = '>' AND LV.VALUE > RV.VALUE OR OPERATOR = '<' AND LV.VALUE < RV.VALUE OR OPERATOR = '=' AND LV.VALUE = RV.VALUE THEN 'true' ELSE 'false' END AS VALUE FROM EXPRESSIONS AS E INNER JOIN VARIABLES AS LV ON E.LEFT_OPERAND = LV.NAME INNER JOIN VARIABLES AS RV ON E.RIGHT_OPERAND = RV.NAME

WITH CTE1 AS ( SELECT E.LEFT_OPERAND, E.RIGHT_OPERAND, V1.VALUE AS LEFT_VALUE, E.OPERATOR, V2.VALUE AS RIGHT_VALUE FROM EXPRESSIONS AS E LEFT JOIN VARIABLES AS V1 ON E.LEFT_OPERAND = V1.NAME LEFT JOIN VARIABLES AS V2 ON E.RIGHT_OPERAND = V2.NAME) SELECT LEFT_OPERAND, OPERATOR, RIGHT_OPERAND, CASE WHEN LEFT_VALUE > RIGHT_VALUE AND OPERATOR = '>' THEN 'true' WHEN LEFT_VALUE < RIGHT_VALUE AND OPERATOR = '<' THEN 'true' WHEN LEFT_VALUE = RIGHT_VALUE AND OPERATOR = '=' THEN 'true' ELSE 'false' END AS VALUE FROM CTE1

SELECT LEFT_OPERAND, OPERATOR, RIGHT_OPERAND, IF(OPERATOR=IF(L.VALUE <R.VALUE,'<',IF(L.VALUE>R.VALUE,'>','=')),'true','false') AS VALUE FROM EXPRESSIONS E JOIN VARIABLES L ON E.LEFT_OPERAND=L.NAME JOIN VARIABLES R ON E.RIGHT_OPERAND=R.NAME

SELECT E.*, (CASE WHEN E.OPERATOR = '>' THEN IF(V1.VALUE > V2.VALUE,'true', 'false') WHEN E.OPERATOR = '<' THEN IF(V1.VALUE < V2.VALUE,'true', 'false') WHEN E.OPERATOR = '=' THEN IF(V1.VALUE = V2.VALUE,'true', 'false') END) AS VALUE FROM EXPRESSIONS E LEFT OUTER JOIN VARIABLES V1 ON E.LEFT_OPERAND = V1.NAME LEFT OUTER JOIN VARIABLES V2 ON E.RIGHT_OPERAND = V2.NAME

SELECT E.LEFT_OPERAND , E.OPERATOR , E.RIGHT_OPERAND , CASE WHEN E.OPERATOR = '>' AND V1.VALUE > V2.VALUE THEN 'true' WHEN E.OPERATOR = '=' AND V1.VALUE = V2.VALUE THEN 'true' WHEN E.OPERATOR = '<' AND V1.VALUE < V2.VALUE THEN 'true' ELSE 'false' END AS VALUE FROM EXPRESSIONS E LEFT JOIN VARIABLES V1 ON E.LEFT_OPERAND = V1.NAME LEFT JOIN VARIABLES V2 ON E.RIGHT_OPERAND = V2.NAME

SELECT LEFT_OPERAND, OPERATOR, RIGHT_OPERAND, CASE WHEN A.OPERATOR = '<' AND B.VALUE < C.VALUE THEN 'true' WHEN A.OPERATOR = '>' AND B.VALUE > C.VALUE THEN 'true' WHEN A.OPERATOR = '=' AND B.VALUE = C.VALUE THEN 'true' ELSE 'false' END AS VALUE FROM EXPRESSIONS A JOIN VARIABLES B ON A.LEFT_OPERAND = B.NAME JOIN VARIABLES C ON A.RIGHT_OPERAND = C.NAME

WITH C1 AS(SELECT LEFT_OPERAND, OPERATOR, RIGHT_OPERAND, V.VALUE LEFT_VALUE, V2.VALUE RIGHT_VALUE FROM EXPRESSIONS E LEFT JOIN VARIABLES V ON E.LEFT_OPERAND = V.NAME LEFT JOIN VARIABLES V2 ON E.RIGHT_OPERAND = V2.NAME) SELECT LEFT_OPERAND, OPERATOR, RIGHT_OPERAND, CASE WHEN OPERATOR = '=' AND LEFT_VALUE = RIGHT_VALUE THEN 'true' WHEN OPERATOR = '>' AND LEFT_VALUE > RIGHT_VALUE THEN 'true' WHEN OPERATOR = '<' AND LEFT_VALUE < RIGHT_VALUE THEN 'true' ELSE 'false' END AS VALUE FROM C1

SELECT T2.LEFT_OPERAND, T2.OPERATOR, T2.RIGHT_OPERAND, ( CASE WHEN T2.OPERATOR = '>' THEN IF(T2.LEFT_VALUE > T2.RIGHT_VALUE, 'true', 'false') WHEN T2.OPERATOR = '<' THEN IF(T2.LEFT_VALUE < T2.RIGHT_VALUE, 'true', 'false') WHEN T2.OPERATOR = '=' THEN IF(T2.LEFT_VALUE = T2.RIGHT_VALUE, 'true', 'false') ELSE 'false' END ) AS VALUE FROM ( SELECT T1.LEFT_OPERAND, T1.OPERATOR, T1.RIGHT_OPERAND, T3.VALUE AS LEFT_VALUE, T4.VALUE AS RIGHT_VALUE FROM EXPRESSIONS T1 LEFT JOIN VARIABLES T3 ON T1.LEFT_OPERAND = T3.NAME LEFT JOIN VARIABLES T4 ON T1.RIGHT_OPERAND = T4.NAME ) T2

SELECT LEFT_OPERAND, OPERATOR, RIGHT_OPERAND, IF(CASE OPERATOR WHEN '<' THEN V1.VALUE < V2.VALUE WHEN '>' THEN V1.VALUE > V2.VALUE ELSE V1.VALUE = V2.VALUE END, 'true', 'false') VALUE FROM EXPRESSIONS E, VARIABLES V1, VARIABLES V2 WHERE E.LEFT_OPERAND = V1.NAME AND E.RIGHT_OPERAND = V2.NAME

WITH CTE AS( SELECT E.LEFT_OPERAND, E.OPERATOR, E.RIGHT_OPERAND, V1.VALUE AS LEFT_VALUE, V2.VALUE AS RIGHT_VALUE FROM EXPRESSIONS E LEFT JOIN VARIABLES V1 ON E.LEFT_OPERAND = V1.NAME LEFT JOIN VARIABLES V2 ON E.RIGHT_OPERAND = V2.NAME ) SELECT LEFT_OPERAND, OPERATOR, RIGHT_OPERAND, CASE WHEN OPERATOR = '>' AND LEFT_VALUE > RIGHT_VALUE THEN 'true' WHEN OPERATOR = '<' AND LEFT_VALUE < RIGHT_VALUE THEN 'true' WHEN OPERATOR = '= ' AND LEFT_VALUE = RIGHT_VALUE THEN 'true' ELSE 'false' END AS VALUE FROM CTE

SELECT A.LEFT_OPERAND, A.OPERATOR, A.RIGHT_OPERAND, CASE WHEN OPERATOR = '>' AND B.VALUE > C.VALUE THEN 'true' WHEN OPERATOR = '=' AND B.VALUE = C.VALUE THEN 'true' WHEN OPERATOR = '<' AND B.VALUE < C.VALUE THEN 'true' ELSE 'false' END AS VALUE FROM EXPRESSIONS A INNER JOIN VARIABLES B ON A.LEFT_OPERAND = B.NAME INNER JOIN VARIABLES C ON A.RIGHT_OPERAND = C.NAME

SELECT LEFT_OPERAND, OPERATOR, RIGHT_OPERAND, CASE WHEN OPERATOR = '>' THEN IF(A.VALUE > B.VALUE, 'true', 'false') WHEN OPERATOR = '<' THEN IF(A.VALUE < B.VALUE, 'true', 'false') WHEN OPERATOR = '=' THEN IF(A.VALUE = B.VALUE, 'true', 'false') END AS VALUE FROM EXPRESSIONS E INNER JOIN VARIABLES AS A ON A.NAME = E.LEFT_OPERAND INNER JOIN VARIABLES AS B ON B.NAME = E.RIGHT_OPERAND

WITH K AS (SELECT V1.VALUE AS LEFT_VALUE, LEFT_OPERAND, E.OPERATOR, V2.VALUE AS RIGHT_VALUE, RIGHT_OPERAND FROM EXPRESSIONS AS E LEFT JOIN VARIABLES AS V1 ON E.LEFT_OPERAND = V1.NAME LEFT JOIN VARIABLES AS V2 ON E.RIGHT_OPERAND = V2.NAME) SELECT LEFT_OPERAND, OPERATOR,RIGHT_OPERAND, CASE WHEN OPERATOR = '>' AND LEFT_VALUE > RIGHT_VALUE THEN 'true' WHEN OPERATOR = '=' AND LEFT_VALUE = RIGHT_VALUE THEN 'true' WHEN OPERATOR = '<' AND LEFT_VALUE < RIGHT_VALUE THEN 'true' ELSE 'false' END AS VALUE FROM K

SELECT E.LEFT_OPERAND, E.OPERATOR, E.RIGHT_OPERAND, ( CASE WHEN E.OPERATOR = '<' AND V1.VALUE<V2.VALUE THEN 'true' WHEN E.OPERATOR = '=' AND V1.VALUE=V2.VALUE THEN 'true' WHEN E.OPERATOR = '>' AND V1.VALUE>V2.VALUE THEN 'true' ELSE 'false' END ) AS VALUE FROM VARIABLES V1 JOIN EXPRESSIONS E ON E.LEFT_OPERAND = V1.NAME JOIN VARIABLES V2 ON E.RIGHT_OPERAND = V2.NAME

SELECT LEFT_OPERAND,OPERATOR,RIGHT_OPERAND, CASE WHEN OPERATOR = '>' AND V1.VALUE > V2.VALUE THEN 'true' WHEN OPERATOR = '<' AND V1.VALUE < V2.VALUE THEN 'true' WHEN OPERATOR = '=' AND V1.VALUE = V2.VALUE THEN 'true' ELSE 'false' END AS VALUE FROM EXPRESSIONS E,VARIABLES V1,VARIABLES V2 WHERE E.LEFT_OPERAND = V1.NAME AND E.RIGHT_OPERAND = V2.NAME

SELECT E.LEFT_OPERAND, E.OPERATOR, E.RIGHT_OPERAND ,(CASE WHEN OPERATOR = '>' AND V1.VALUE>V2.VALUE THEN 'true' WHEN OPERATOR = '<' AND V1.VALUE<V2.VALUE THEN 'true' WHEN OPERATOR = '=' AND V1.VALUE=V2.VALUE THEN 'true' ELSE 'false' END) AS VALUE FROM EXPRESSIONS E LEFT JOIN VARIABLES V1 ON V1.NAME = E.LEFT_OPERAND LEFT JOIN VARIABLES V2 ON V2.NAME = E.RIGHT_OPERAND

SELECT E.* , CASE WHEN E.OPERATOR='>' AND (V1.VALUE > V2.VALUE) THEN 'true' WHEN E.OPERATOR='<' AND (V1.VALUE < V2.VALUE) THEN 'true' WHEN E.OPERATOR='=' AND (V1.VALUE = V2.VALUE) THEN 'true' ELSE 'false' END AS VALUE FROM EXPRESSIONS E JOIN VARIABLES V1 ON V1.NAME=E.LEFT_OPERAND JOIN VARIABLES V2 ON V2.NAME=E.RIGHT_OPERAND

WITH ASSIGN_VALUES AS ( SELECT A.LEFT_OPERAND,OPERATOR,RIGHT_OPERAND,B.VALUE AS LEFT_VALUE, C.VALUE AS RIGHT_VALUE FROM EXPRESSIONS A JOIN VARIABLES B ON A.LEFT_OPERAND = B.NAME JOIN VARIABLES C ON A.RIGHT_OPERAND = C.NAME) SELECT LEFT_OPERAND,OPERATOR,RIGHT_OPERAND, CASE WHEN OPERATOR = '>' THEN IF(LEFT_VALUE > RIGHT_VALUE,'true','false') WHEN OPERATOR = '<' THEN IF(LEFT_VALUE < RIGHT_VALUE,'true','false') WHEN OPERATOR = '=' THEN IF(LEFT_VALUE = RIGHT_VALUE,'true','false') END AS VALUE FROM ASSIGN_VALUES

SELECT A.*, CASE WHEN OPERATOR = '>' AND B.VALUE > C.VALUE THEN 'true' WHEN OPERATOR = '<' AND B.VALUE < C.VALUE THEN 'true' WHEN OPERATOR = '=' AND B.VALUE = C.VALUE THEN 'true' ELSE 'false' END AS VALUE FROM EXPRESSIONS AS A LEFT JOIN VARIABLES AS B ON A.LEFT_OPERAND = B.NAME LEFT JOIN VARIABLES AS C ON A.RIGHT_OPERAND = C.NAME

SELECT E.LEFT_OPERAND, E.OPERATOR, E.RIGHT_OPERAND, CASE WHEN E.OPERATOR = '>' AND VL.VALUE > VR.VALUE THEN 'true' WHEN E.OPERATOR = '>' AND VL.VALUE <= VR.VALUE THEN 'false' WHEN E.OPERATOR = '<' AND VL.VALUE < VR.VALUE THEN 'true' WHEN E.OPERATOR = '<' AND VL.VALUE >= VR.VALUE THEN 'false' WHEN VL.VALUE = VR.VALUE THEN 'true' ELSE 'false' END VALUE FROM EXPRESSIONS E LEFT JOIN VARIABLES VL ON E.LEFT_OPERAND = VL.NAME LEFT JOIN VARIABLES VR ON E.RIGHT_OPERAND = VR.NAME

WITH C1 AS (SELECT LEFT_OPERAND, VALUE AS LEFT_VALUE, OPERATOR, RIGHT_OPERAND FROM EXPRESSIONS E JOIN VARIABLES V ON E.LEFT_OPERAND=V.NAME), C2 AS (SELECT C1.LEFT_OPERAND, C1.LEFT_VALUE, C1.OPERATOR, C1.RIGHT_OPERAND, V.VALUE AS RIGHT_VALUE FROM C1 JOIN VARIABLES V ON C1.RIGHT_OPERAND = V.NAME) SELECT LEFT_OPERAND, OPERATOR, RIGHT_OPERAND, CASE WHEN OPERATOR = '=' THEN IF(LEFT_VALUE = RIGHT_VALUE, 'true', 'false') WHEN OPERATOR = '>' THEN IF(LEFT_VALUE > RIGHT_VALUE, 'true', 'false') WHEN OPERATOR = '<' THEN IF(LEFT_VALUE < RIGHT_VALUE, 'true', 'false') END AS VALUE FROM C2

SELECT A.LEFT_OPERAND, A.OPERATOR, A.RIGHT_OPERAND , CASE WHEN OPERATOR = '=' AND B.VALUE=C.VALUE THEN 'true' WHEN OPERATOR = '<' AND B.VALUE<C.VALUE THEN 'true' WHEN OPERATOR = '>' AND B.VALUE>C.VALUE THEN 'true' ELSE 'false' END AS VALUE FROM EXPRESSIONS AS A JOIN VARIABLES AS B ON (A.LEFT_OPERAND=B.NAME) JOIN VARIABLES AS C ON (A.RIGHT_OPERAND=C.NAME)

SELECT LEFT_OPERAND, OPERATOR, RIGHT_OPERAND, (CASE WHEN OPERATOR = '>' AND V1.VALUE > V2.VALUE THEN 'true' WHEN OPERATOR = '<' AND V1.VALUE < V2.VALUE THEN 'true' WHEN OPERATOR = '=' AND V1.VALUE = V2.VALUE THEN 'true' ELSE 'false' END) AS VALUE FROM EXPRESSIONS E JOIN VARIABLES V1 ON V1.NAME = E.LEFT_OPERAND JOIN VARIABLES V2 ON V2.NAME = E.RIGHT_OPERAND

SELECT LEFT_OPERAND, OPERATOR, RIGHT_OPERAND, (CASE WHEN OPERATOR = '>' AND VR1.VALUE > VR2.VALUE THEN 'true' WHEN OPERATOR = '=' AND VR1.VALUE = VR2.VALUE THEN 'true' WHEN OPERATOR = '<' AND VR1.VALUE < VR2.VALUE THEN 'true' ELSE 'false' END) AS VALUE FROM EXPRESSIONS EX JOIN VARIABLES VR1 ON VR1.NAME = EX.LEFT_OPERAND JOIN VARIABLES VR2 ON VR2.NAME = EX.RIGHT_OPERAND

SELECT LEFT_OPERAND, OPERATOR, RIGHT_OPERAND, CASE WHEN OPERATOR = '>' THEN IF(V1.VALUE > V2.VALUE, 'true', 'false') WHEN OPERATOR = '<' THEN IF(V1.VALUE < V2.VALUE, 'true', 'false') WHEN OPERATOR = '=' THEN IF(V1.VALUE = V2.VALUE, 'true', 'false') ELSE 'false' END AS VALUE FROM EXPRESSIONS E JOIN VARIABLES V1 ON E.LEFT_OPERAND = V1.NAME JOIN VARIABLES V2 ON V2.NAME =E.RIGHT_OPERAND

SELECT LEFT_OPERAND, OPERATOR, RIGHT_OPERAND, CASE WHEN OPERATOR = '<' THEN IF(V1.VALUE<V2.VALUE, 'true', 'false') WHEN OPERATOR = '>' THEN IF(V1.VALUE<V2.VALUE, 'true', 'false') ELSE IF(V1.VALUE=V2.VALUE, 'true', 'false') END AS VALUE FROM EXPRESSIONS E JOIN VARIABLES V1 ON V1.NAME = E.LEFT_OPERAND JOIN VARIABLES V2 ON V2.NAME = E.RIGHT_OPERAND

WITH C1 AS ( SELECT E.* ,V1.VALUE AS X, V2.VALUE AS Y FROM EXPRESSIONS E LEFT JOIN VARIABLES V1 ON E.LEFT_OPERAND = V1.NAME LEFT JOIN VARIABLES V2 ON E.RIGHT_OPERAND = V2.NAME ), C2 AS ( SELECT *, CASE WHEN X > Y THEN '>' WHEN X < Y THEN '<' ELSE '=' END AS RELATION FROM C1 ) SELECT LEFT_OPERAND,OPERATOR,RIGHT_OPERAND, CASE WHEN RELATION = OPERATOR THEN 'true' ELSE 'false' END AS VALUE FROM C2

SELECT E.*, CASE WHEN E.OPERATOR='<' THEN IF(L.VALUE<R.VALUE,'true','false') WHEN E.OPERATOR='>' THEN IF(L.VALUE>R.VALUE,'true','false') ELSE IF(L.VALUE=R.VALUE,'true','false') END AS VALUE FROM EXPRESSIONS E JOIN VARIABLES L ON E.LEFT_OPERAND=L.NAME JOIN VARIABLES R ON E.RIGHT_OPERAND=R.NAME

SELECT E.*, (CASE WHEN E.OPERATOR='>' AND V.VALUE>V1.VALUE THEN 'true' WHEN E.OPERATOR='>' AND V.VALUE<=V1.VALUE THEN 'false' WHEN E.OPERATOR='<' AND V.VALUE<V1.VALUE THEN 'true' WHEN E.OPERATOR='<' AND V.VALUE>=V1.VALUE THEN 'false' WHEN E.OPERATOR='=' AND V.VALUE=V1.VALUE THEN 'true' WHEN E.OPERATOR='=' AND V.VALUE<>V1.VALUE THEN 'false' END) AS VALUE FROM EXPRESSIONS E LEFT JOIN VARIABLES V ON E.LEFT_OPERAND = V.NAME LEFT JOIN VARIABLES V1 ON E.RIGHT_OPERAND = V1.NAME

SELECT E.LEFT_OPERAND, E.OPERATOR, E.RIGHT_OPERAND, CASE WHEN E.OPERATOR = '=' AND V.VALUE = V2.VALUE THEN 'true' WHEN E.OPERATOR = '>' AND V.VALUE > V2.VALUE THEN 'true' WHEN E.OPERATOR = '<' AND V.VALUE < V2.VALUE THEN 'true' ELSE 'false' END AS VALUE FROM EXPRESSIONS E INNER JOIN VARIABLES V ON E.LEFT_OPERAND = V.NAME INNER JOIN VARIABLES V2 ON E.RIGHT_OPERAND = V2.NAME

SELECT E.LEFT_OPERAND, E.OPERATOR,E.RIGHT_OPERAND,(CASE WHEN E.OPERATOR='>' THEN IF(V1.VALUE>V2.VALUE, 'true', 'false') WHEN E.OPERATOR='<' THEN IF (V1.VALUE<V2.VALUE, 'true','false') ELSE IF(V1.VALUE=V2.VALUE,'true', 'false') END) AS VALUE FROM EXPRESSIONS AS E JOIN VARIABLES AS V1 ON E.LEFT_OPERAND=V1.NAME JOIN VARIABLES AS V2 ON E.RIGHT_OPERAND=V2.NAME

WITH TEMP1 AS (SELECT LEFT_OPERAND, OPERATOR, RIGHT_OPERAND, V.VALUE AS LEFT_VALUE FROM EXPRESSIONS LEFT JOIN VARIABLES V ON LEFT_OPERAND = NAME), TEMP2 AS (SELECT LEFT_OPERAND, OPERATOR, RIGHT_OPERAND, LEFT_VALUE, V.VALUE AS RIGHT_VALUE FROM TEMP1 LEFT JOIN VARIABLES V ON RIGHT_OPERAND = NAME), TEMP3 AS (SELECT LEFT_OPERAND, OPERATOR, RIGHT_OPERAND, CASE WHEN OPERATOR = '>' THEN (LEFT_VALUE > RIGHT_VALUE) WHEN OPERATOR = '<' THEN (LEFT_VALUE < RIGHT_VALUE) ELSE (LEFT_VALUE = RIGHT_VALUE) END AS NUMB FROM TEMP2) SELECT LEFT_OPERAND, OPERATOR, RIGHT_OPERAND, CASE WHEN NUMB = 1 THEN 'true' ELSE 'false' END AS VALUE FROM TEMP3

SELECT E.LEFT_OPERAND, E.OPERATOR, E.RIGHT_OPERAND, (CASE WHEN OPERATOR = '>' THEN IF(V1.VALUE > V2.VALUE, 'true', 'false') WHEN OPERATOR = '<' THEN IF(V1.VALUE < V2.VALUE, 'true', 'false') WHEN OPERATOR = '=' THEN IF(V1.VALUE = V2.VALUE, 'true', 'false') END) AS VALUE FROM EXPRESSIONS E LEFT JOIN VARIABLES V1 ON V1.NAME = E.LEFT_OPERAND LEFT JOIN VARIABLES V2 ON V2.NAME = E.RIGHT_OPERAND

SELECT LEFT_OPERAND,OPERATOR,RIGHT_OPERAND, CASE WHEN A.OPERATOR = '>' AND B.VALUE > C.VALUE THEN 'true' WHEN A.OPERATOR = '<' AND B.VALUE < C.VALUE THEN 'true' WHEN A.OPERATOR = '=' AND B.VALUE = C.VALUE THEN 'true' ELSE 'false' END AS VALUE FROM EXPRESSIONS A LEFT JOIN VARIABLES B ON A.LEFT_OPERAND = B.NAME LEFT JOIN VARIABLES C ON A.RIGHT_OPERAND = C.NAME

SELECT LEFT_OPERAND, OPERATOR, RIGHT_OPERAND, (CASE WHEN OPERATOR = '>' THEN IF (V1.VALUE > V2.VALUE, 'true', 'false') WHEN OPERATOR = '<' THEN IF (V1.VALUE < V2.VALUE, 'true', 'false') ELSE IF(V1.VALUE = V2.VALUE, 'true', 'false') END) AS VALUE FROM EXPRESSIONS E JOIN VARIABLES V1 ON E.LEFT_OPERAND = V1.NAME JOIN VARIABLES V2 ON E.RIGHT_OPERAND = V2.NAME

SELECT A.*, CASE WHEN A.OPERATOR = '<' AND B.VALUE < C.VALUE THEN 'true' WHEN A.OPERATOR = '=' AND B.VALUE = C.VALUE THEN 'true' WHEN A.OPERATOR = '>' AND B.VALUE > C.VALUE THEN 'true' ELSE 'false' END AS VALUE FROM EXPRESSIONS A LEFT JOIN VARIABLES B ON A.LEFT_OPERAND = B.NAME LEFT JOIN VARIABLES C ON A.RIGHT_OPERAND = C.NAME

SELECT E.*, CASE WHEN OPERATOR = '>' AND V.VALUE > V2.VALUE THEN 'true' WHEN OPERATOR = '<' AND V.VALUE < V2.VALUE THEN 'true' WHEN OPERATOR = '=' AND V.VALUE = V2.VALUE THEN 'true' ELSE 'false' END AS VALUE FROM EXPRESSIONS E JOIN VARIABLES V ON E.LEFT_OPERAND = V.NAME JOIN VARIABLES V2 ON E.RIGHT_OPERAND = V2.NAME

SELECT LEFT_OPERAND,RIGHT_OPERAND,OPERATOR, CASE WHEN LEFT_VALUE>RIGHT_VALUE AND OPERATOR='>' THEN 'true' WHEN LEFT_VALUE=RIGHT_VALUE AND OPERATOR='=' THEN 'true' WHEN LEFT_VALUE<RIGHT_VALUE AND OPERATOR='<' THEN 'true' ELSE 'false' END VALUE FROM (SELECT LEFT_OPERAND,RIGHT_OPERAND, L.VALUE AS LEFT_VALUE,OPERATOR, R.VALUE AS RIGHT_VALUE FROM EXPRESSIONS E LEFT JOIN VARIABLES L ON E.LEFT_OPERAND=L.NAME LEFT JOIN VARIABLES R ON E.RIGHT_OPERAND=R.NAME) A

SELECT E.* , CASE WHEN E.OPERATOR = '=' AND L.VALUE = R.VALUE THEN 'true' WHEN E.OPERATOR = '<' AND L.VALUE < R.VALUE THEN 'true' WHEN E.OPERATOR = '>' AND L.VALUE > R.VALUE THEN 'true' ELSE 'false' END AS VALUE FROM EXPRESSIONS E LEFT JOIN VARIABLES L ON E.LEFT_OPERAND = L.NAME LEFT JOIN VARIABLES R ON E.RIGHT_OPERAND = R.NAME

SELECT EXPRESSIONS.LEFT_OPERAND, OPERATOR, EXPRESSIONS.RIGHT_OPERAND, (CASE WHEN OPERATOR = '>' AND V1.VALUE > V2.VALUE THEN 'true' WHEN OPERATOR = '=' AND V1.VALUE = V2.VALUE THEN 'true' WHEN OPERATOR = '<' AND V1.VALUE < V2.VALUE THEN 'true' ELSE 'false' END ) AS VALUE FROM EXPRESSIONS JOIN VARIABLES V1 ON EXPRESSIONS.LEFT_OPERAND = V1.NAME JOIN VARIABLES V2 ON EXPRESSIONS.RIGHT_OPERAND = V2.NAME

SELECT EXPRESSIONS.LEFT_OPERAND, EXPRESSIONS.OPERATOR, EXPRESSIONS.RIGHT_OPERAND, CASE WHEN EXPRESSIONS.OPERATOR='>' AND A.VALUE>B.VALUE THEN 'true' WHEN EXPRESSIONS.OPERATOR='=' AND A.VALUE=B.VALUE THEN 'true' WHEN EXPRESSIONS.OPERATOR='<' AND A.VALUE<B.VALUE THEN 'true' ELSE 'false' END AS VALUE FROM EXPRESSIONS JOIN VARIABLES AS A ON A.NAME=EXPRESSIONS.LEFT_OPERAND JOIN VARIABLES AS B ON B.NAME=EXPRESSIONS.RIGHT_OPERAND

SELECT A.LEFT_OPERAND,A.OPERATOR,A.RIGHT_OPERAND, (CASE WHEN A.OPERATOR = '>' AND V1.VALUE > V2.VALUE THEN 'true' WHEN A.OPERATOR = '<' AND V1.VALUE < V2.VALUE THEN 'true' WHEN A.OPERATOR = '=' AND V1.VALUE = V2.VALUE THEN 'true' ELSE 'false' END ) AS VALUE FROM EXPRESSIONS A JOIN VARIABLES V1 ON V1.NAME = A.LEFT_OPERAND JOIN VARIABLES V2 ON V2.NAME = A.RIGHT_OPERAND

SELECT E.*, CASE WHEN (E.OPERATOR = '>') AND (V1.VALUE > V2.VALUE) THEN 'true' WHEN (E.OPERATOR = '<') AND (V1.VALUE < V2.VALUE) THEN 'true' WHEN (E.OPERATOR = '=') AND (V1.VALUE = V2.VALUE) THEN 'true' ELSE 'false' END VALUE FROM EXPRESSIONS E LEFT OUTER JOIN VARIABLES V1 ON V1.NAME=E.LEFT_OPERAND LEFT OUTER JOIN VARIABLES V2 ON V2.NAME=E.RIGHT_OPERAND

SELECT E.LEFT_OPERAND, E.OPERATOR, E.RIGHT_OPERAND, ( CASE WHEN E.OPERATOR = '<' AND V1.VALUE < V2.VALUE THEN 'true' WHEN E.OPERATOR = '>' AND V1.VALUE > V2.VALUE THEN 'true' WHEN E.OPERATOR = '=' AND V1.VALUE = V2.VALUE THEN 'true' ELSE 'false' END ) AS VALUE FROM EXPRESSIONS E JOIN VARIABLES V1 ON E.LEFT_OPERAND = V1.NAME JOIN VARIABLES V2 ON E.RIGHT_OPERAND = V2.NAME

SELECT E.LEFT_OPERAND, E.OPERATOR, E.RIGHT_OPERAND, CASE WHEN E.OPERATOR = '=' THEN IF(V1.VALUE = V2.VALUE, 'true', 'false') WHEN E.OPERATOR = '<' THEN IF(V1.VALUE < V2.VALUE, 'true', 'false') ELSE IF(V1.VALUE > V2.VALUE, 'true', 'false') END AS VALUE FROM EXPRESSIONS E LEFT JOIN VARIABLES V1 ON E.LEFT_OPERAND = V1.NAME LEFT JOIN VARIABLES V2 ON E.RIGHT_OPERAND = V2.NAME

SELECT LEFT_OPERAND, OPERATOR, RIGHT_OPERAND, (CASE WHEN OPERATOR = '>' THEN IF(V1.VALUE > V2.VALUE, 'true', 'false') WHEN OPERATOR = '<' THEN IF(V1.VALUE < V2.VALUE, 'true', 'false') ELSE IF(V1.VALUE = V2.VALUE, 'true', 'false') END) VALUE FROM EXPRESSIONS E JOIN VARIABLES V1 ON E.LEFT_OPERAND = V1.NAME JOIN VARIABLES V2 ON E.RIGHT_OPERAND = V2.NAME

SELECT E.LEFT_OPERAND, E.OPERATOR, E.RIGHT_OPERAND, CASE WHEN E.OPERATOR = '=' THEN IF(V.VALUE = VR.VALUE ,'true','false') WHEN E.OPERATOR = '>' THEN IF(V.VALUE > VR.VALUE ,'true','false') WHEN E.OPERATOR = '<' THEN IF(V.VALUE < VR.VALUE ,'true','false') END VALUE FROM EXPRESSIONS E JOIN VARIABLES V ON V.NAME = E.LEFT_OPERAND JOIN VARIABLES VR ON VR.NAME = E.RIGHT_OPERAND

SELECT E.LEFT_OPERAND, OPERATOR, E.RIGHT_OPERAND, CASE WHEN (V1.VALUE > V2.VALUE AND OPERATOR ='>') OR (V1.VALUE = V2.VALUE AND OPERATOR ='=') OR( V1.VALUE < V2.VALUE AND OPERATOR ='<') THEN 'true' ELSE 'false' END AS VALUE FROM EXPRESSIONS E INNER JOIN VARIABLES V1 ON V1.NAME = E.LEFT_OPERAND INNER JOIN VARIABLES V2 ON V2.NAME = E.RIGHT_OPERAND

WITH CTE AS ( SELECT DISTINCT B.VALUE,A.LEFT_OPERAND, A.OPERATOR, A.RIGHT_OPERAND, C.VALUE AS VALUEE FROM EXPRESSIONS A INNER JOIN VARIABLES B ON A.LEFT_OPERAND = B.NAME INNER JOIN VARIABLES C ON A.RIGHT_OPERAND = C.NAME ), CTC AS( SELECT LEFT_OPERAND, CTE.OPERATOR, RIGHT_OPERAND, (CASE WHEN CTE.OPERATOR = '>' AND CTE.VALUE > CTE.VALUEE THEN 'true' WHEN CTE.OPERATOR = '<' AND CTE.VALUE < CTE.VALUEE THEN 'true' WHEN CTE.OPERATOR = '=' AND CTE.VALUE = CTE.VALUEE THEN 'true' ELSE 'false' END) VALUE FROM CTE ) SELECT LEFT_OPERAND, OPERATOR, RIGHT_OPERAND, VALUE FROM CTC

WITH T AS (SELECT V1.VALUE AS VALUE1, E.LEFT_OPERAND, E.OPERATOR, V2.VALUE AS VALUE2, E.RIGHT_OPERAND FROM EXPRESSIONS E JOIN VARIABLES V1 ON E.LEFT_OPERAND = V1.NAME JOIN VARIABLES V2 ON E.RIGHT_OPERAND = V2.NAME) SELECT T.LEFT_OPERAND, T.OPERATOR, T.RIGHT_OPERAND, CASE WHEN T.OPERATOR = '>' AND T.VALUE1 > T.VALUE2 THEN 'true' WHEN T.OPERATOR = '=' AND T.VALUE1 = T.VALUE2 THEN 'true' WHEN T.OPERATOR = '<' AND T.VALUE1 < T.VALUE2 THEN 'true' ELSE 'false' END AS VALUE FROM T

SELECT E.*, CASE WHEN OPERATOR = '>' AND V1.VALUE > V2.VALUE THEN 'true' WHEN OPERATOR = '=' AND V1.VALUE = V2.VALUE THEN 'true' WHEN OPERATOR = '<' AND V1.VALUE < V2.VALUE THEN 'true' ELSE 'false' END AS VALUE FROM EXPRESSIONS AS E LEFT JOIN VARIABLES AS V1 ON E.LEFT_OPERAND = V1.NAME LEFT JOIN VARIABLES AS V2 ON E.RIGHT_OPERAND = V2.NAME

SELECT LEFT_OPERAND, OPERATOR, RIGHT_OPERAND, CASE WHEN OPERATOR = '=' THEN (CASE WHEN (V1.VALUE=V2.VALUE) = 1 THEN 'true' ELSE 'false' END) WHEN OPERATOR = '>' THEN (CASE WHEN (V1.VALUE>V2.VALUE) = 1 THEN 'true' ELSE 'false' END) WHEN OPERATOR = '<' THEN (CASE WHEN (V1.VALUE<V2.VALUE) = 1 THEN 'true' ELSE 'false' END) END AS VALUE FROM EXPRESSIONS E JOIN VARIABLES V1 ON V1.NAME = E.LEFT_OPERAND JOIN VARIABLES V2 ON V2.NAME = E.RIGHT_OPERAND

SELECT LEFT_OPERAND,OPERATOR,RIGHT_OPERAND, CASE WHEN OPERATOR = '>' THEN IF((V1.VALUE-V2.VALUE)>0,'true','false') WHEN OPERATOR = '<' THEN IF ((V1.VALUE-V2.VALUE)<0,'true','false') WHEN OPERATOR = '=' THEN IF ((V1.VALUE-V2.VALUE) = 0, 'true','false') END AS VALUE FROM EXPRESSIONS LEFT JOIN VARIABLES V1 ON EXPRESSIONS.LEFT_OPERAND = V1.NAME LEFT JOIN VARIABLES V2 ON EXPRESSIONS.RIGHT_OPERAND = V2.NAME

SELECT E.*, (CASE WHEN E.OPERATOR = '>' THEN IF(V1.VALUE > V2.VALUE, 'true', 'false') WHEN E.OPERATOR = '=' THEN IF(V1.VALUE = V2.VALUE, 'true', 'false') ELSE IF(V1.VALUE < V2.VALUE, 'true', 'false') END ) AS VALUE FROM EXPRESSIONS E JOIN VARIABLES V1 ON E.LEFT_OPERAND = V1.NAME JOIN VARIABLES V2 ON E.RIGHT_OPERAND = V2.NAME

SELECT LEFT_OPERAND, OPERATOR, RIGHT_OPERAND, IF(CASE WHEN OPERATOR = '<' THEN LEFTOPVAL.VALUE < RIGHTOPVAL.VALUE WHEN OPERATOR = '>' THEN LEFTOPVAL.VALUE > RIGHTOPVAL.VALUE WHEN OPERATOR = '=' THEN LEFTOPVAL.VALUE = RIGHTOPVAL.VALUE END, 'true','false') AS VALUE FROM EXPRESSIONS JOIN VARIABLES LEFTOPVAL ON LEFT_OPERAND = LEFTOPVAL.NAME JOIN VARIABLES RIGHTOPVAL ON RIGHT_OPERAND = RIGHTOPVAL.NAME

SELECT E.*, CASE WHEN OPERATOR = '>' AND A.VALUE > B.VALUE THEN 'true' WHEN OPERATOR = '<' AND A.VALUE < B.VALUE THEN 'true' WHEN OPERATOR = '=' AND A.VALUE = B.VALUE THEN 'true' ELSE 'false' END AS VALUE FROM EXPRESSIONS E JOIN VARIABLES A ON E.LEFT_OPERAND = A.NAME JOIN VARIABLES B ON E.RIGHT_OPERAND = B.NAME

SELECT LEFT_OPERAND, OPERATOR, RIGHT_OPERAND, CASE WHEN OPERATOR = '<' AND V1.VALUE < V2.VALUE THEN 'true' WHEN OPERATOR = '=' AND V1.VALUE = V2.VALUE THEN 'true' WHEN OPERATOR = '>' AND V1.VALUE > V2.VALUE THEN 'true' ELSE 'false' END AS VALUE FROM EXPRESSIONS E JOIN VARIABLES V1 ON E.LEFT_OPERAND = V1.NAME JOIN VARIABLES V2 ON E.RIGHT_OPERAND = V2.NAME

SELECT LEFT_OPERAND, OPERATOR, RIGHT_OPERAND, (CASE WHEN OPERATOR = '>' AND V1.VALUE > V2.VALUE THEN 'true' WHEN OPERATOR = '<' AND V1.VALUE < V2.VALUE THEN 'true' WHEN OPERATOR = '=' AND V1.VALUE = V2.VALUE THEN 'true' ELSE 'false' END) AS VALUE FROM EXPRESSIONS JOIN VARIABLES V1 ON EXPRESSIONS.LEFT_OPERAND = V1.NAME JOIN VARIABLES V2 ON EXPRESSIONS.RIGHT_OPERAND = V2.NAME

WITH CTE AS ( SELECT LEFT_OPERAND,OPERATOR,RIGHT_OPERAND, CASE WHEN T2.VALUE -T3.VALUE > 0 THEN '>' WHEN T2.VALUE -T3.VALUE < 0 THEN '<' ELSE '=' END AS VALUE FROM EXPRESSIONS T1 LEFT JOIN VARIABLES T2 ON T2.NAME = T1.LEFT_OPERAND LEFT JOIN VARIABLES T3 ON T3.NAME = T1.RIGHT_OPERAND) SELECT LEFT_OPERAND,OPERATOR,RIGHT_OPERAND, IF(VALUE = OPERATOR,'true','false') AS VALUE FROM CTE

SELECT LEFT_OPERAND, OPERATOR, RIGHT_OPERAND, (CASE WHEN OPERATOR = '>' AND V1.VALUE > V2.VALUE THEN 'true' WHEN OPERATOR = '<' AND V1.VALUE < V2.VALUE THEN 'true' WHEN OPERATOR = '=' AND V1.VALUE = V2.VALUE THEN 'true' ELSE 'false' END) AS VALUE FROM EXPRESSIONS LEFT JOIN VARIABLES AS V1 ON EXPRESSIONS.LEFT_OPERAND = V1.NAME JOIN VARIABLES AS V2 ON EXPRESSIONS.RIGHT_OPERAND = V2.NAME

SELECT E.LEFT_OPERAND, E.OPERATOR, E.RIGHT_OPERAND, (CASE WHEN E.OPERATOR = '>' AND V1.VALUE > V2.VALUE THEN 'true' WHEN E.OPERATOR = '<' AND V1.VALUE < V2.VALUE THEN 'true' WHEN E.OPERATOR = '=' AND V1.VALUE = V2.VALUE THEN 'true' ELSE 'false' END) AS VALUE FROM EXPRESSIONS E LEFT JOIN VARIABLES V1 ON E.LEFT_OPERAND = V1.NAME LEFT JOIN VARIABLES V2 ON E.RIGHT_OPERAND = V2.NAME

SELECT E.*, CASE WHEN E.OPERATOR = '<' THEN IF(L.VALUE < R.VALUE,'true','false') WHEN E.OPERATOR = '>' THEN IF(L.VALUE > R.VALUE,'true','false') ELSE IF(L.VALUE = R.VALUE,'true','false') END AS VALUE FROM EXPRESSIONS E LEFT JOIN VARIABLES L ON E.LEFT_OPERAND = L.NAME LEFT JOIN VARIABLES R ON E.RIGHT_OPERAND = R.NAME

SELECT B.LEFT_OPERAND, B.OPERATOR, B.RIGHT_OPERAND, (CASE WHEN OPERATOR = '>' AND A.VALUE > C.VALUE THEN 'true' WHEN OPERATOR = '=' AND A.VALUE = C.VALUE THEN 'true' WHEN OPERATOR = '<' AND A.VALUE < C.VALUE THEN 'true' ELSE 'false' END) AS VALUE FROM EXPRESSIONS B LEFT JOIN VARIABLES A ON A.NAME=B.LEFT_OPERAND JOIN VARIABLES C ON C.NAME= B.RIGHT_OPERAND

SELECT X.LEFT_OPERAND, X.OPERATOR, X.RIGHT_OPERAND, CASE WHEN X.VALUE = 1 THEN 'true' ELSE 'false' END AS VALUE FROM (SELECT EXPRESSIONS.*, CASE WHEN OPERATOR = '>' THEN L.VALUE > R.VALUE WHEN OPERATOR = '<' THEN L.VALUE < R.VALUE ELSE L.VALUE = R.VALUE END AS VALUE FROM EXPRESSIONS LEFT JOIN VARIABLES L ON EXPRESSIONS.LEFT_OPERAND = L.NAME LEFT JOIN VARIABLES R ON EXPRESSIONS.RIGHT_OPERAND = R.NAME) X

WITH CTE AS (SELECT A.VALUE AS VALUE1,B.LEFT_OPERAND,B.RIGHT_OPERAND,C.VALUE AS VALUE2,B.OPERATOR FROM VARIABLES A JOIN EXPRESSIONS B ON B.LEFT_OPERAND=A.NAME JOIN VARIABLES C ON B.RIGHT_OPERAND=C.NAME) SELECT LEFT_OPERAND,OPERATOR,RIGHT_OPERAND, CASE WHEN OPERATOR='>' AND VALUE1>VALUE2 THEN 'true' WHEN OPERATOR='=' AND VALUE1=VALUE2 THEN 'true' WHEN OPERATOR='<' AND VALUE1<VALUE2 THEN 'true' ELSE 'false' END AS VALUE FROM CTE

SELECT LEFT_OPERAND, OPERATOR, RIGHT_OPERAND, CASE WHEN OPERATOR='<' THEN CASE WHEN V1.VALUE<V2.VALUE THEN 'true' ELSE 'false' END WHEN OPERATOR='=' THEN CASE WHEN V1.VALUE=V2.VALUE THEN 'true' ELSE 'false' END ELSE CASE WHEN V1.VALUE>V2.VALUE THEN 'true' ELSE 'false' END END AS VALUE FROM EXPRESSIONS LEFT JOIN VARIABLES AS V1 ON EXPRESSIONS.LEFT_OPERAND = V1.NAME LEFT JOIN VARIABLES AS V2 ON EXPRESSIONS.RIGHT_OPERAND = V2.NAME

SELECT E.LEFT_OPERAND, E.OPERATOR, E.RIGHT_OPERAND, CASE WHEN E.OPERATOR = '>' AND V.VALUE > V2.VALUE THEN 'true' WHEN E.OPERATOR = '<' AND V.VALUE < V2.VALUE THEN 'true' WHEN E.OPERATOR = '=' AND V.VALUE = V2.VALUE THEN 'true' ELSE 'false' END AS VALUE FROM EXPRESSIONS AS E LEFT JOIN VARIABLES AS V ON V.NAME = E.LEFT_OPERAND LEFT JOIN VARIABLES AS V2 ON V2.NAME = E.RIGHT_OPERAND

SELECT LEFT_OPERAND, OPERATOR, RIGHT_OPERAND , CASE WHEN OPERATOR='>' AND T1.VALUE>T2.VALUE THEN 'true' WHEN OPERATOR='=' AND T1.VALUE=T2.VALUE THEN 'true' WHEN OPERATOR='<' AND T1.VALUE<T2.VALUE THEN 'true' ELSE 'false' END AS VALUE FROM EXPRESSIONS JOIN VARIABLES T1 ON T1.NAME=LEFT_OPERAND JOIN VARIABLES T2 ON T2.NAME=RIGHT_OPERAND

SELECT E.LEFT_OPERAND, E.OPERATOR, E.RIGHT_OPERAND, (CASE WHEN V.VALUE < VA.VALUE AND OPERATOR LIKE '<' THEN 'true' WHEN V.VALUE > VA.VALUE AND OPERATOR LIKE '>' THEN 'true' WHEN V.VALUE = VA.VALUE AND OPERATOR LIKE '=' THEN 'true' ELSE 'false' END ) AS VALUE FROM EXPRESSIONS E JOIN VARIABLES V ON V.NAME = E.LEFT_OPERAND JOIN VARIABLES VA ON VA.NAME = E.RIGHT_OPERAND

SELECT EXPRESSIONS.LEFT_OPERAND, EXPRESSIONS.OPERATOR, EXPRESSIONS.RIGHT_OPERAND, (CASE WHEN EXPRESSIONS.OPERATOR='>' AND V1.VALUE>V2.VALUE THEN 'true' WHEN EXPRESSIONS.OPERATOR='=' AND V1.VALUE=V2.VALUE THEN 'true' WHEN EXPRESSIONS.OPERATOR='<' AND V1.VALUE<V2.VALUE THEN 'true' ELSE 'false' END ) AS VALUE FROM EXPRESSIONS JOIN VARIABLES V1 ON V1.NAME=EXPRESSIONS.LEFT_OPERAND JOIN VARIABLES V2 ON V2.NAME=EXPRESSIONS.RIGHT_OPERAND

SELECT LEFT_OPERAND, OPERATOR, RIGHT_OPERAND, CASE WHEN (V1.VALUE<V2.VALUE AND OPERATOR='<') OR (V1.VALUE=V2.VALUE AND OPERATOR='=') OR (V1.VALUE>V2.VALUE AND OPERATOR='>') THEN 'true' ELSE 'false' END AS VALUE FROM EXPRESSIONS E JOIN VARIABLES V1 ON E.LEFT_OPERAND=V1.NAME JOIN VARIABLES V2 ON E.RIGHT_OPERAND=V2.NAME

SELECT E.LEFT_OPERAND, E.OPERATOR, E.RIGHT_OPERAND, CASE WHEN OPERATOR = '>' AND V1.VALUE > V2.VALUE THEN 'true' WHEN OPERATOR = '<' AND V1.VALUE < V2.VALUE THEN 'true' WHEN OPERATOR = '=' AND V1.VALUE = V2.VALUE THEN 'true' ELSE 'false' END AS VALUE FROM EXPRESSIONS AS E JOIN VARIABLES AS V1 ON V1.NAME = E.LEFT_OPERAND JOIN VARIABLES AS V2 ON V2.NAME = E.RIGHT_OPERAND

SELECT LEFT_OPERAND, OPERATOR, RIGHT_OPERAND, (CASE OPERATOR WHEN '>' THEN CASE WHEN VL.VALUE > VR.VALUE THEN 'true' ELSE 'false' END WHEN '<' THEN CASE WHEN VL.VALUE < VR.VALUE THEN 'true' ELSE 'false' END WHEN '=' THEN CASE WHEN VL.VALUE = VR.VALUE THEN 'true' ELSE 'false' END END ) AS VALUE FROM EXPRESSIONS E JOIN VARIABLES AS VL ON E.LEFT_OPERAND = VL.NAME JOIN VARIABLES AS VR ON E.RIGHT_OPERAND = VR.NAME

WITH CTE AS (SELECT B.LEFT_OPERAND, B.OPERATOR, B.RIGHT_OPERAND, A1.VALUE AS LEFT_VALUE, A2.VALUE AS RIGHT_VALUE FROM EXPRESSIONS B INNER JOIN VARIABLES A1 ON B.LEFT_OPERAND = A1.NAME INNER JOIN VARIABLES A2 ON B.RIGHT_OPERAND = A2.NAME) SELECT LEFT_OPERAND, OPERATOR, RIGHT_OPERAND, CASE WHEN OPERATOR = '>' THEN IF(LEFT_VALUE>RIGHT_VALUE,'true','false') WHEN OPERATOR = '=' THEN IF(LEFT_VALUE=RIGHT_VALUE,'true','false') WHEN OPERATOR = '<' THEN IF(LEFT_VALUE<RIGHT_VALUE,'true','false') END AS VALUE FROM CTE

SELECT LEFT_OPERAND, OPERATOR, RIGHT_OPERAND , CASE WHEN OPERATOR = '>' AND V1.VALUE > V2.VALUE THEN 'true' WHEN OPERATOR = '<' AND V1.VALUE < V2.VALUE THEN 'true' WHEN OPERATOR = '=' AND V1.VALUE = V2.VALUE THEN 'true' ELSE 'false' END AS VALUE FROM EXPRESSIONS E LEFT JOIN VARIABLES V1 ON E.LEFT_OPERAND = V1.NAME LEFT JOIN VARIABLES V2 ON E.RIGHT_OPERAND = V2.NAME

WITH CTE AS (SELECT A.LEFT_OPERAND, B.VALUE AS LEFT_VALUE, A.OPERATOR, A.RIGHT_OPERAND, C.VALUE AS RIGHT_VALUE FROM EXPRESSIONS A INNER JOIN VARIABLES B ON A.LEFT_OPERAND=B.NAME INNER JOIN VARIABLES C ON A.RIGHT_OPERAND=C.NAME) SELECT LEFT_OPERAND,OPERATOR ,RIGHT_OPERAND , (CASE WHEN LEFT_VALUE>RIGHT_VALUE AND OPERATOR='>' THEN 'true' WHEN LEFT_VALUE<RIGHT_VALUE AND OPERATOR='<' THEN 'true' WHEN LEFT_VALUE=RIGHT_VALUE AND OPERATOR='=' THEN 'true' ELSE 'false' END) AS VALUE FROM CTE

SELECT LEFT_OPERAND, OPERATOR, RIGHT_OPERAND,(CASE WHEN OPERATOR = '>' AND V1.VALUE > V2.VALUE THEN 'true' WHEN OPERATOR = '<' AND V1.VALUE < V2.VALUE THEN 'true' WHEN OPERATOR = '=' AND V1.VALUE = V2.VALUE THEN 'true' ELSE 'false' END ) AS VALUE FROM EXPRESSIONS E LEFT JOIN VARIABLES V1 ON E.LEFT_OPERAND = V1.NAME LEFT JOIN VARIABLES V2 ON E.RIGHT_OPERAND = V2.NAME

SELECT A.*, CASE WHEN OPERATOR = '>' THEN (CASE WHEN B.VALUE > C.VALUE THEN 'true' ELSE 'false' END) WHEN OPERATOR = '<' THEN (CASE WHEN B.VALUE < C.VALUE THEN 'true' ELSE 'false' END) WHEN OPERATOR = '=' THEN (CASE WHEN B.VALUE = C.VALUE THEN 'true' ELSE 'false' END) END AS VALUE FROM EXPRESSIONS AS A LEFT JOIN VARIABLES AS B ON A.LEFT_OPERAND = B.NAME LEFT JOIN VARIABLES AS C ON A.RIGHT_OPERAND = C.NAME

SELECT LEFT_OPERAND, OPERATOR, RIGHT_OPERAND, CASE WHEN OPERATOR = '>' AND V1.VALUE > V2.VALUE THEN 'true' WHEN OPERATOR = '<' AND V1.VALUE < V2.VALUE THEN 'true' WHEN OPERATOR = '=' AND V1.VALUE = V2.VALUE THEN 'true' ELSE 'false' END AS VALUE FROM VARIABLES V1 JOIN EXPRESSIONS E ON V1.NAME = E.LEFT_OPERAND JOIN VARIABLES V2 ON V2.NAME = E.RIGHT_OPERAND

SELECT LEFT_OPERAND, OPERATOR, RIGHT_OPERAND, CASE WHEN E.OPERATOR ='=' THEN IF(V1.VALUE = V2.VALUE,'true', 'false') WHEN E.OPERATOR ='>' THEN IF(V1.VALUE >V2.VALUE,'true','false') WHEN E.OPERATOR ='<' THEN IF(V1.VALUE<V2.VALUE,'true','false') END AS VALUE FROM EXPRESSIONS E LEFT JOIN VARIABLES V1 ON E.LEFT_OPERAND = V1.NAME LEFT JOIN VARIABLES V2 ON E.RIGHT_OPERAND = V2.NAME

SELECT LEFT_OPERAND, OPERATOR, RIGHT_OPERAND, (CASE WHEN OPERATOR = '<' THEN IF(L.VALUE < R.VALUE, 'true', 'false') WHEN OPERATOR = '>' THEN IF(L.VALUE > R.VALUE, 'true', 'false') ELSE IF(L.VALUE = R.VALUE, 'true', 'false') END) AS VALUE FROM EXPRESSIONS LEFT JOIN VARIABLES L ON LEFT_OPERAND = L.NAME LEFT JOIN VARIABLES R ON RIGHT_OPERAND = R.NAME

SELECT LEFT_OPERAND, OPERATOR, RIGHT_OPERAND, CASE WHEN OPERATOR = '>' THEN CASE WHEN V_LEFT.VALUE > V_RIGHT.VALUE THEN 'true' ELSE 'false' END WHEN OPERATOR = '<' THEN CASE WHEN V_LEFT.VALUE < V_RIGHT.VALUE THEN 'true' ELSE 'false' END ELSE CASE WHEN V_LEFT.VALUE = V_RIGHT.VALUE THEN 'true' ELSE 'false' END END AS VALUE FROM EXPRESSIONS E INNER JOIN VARIABLES V_LEFT INNER JOIN VARIABLES V_RIGHT ON E.LEFT_OPERAND = V_LEFT.NAME AND E.RIGHT_OPERAND = V_RIGHT.NAME

SELECT LEFT_OPERAND, OPERATOR, RIGHT_OPERAND, CASE WHEN OPERATOR = '=' AND VL.VALUE = VR.VALUE THEN 'true' WHEN OPERATOR = '<' AND VL.VALUE < VR.VALUE THEN 'true' WHEN OPERATOR = '>' AND VL.VALUE > VR.VALUE THEN 'true' ELSE 'false' END AS VALUE FROM EXPRESSIONS E JOIN VARIABLES VL ON E.LEFT_OPERAND = VL.NAME JOIN VARIABLES VR ON E.RIGHT_OPERAND = VR.NAME

SELECT E.LEFT_OPERAND, E.OPERATOR, E.RIGHT_OPERAND, ( CASE WHEN E.OPERATOR = '<' AND V1.VALUE < V2.VALUE THEN 'true' WHEN E.OPERATOR = '=' AND V1.VALUE = V2.VALUE THEN 'true' WHEN E.OPERATOR = '>' AND V1.VALUE > V2.VALUE THEN 'true' ELSE 'false' END ) AS VALUE FROM EXPRESSIONS AS E JOIN VARIABLES AS V1 ON E.LEFT_OPERAND = V1.NAME JOIN VARIABLES AS V2 ON E.RIGHT_OPERAND = V2.NAME

SELECT E.LEFT_OPERAND ,E.OPERATOR ,E.RIGHT_OPERAND ,CASE WHEN E.OPERATOR = '>' AND L.VALUE > R.VALUE THEN 'true' WHEN E.OPERATOR = '=' AND L.VALUE = R.VALUE THEN 'true' WHEN E.OPERATOR = '<' AND L.VALUE < R.VALUE THEN 'true' ELSE 'false' END VALUE FROM EXPRESSIONS E JOIN VARIABLES L ON E.LEFT_OPERAND = L.NAME JOIN VARIABLES R ON E.RIGHT_OPERAND = R.NAME

SELECT LEFT_OPERAND, OPERATOR, RIGHT_OPERAND, CASE WHEN OPERATOR='>' THEN IF(V1.VALUE>V2.VALUE,'true','false') WHEN OPERATOR='<' THEN IF(V1.VALUE<V2.VALUE,'true','false') WHEN OPERATOR='=' THEN IF(V1.VALUE=V2.VALUE,'true','false') END VALUE FROM EXPRESSIONS E JOIN VARIABLES V1 ON V1.NAME=E.LEFT_OPERAND JOIN VARIABLES V2 ON V2.NAME=E.RIGHT_OPERAND

SELECT T.LEFT_OPERAND,T.OPERATOR,T.RIGHT_OPERAND, (CASE WHEN OPERATOR='>' AND T.VX >T.VY THEN 'true' WHEN OPERATOR='=' AND T.VX =T.VY THEN 'true' WHEN OPERATOR='<' AND T.VX <T.VY THEN 'true' ELSE 'false' END) AS VALUE FROM (SELECT A.LEFT_OPERAND,A.OPERATOR,A.RIGHT_OPERAND, A.VX,VYY.VALUE AS VY FROM (SELECT E.LEFT_OPERAND,E.OPERATOR,E.RIGHT_OPERAND, V.VALUE AS VX FROM EXPRESSIONS AS E LEFT JOIN VARIABLES AS V ON E.LEFT_OPERAND=V.NAME) AS A LEFT JOIN VARIABLES AS VYY ON A.RIGHT_OPERAND=VYY.NAME )AS T

SELECT E.* , CASE WHEN (E.OPERATOR = '>' AND V1.VALUE > V2.VALUE) OR (E.OPERATOR = '=' AND V1.VALUE = V2.VALUE) OR (E.OPERATOR = '<' AND V1.VALUE < V2.VALUE) THEN 'true' ELSE 'false' END VALUE FROM EXPRESSIONS E LEFT JOIN VARIABLES V1 ON E.LEFT_OPERAND = V1.NAME LEFT JOIN VARIABLES V2 ON E.RIGHT_OPERAND = V2.NAME

SELECT LEFT_OPERAND, OPERATOR, RIGHT_OPERAND, CASE OPERATOR WHEN '>' THEN IF(LEFTVARIABLES.VALUE > RIGHTVARIABLES.VALUE, 'true', 'false') WHEN '<' THEN IF(LEFTVARIABLES.VALUE < RIGHTVARIABLES.VALUE, 'true', 'false') ELSE IF(LEFTVARIABLES.VALUE = RIGHTVARIABLES.VALUE, 'true', 'false') END AS VALUE FROM EXPRESSIONS JOIN VARIABLES AS LEFTVARIABLES ON LEFT_OPERAND = LEFTVARIABLES.NAME JOIN VARIABLES AS RIGHTVARIABLES ON RIGHT_OPERAND = RIGHTVARIABLES.NAME

SELECT EXPRESSIONS.*, CASE EXPRESSIONS.OPERATOR WHEN '>' THEN (IF(LEFT_VARIABLES.VALUE > RIGHT_VARIABLES.VALUE, 'true', 'false')) WHEN '<' THEN (IF(LEFT_VARIABLES.VALUE < RIGHT_VARIABLES.VALUE, 'true', 'false')) WHEN '=' THEN(IF(LEFT_VARIABLES.VALUE = RIGHT_VARIABLES.VALUE, 'true', 'false')) END AS VALUE FROM EXPRESSIONS JOIN VARIABLES LEFT_VARIABLES ON LEFT_VARIABLES.NAME = EXPRESSIONS.LEFT_OPERAND JOIN VARIABLES RIGHT_VARIABLES ON RIGHT_VARIABLES.NAME = EXPRESSIONS.RIGHT_OPERAND
