SELECT A.LEFT_OPERAND, A.OPERATOR, A.RIGHT_OPERAND, CASE WHEN A.VALUE1>A.VALUE2 AND A.OPERATOR='>' THEN 'true' WHEN A.VALUE1<A.VALUE2 AND A.OPERATOR='<' THEN 'true' WHEN A.VALUE1=A.VALUE2 AND A.OPERATOR='=' THEN 'true' ELSE 'false' END VALUE FROM (SELECT LEFT_OPERAND, V1.VALUE VALUE1, OPERATOR, RIGHT_OPERAND, V2.VALUE VALUE2 FROM EXPRESSIONS E LEFT JOIN VARIABLES V1 ON E.LEFT_OPERAND=V1.NAME LEFT JOIN VARIABLES V2 ON E.RIGHT_OPERAND=V2.NAME) A

SELECT E.LEFT_OPERAND, E.OPERATOR, E.RIGHT_OPERAND, CASE WHEN (V1.VALUE > V2.VALUE AND E.OPERATOR = '>') OR (V1.VALUE = V2.VALUE AND E.OPERATOR = '=') OR (V1.VALUE < V2.VALUE AND E.OPERATOR = '<') THEN 'true' ELSE 'false' END AS VALUE FROM EXPRESSIONS E JOIN VARIABLES V1 ON E.LEFT_OPERAND = V1.NAME JOIN VARIABLES V2 ON E.RIGHT_OPERAND = V2.NAME

WITH CTE AS (SELECT LEFT_OPERAND, OPERATOR, RIGHT_OPERAND,VALUE AS LEFT_VAL FROM EXPRESSIONS LEFT JOIN VARIABLES ON EXPRESSIONS.LEFT_OPERAND = VARIABLES.NAME ) , CTE2 AS (SELECT LEFT_OPERAND,LEFT_VAL,OPERATOR, RIGHT_OPERAND,VALUE AS RIGHT_VAL FROM CTE LEFT JOIN VARIABLES ON CTE.RIGHT_OPERAND = VARIABLES.NAME ) SELECT LEFT_OPERAND,OPERATOR,RIGHT_OPERAND, CASE WHEN (LEFT_VAL > RIGHT_VAL AND OPERATOR = '>') OR (LEFT_VAL < RIGHT_VAL AND OPERATOR = '<') OR (LEFT_VAL = RIGHT_VAL AND OPERATOR = '=') THEN 'true' ELSE 'false' END AS VALUE FROM CTE2

SELECT LEFT_OPERAND, OPERATOR, RIGHT_OPERAND, CASE WHEN OPERATOR = '=' THEN IF(V.VALUE = V2.VALUE, 'true','false') WHEN OPERATOR = '>' THEN IF(V.VALUE > V2.VALUE, 'true','false') WHEN OPERATOR = '<' THEN IF(V.VALUE < V2.VALUE, 'true','false') END AS VALUE FROM EXPRESSIONS E JOIN VARIABLES V ON E.LEFT_OPERAND = V.NAME JOIN VARIABLES V2 ON E.RIGHT_OPERAND = V2.NAME

SELECT E.LEFT_OPERAND, E.OPERATOR, E.RIGHT_OPERAND, CASE WHEN (E.OPERATOR='>' AND V1.VALUE>V2.VALUE) THEN 'true' WHEN (E.OPERATOR='>' AND V1.VALUE<V2.VALUE) THEN 'false' WHEN (E.OPERATOR='<' AND V1.VALUE<V2.VALUE) THEN 'true' WHEN (E.OPERATOR='<' AND V1.VALUE>V2.VALUE) THEN 'false' WHEN (E.OPERATOR='=' AND V1.VALUE=V2.VALUE) THEN 'true' WHEN (E.OPERATOR='=' AND V1.VALUE!=V2.VALUE) THEN 'false' ELSE 'false' END AS VALUE FROM EXPRESSIONS E , VARIABLES V1, VARIABLES V2 WHERE E.LEFT_OPERAND=V1.NAME AND E.RIGHT_OPERAND =V2.NAME

SELECT T1.LEFT_OPERAND, T1.OPERATOR, T1.RIGHT_OPERAND, CASE WHEN T1.VALUE=1 THEN 'true' ELSE 'false' END AS VALUE FROM ( SELECT E.*, CASE WHEN E.OPERATOR='>' AND (V1.VALUE>V2.VALUE) THEN 1 WHEN E.OPERATOR='<' AND (V1.VALUE<V2.VALUE) THEN 1 WHEN E.OPERATOR='=' AND (V1.VALUE=V2.VALUE) THEN 1 ELSE 0 END AS VALUE FROM EXPRESSIONS E JOIN VARIABLES V1 ON E.LEFT_OPERAND=V1.NAME JOIN VARIABLES V2 ON E.RIGHT_OPERAND=V2.NAME ) T1

SELECT LEFT_OPERAND,OPERATOR,RIGHT_OPERAND, CASE WHEN OPERATOR = '<' AND L.VALUE < R.VALUE THEN 'true' WHEN OPERATOR = '>' AND L.VALUE > R.VALUE THEN 'true' WHEN OPERATOR = '=' AND L.VALUE = R.VALUE THEN 'true' ELSE 'false' END AS VALUE FROM EXPRESSIONS E JOIN VARIABLES L ON E.LEFT_OPERAND = L.NAME JOIN VARIABLES R ON E.RIGHT_OPERAND = R.NAME

SELECT A.*, CASE WHEN OPERATOR = '=' AND B.VALUE = C.VALUE THEN 'true' WHEN OPERATOR = '>' AND B.VALUE > C.VALUE THEN 'true' WHEN OPERATOR = '<' AND B.VALUE < C.VALUE THEN 'true' ELSE 'false' END AS VALUE FROM EXPRESSIONS A JOIN VARIABLES B ON A.LEFT_OPERAND = B.NAME JOIN VARIABLES C ON A.RIGHT_OPERAND = C.NAME

SELECT LEFT_OPERAND, OPERATOR, RIGHT_OPERAND, CASE WHEN OPERATOR = '>' AND V1.VALUE > V2.VALUE THEN 'true' WHEN OPERATOR = '=' AND V1.VALUE = V2.VALUE THEN 'true' WHEN OPERATOR = '<' AND V1.VALUE < V2.VALUE THEN 'true' ELSE 'false' END AS VALUE FROM EXPRESSIONS E LEFT JOIN VARIABLES V1 ON V1.NAME = E.LEFT_OPERAND LEFT JOIN VARIABLES V2 ON V2.NAME = E.RIGHT_OPERAND

SELECT E.LEFT_OPERAND,E.OPERATOR,E.RIGHT_OPERAND, CASE WHEN OPERATOR='<' THEN IF (L_V.VALUE <R_V.VALUE,'true','false') WHEN OPERATOR='>' THEN IF (L_V.VALUE >R_V.VALUE,'true','false') WHEN OPERATOR='=' THEN IF (L_V.VALUE =R_V.VALUE,'true','false') END VALUE FROM EXPRESSIONS E JOIN VARIABLES L_V ON (E.LEFT_OPERAND=L_V.NAME) JOIN VARIABLES R_V ON (E.RIGHT_OPERAND=R_V.NAME)

SELECT LEFT_OPERAND ,OPERATOR ,RIGHT_OPERAND ,CASE WHEN OPERATOR = '<' THEN IF(V1.VALUE < V2.VALUE,'true','false') WHEN OPERATOR = '=' THEN IF(V1.VALUE = V2.VALUE,'true','false') ELSE IF(V1.VALUE > V2.VALUE,'true','false') END AS VALUE FROM EXPRESSIONS E LEFT JOIN VARIABLES V1 ON E.LEFT_OPERAND = V1.NAME LEFT JOIN VARIABLES V2 ON E.RIGHT_OPERAND = V2.NAME

SELECT LEFT_OPERAND,OPERATOR,RIGHT_OPERAND, CASE WHEN OPERATOR='>' AND V1.VALUE > V2.VALUE THEN 'true' WHEN OPERATOR='<' AND V1.VALUE < V2.VALUE THEN 'true' WHEN OPERATOR='=' AND V1.VALUE = V2.VALUE THEN 'true' ELSE 'false' END AS VALUE FROM EXPRESSIONS E INNER JOIN VARIABLES V1 ON E.LEFT_OPERAND = V1.NAME INNER JOIN VARIABLES V2 ON E.RIGHT_OPERAND = V2.NAME

WITH CTE AS ( SELECT LEFT_OPERAND, T2.VALUE AS LEFT_VALUE, OPERATOR, RIGHT_OPERAND, T3.VALUE AS RIGHT_VALUE FROM EXPRESSIONS T1 LEFT JOIN VARIABLES T2 ON T1.LEFT_OPERAND = T2.NAME LEFT JOIN VARIABLES T3 ON T1.RIGHT_OPERAND = T3.NAME ), CTE2 AS ( SELECT LEFT_OPERAND, OPERATOR, RIGHT_OPERAND, CASE WHEN OPERATOR = '>' THEN LEFT_VALUE > RIGHT_VALUE WHEN OPERATOR = '=' THEN LEFT_VALUE = RIGHT_VALUE ELSE LEFT_VALUE < RIGHT_VALUE END AS VALUE FROM CTE ) SELECT LEFT_OPERAND, OPERATOR, RIGHT_OPERAND, CASE WHEN VALUE = 1 THEN 'true' ELSE 'false' END AS VALUE FROM CTE2

SELECT LEFT_OPERAND, OPERATOR, RIGHT_OPERAND, CASE WHEN VALUE = 1 THEN 'true' ELSE 'false' END AS VALUE FROM (SELECT LEFT_OPERAND, OPERATOR, RIGHT_OPERAND, CASE WHEN OPERATOR = '<' THEN V1.VALUE < V2.VALUE WHEN OPERATOR = '>' THEN V1.VALUE > V2.VALUE ELSE V1.VALUE = V2.VALUE END AS VALUE FROM VARIABLES V1, EXPRESSIONS E, VARIABLES V2 WHERE V1.NAME = E.LEFT_OPERAND AND V2.NAME = E.RIGHT_OPERAND) AS T

SELECT E.LEFT_OPERAND,E.OPERATOR,E.RIGHT_OPERAND,CASE WHEN E.OPERATOR='>' AND V1.VALUE>V2.VALUE THEN 'true' WHEN E.OPERATOR='<' AND V1.VALUE<V2.VALUE THEN 'true' WHEN E.OPERATOR='=' AND V1.VALUE=V2.VALUE THEN 'true' ELSE 'false' END AS VALUE FROM EXPRESSIONS E LEFT JOIN VARIABLES V1 ON (E.LEFT_OPERAND=V1.NAME) LEFT JOIN VARIABLES V2 ON (E.RIGHT_OPERAND=V2.NAME)

SELECT E.LEFT_OPERAND, E.OPERATOR, E.RIGHT_OPERAND, CASE WHEN E.OPERATOR = '<' AND V1.VALUE<V2.VALUE THEN 'true' WHEN E.OPERATOR = '>' AND V1.VALUE>V2.VALUE THEN 'true' WHEN E.OPERATOR = '=' AND V1.VALUE=V2.VALUE THEN 'true' ELSE 'false' END AS VALUE FROM EXPRESSIONS AS E JOIN VARIABLES AS V1 ON E.LEFT_OPERAND = V1.NAME JOIN VARIABLES AS V2 ON E.RIGHT_OPERAND = V2.NAME

SELECT V.LEFT_OPERAND, V.OPERATOR, V.RIGHT_OPERAND, CASE WHEN E1.VALUE<E2.VALUE AND OPERATOR = '<' THEN 'true' WHEN E1.VALUE>E2.VALUE AND OPERATOR = '>' THEN 'true' WHEN E1.VALUE=E2.VALUE AND OPERATOR = '=' THEN 'true' ELSE 'false' END AS VALUE FROM EXPRESSIONS V JOIN VARIABLES E1 ON E1.NAME=V.LEFT_OPERAND JOIN VARIABLES E2 ON E2.NAME =V.RIGHT_OPERAND

SELECT E.LEFT_OPERAND, E.OPERATOR, E.RIGHT_OPERAND, (CASE WHEN V1.VALUE > V2.VALUE AND E.OPERATOR = '>' THEN 'true' WHEN V1.VALUE = V2.VALUE AND E.OPERATOR = '=' THEN 'true' WHEN V1.VALUE < V2.VALUE AND E.OPERATOR = '<' THEN 'true' ELSE 'false' END) AS VALUE FROM EXPRESSIONS AS E JOIN VARIABLES AS V1 ON E.LEFT_OPERAND = V1.NAME JOIN VARIABLES AS V2 ON E.RIGHT_OPERAND = V2.NAME

SELECT T.LEFT_OPERAND, T.OPERATOR, T.RIGHT_OPERAND, CASE WHEN T.OPERATOR = '=' THEN IF(T.LEFT_VALUE = T.RIGHT_VALUE, 'true', 'false') WHEN T.OPERATOR = '>' THEN IF(T.LEFT_VALUE > T.RIGHT_VALUE, 'true', 'false') WHEN T.OPERATOR = '<' THEN IF(T.LEFT_VALUE < T.RIGHT_VALUE, 'true', 'false') END AS VALUE FROM ( SELECT E.*, V.VALUE AS LEFT_VALUE, V2.VALUE AS RIGHT_VALUE FROM EXPRESSIONS AS E JOIN VARIABLES AS V ON E.LEFT_OPERAND = V.NAME JOIN VARIABLES AS V2 ON E.RIGHT_OPERAND = V2.NAME ) AS T

SELECT E.LEFT_OPERAND, E.OPERATOR, E.RIGHT_OPERAND, IF( IF( E.OPERATOR = '=', L.VALUE = R.VALUE, IF( E.OPERATOR = '>', L.VALUE > R.VALUE, L.VALUE < R.VALUE ) ), 'true', 'false' ) AS VALUE FROM EXPRESSIONS E LEFT JOIN VARIABLES L ON (E.LEFT_OPERAND = L.NAME) LEFT JOIN VARIABLES R ON (E.RIGHT_OPERAND = R.NAME)

SELECT LEFT_OPERAND, OPERATOR, RIGHT_OPERAND, CASE WHEN OPERATOR = '>' AND V1.VALUE > V2.VALUE THEN 'true' WHEN OPERATOR = '<' AND V1.VALUE < V2.VALUE THEN 'true' WHEN OPERATOR = '=' AND V1.VALUE = V2.VALUE THEN 'true' ELSE 'false' END AS VALUE FROM EXPRESSIONS E INNER JOIN VARIABLES V1 ON V1.NAME = E.LEFT_OPERAND INNER JOIN VARIABLES V2 ON V2.NAME = E.RIGHT_OPERAND

SELECT E.LEFT_OPERAND, E.OPERATOR, E.RIGHT_OPERAND, ( CASE WHEN E.OPERATOR = '<' AND V1.VALUE < V2.VALUE THEN 'true' WHEN E.OPERATOR = '=' AND V1.VALUE = V2.VALUE THEN 'true' WHEN E.OPERATOR = '>' AND V1.VALUE > V2.VALUE THEN 'true' ELSE 'false' END ) AS VALUE FROM EXPRESSIONS E INNER JOIN VARIABLES V1 ON E.LEFT_OPERAND = V1.NAME INNER JOIN VARIABLES V2 ON E.RIGHT_OPERAND = V2.NAME

WITH T AS ( SELECT E.LEFT_OPERAND, E.OPERATOR, E.RIGHT_OPERAND, V.VALUE AS LEFT_VALUE, VV.VALUE AS RIGHT_VALUE, V.VALUE-VV.VALUE AS DIFF FROM EXPRESSIONS E LEFT JOIN VARIABLES V ON E.LEFT_OPERAND=V.NAME LEFT JOIN VARIABLES VV ON E.RIGHT_OPERAND=VV.NAME ) SELECT LEFT_OPERAND, OPERATOR, RIGHT_OPERAND, IF(CASE OPERATOR WHEN '<' THEN (DIFF<0) WHEN '>' THEN (DIFF>0) WHEN '=' THEN (DIFF=0) END, 'true', 'false') AS VALUE FROM T

SELECT LEFT_OPERAND, OPERATOR, RIGHT_OPERAND, CASE WHEN OPERATOR='>' THEN IF(LEFT_VALUE>RIGHT_VALUE,'true','false') WHEN OPERATOR='<' THEN IF(LEFT_VALUE<RIGHT_VALUE,'true','false') ELSE IF(LEFT_VALUE=RIGHT_VALUE,'true','false') END AS VALUE FROM (SELECT LEFT_OPERAND, OPERATOR, RIGHT_OPERAND, SUM(CASE WHEN LEFT_OPERAND=NAME THEN VALUE ELSE NULL END) AS LEFT_VALUE, SUM(CASE WHEN RIGHT_OPERAND=NAME THEN VALUE ELSE NULL END) AS RIGHT_VALUE FROM EXPRESSIONS E JOIN VARIABLES V ON E.LEFT_OPERAND=NAME OR E.RIGHT_OPERAND=NAME GROUP BY LEFT_OPERAND, OPERATOR, RIGHT_OPERAND)T1

SELECT LEFT_OPERAND, OPERATOR, RIGHT_OPERAND, CASE WHEN (L-R>0 AND OPERATOR='>') OR(L=R AND OPERATOR='=') OR(L-R<0 AND OPERATOR='<') THEN 'true' ELSE 'false' END AS VALUE FROM( SELECT E.LEFT_OPERAND, E.OPERATOR, E.RIGHT_OPERAND, V1.VALUE L, V2.VALUE R FROM EXPRESSIONS E LEFT JOIN VARIABLES V1 ON E.LEFT_OPERAND = V1.NAME LEFT JOIN VARIABLES V2 ON E.RIGHT_OPERAND = V2.NAME) T

SELECT EXPRESSIONS.*, ( CASE WHEN EXPRESSIONS.OPERATOR = '<' AND V1.VALUE < V2.VALUE THEN 'true' WHEN EXPRESSIONS.OPERATOR = '=' AND V1.VALUE = V2.VALUE THEN 'true' WHEN EXPRESSIONS.OPERATOR = '>' AND V1.VALUE > V2.VALUE THEN 'true' ELSE 'false' END ) AS VALUE FROM EXPRESSIONS JOIN VARIABLES V1 ON EXPRESSIONS.LEFT_OPERAND = V1.NAME JOIN VARIABLES V2 ON EXPRESSIONS.RIGHT_OPERAND = V2.NAME

SELECT E.*, CASE WHEN OPERATOR='>' AND V1.VALUE>V2.VALUE OR OPERATOR='=' AND V1.VALUE=V2.VALUE OR OPERATOR='<' AND V1.VALUE<V2.VALUE THEN 'true' ELSE 'false' END AS VALUE FROM EXPRESSIONS E LEFT JOIN VARIABLES V1 ON E.LEFT_OPERAND = V1.NAME LEFT JOIN VARIABLES V2 ON E.RIGHT_OPERAND = V2.NAME

SELECT E.LEFT_OPERAND, E.OPERATOR, E.RIGHT_OPERAND, CASE WHEN E.OPERATOR = '>' AND V1.VALUE > V2.VALUE THEN 'true' WHEN E.OPERATOR = '=' AND V1.VALUE = V2.VALUE THEN 'true' WHEN E.OPERATOR = '<' AND V1.VALUE < V2.VALUE THEN 'true' ELSE 'false' END AS VALUE FROM EXPRESSIONS E JOIN VARIABLES V1 ON V1.NAME = E.LEFT_OPERAND JOIN VARIABLES V2 ON V2.NAME = E.RIGHT_OPERAND

SELECT LEFT_OPERAND, OPERATOR, RIGHT_OPERAND, CASE WHEN OPERATOR = '>' AND LEFT_VARS.VALUE > RIGHT_VARS.VALUE THEN 'true' WHEN OPERATOR = '<' AND LEFT_VARS.VALUE < RIGHT_VARS.VALUE THEN 'true' WHEN OPERATOR = '=' AND LEFT_VARS.VALUE = RIGHT_VARS.VALUE THEN 'true' ELSE 'false' END VALUE FROM EXPRESSIONS LEFT JOIN VARIABLES LEFT_VARS ON LEFT_VARS.NAME = LEFT_OPERAND LEFT JOIN VARIABLES RIGHT_VARS ON RIGHT_VARS.NAME = RIGHT_OPERAND

SELECT LEFT_OPERAND,OPERATOR,RIGHT_OPERAND, CASE WHEN LEFT_SIDE > RIGHT_SIDE AND OPERATOR = '>' THEN 'true' WHEN LEFT_SIDE = RIGHT_SIDE AND OPERATOR = '=' THEN 'true' WHEN LEFT_SIDE < RIGHT_SIDE AND OPERATOR = '<' THEN 'true' ELSE 'false' END AS VALUE FROM (SELECT LEFT_OPERAND,OPERATOR,RIGHT_OPERAND,V.VALUE AS LEFT_SIDE, A.VALUE AS RIGHT_SIDE FROM EXPRESSIONS E LEFT JOIN VARIABLES V ON E.LEFT_OPERAND = V.NAME LEFT JOIN VARIABLES A ON A.NAME = E.RIGHT_OPERAND) T1

SELECT EE.*, (CASE WHEN EE.OPERATOR = '>' AND V1.VALUE > V2.VALUE THEN 'true' WHEN EE.OPERATOR = '=' AND V1.VALUE = V2.VALUE THEN 'true' WHEN EE.OPERATOR = '<' AND V1.VALUE < V2.VALUE THEN 'true' ELSE 'false' END) AS VALUE FROM EXPRESSIONS AS EE LEFT JOIN VARIABLES AS V1 ON EE.LEFT_OPERAND = V1.NAME LEFT JOIN VARIABLES AS V2 ON EE.RIGHT_OPERAND = V2.NAME

SELECT LEFT_OPERAND , OPERATOR , RIGHT_OPERAND , CASE WHEN LEFT_X.VALUE > RIGHT_Y.VALUE AND OPERATOR = '>' THEN 'true' WHEN LEFT_X.VALUE = RIGHT_Y.VALUE AND OPERATOR = '=' THEN 'true' WHEN LEFT_X.VALUE < RIGHT_Y.VALUE AND OPERATOR = '<' THEN 'true' ELSE 'false' END AS VALUE FROM EXPRESSIONS LEFT JOIN VARIABLES AS LEFT_X ON EXPRESSIONS.LEFT_OPERAND = LEFT_X.NAME LEFT JOIN VARIABLES AS RIGHT_Y ON EXPRESSIONS.RIGHT_OPERAND = RIGHT_Y.NAME

SELECT LEFT_OPERAND, OPERATOR, RIGHT_OPERAND, CASE WHEN (V1.VALUE > V2.VALUE AND OPERATOR = '>') OR (V1.VALUE < V2.VALUE AND OPERATOR = '<') OR (V1.VALUE = V2.VALUE AND OPERATOR = '=') THEN 'true' ELSE 'false' END AS VALUE FROM VARIABLES V1 JOIN EXPRESSIONS E JOIN VARIABLES V2 ON E.LEFT_OPERAND = V1.NAME AND E.RIGHT_OPERAND = V2.NAME

WITH T1 AS( SELECT E.LEFT_OPERAND, V1.VALUE AS LEFT_OP, E.OPERATOR, E.RIGHT_OPERAND, V2.VALUE AS RIGHT_OP FROM EXPRESSIONS E LEFT JOIN VARIABLES V1 ON E.LEFT_OPERAND = V1.NAME LEFT JOIN VARIABLES V2 ON E.RIGHT_OPERAND = V2.NAME ) SELECT LEFT_OPERAND, OPERATOR, RIGHT_OPERAND, CASE WHEN OPERATOR = '=' AND LEFT_OP = RIGHT_OP THEN 'true' WHEN OPERATOR = '>' AND LEFT_OP > RIGHT_OP THEN 'true' WHEN OPERATOR = '<' AND LEFT_OP < RIGHT_OP THEN 'true' ELSE 'false' END AS VALUE FROM T1

WITH CTE AS ( SELECT LEFT_OPERAND, T2.VALUE AS LEFT_VALUE, OPERATOR, RIGHT_OPERAND, T3.VALUE AS RIGHT_VALUE FROM EXPRESSIONS T1 LEFT JOIN VARIABLES T2 ON T1.LEFT_OPERAND = T2.NAME LEFT JOIN VARIABLES T3 ON T1.RIGHT_OPERAND = T3.NAME ) SELECT LEFT_OPERAND, OPERATOR, RIGHT_OPERAND, CASE WHEN OPERATOR = '>' AND LEFT_VALUE > RIGHT_VALUE THEN 'true' WHEN OPERATOR = '>' AND LEFT_VALUE <= RIGHT_VALUE THEN 'false' WHEN OPERATOR = '=' AND LEFT_VALUE = RIGHT_VALUE THEN 'true' WHEN OPERATOR = '=' AND LEFT_VALUE != RIGHT_VALUE THEN 'false' WHEN OPERATOR = '<' AND LEFT_VALUE < RIGHT_VALUE THEN 'true' ELSE 'false' END AS VALUE FROM CTE

SELECT A.LEFT_OPERAND, A.OPERATOR, A.RIGHT_OPERAND, ( CASE WHEN A.OPERATOR = '>' AND B.VALUE > C.VALUE THEN 'true' WHEN A.OPERATOR = '<' AND B.VALUE < C.VALUE THEN 'true' WHEN A.OPERATOR = '=' AND B.VALUE = C.VALUE THEN 'true' ELSE 'false' END ) VALUE FROM EXPRESSIONS A LEFT JOIN VARIABLES B ON A.LEFT_OPERAND = B.NAME LEFT JOIN VARIABLES C ON A.RIGHT_OPERAND = C.NAME

SELECT E.LEFT_OPERAND, E.OPERATOR, E.RIGHT_OPERAND, CASE WHEN E.OPERATOR = '>' AND V.VALUE > V2.VALUE THEN 'true' WHEN E.OPERATOR = '<' AND V.VALUE < V2.VALUE THEN 'true' WHEN E.OPERATOR = '=' AND V.VALUE = V2.VALUE THEN 'true' ELSE 'false' END AS VALUE FROM EXPRESSIONS E JOIN VARIABLES V ON E.LEFT_OPERAND = V.NAME JOIN VARIABLES V2 ON E.RIGHT_OPERAND = V2.NAME

SELECT LEFT_OPERAND, OPERATOR, RIGHT_OPERAND, CASE WHEN LEFT_VALUE > RIGHT_VALUE AND OPERATOR = '>' THEN 'true' WHEN LEFT_VALUE < RIGHT_VALUE AND OPERATOR = '<' THEN 'true' WHEN LEFT_VALUE = RIGHT_VALUE AND OPERATOR = '=' THEN 'true' ELSE 'false' END AS VALUE FROM ( SELECT A.VALUE AS LEFT_VALUE, B.VALUE AS RIGHT_VALUE, LEFT_OPERAND, OPERATOR, RIGHT_OPERAND FROM VARIABLES AS A JOIN EXPRESSIONS ON A.NAME = EXPRESSIONS.LEFT_OPERAND JOIN VARIABLES AS B ON B.NAME = EXPRESSIONS.RIGHT_OPERAND ) AS SUB

SELECT VL.NAME LEFT_OPERAND, E.OPERATOR OPERATOR, VR.NAME RIGHT_OPERAND, CASE WHEN OPERATOR = '<' THEN CASE WHEN VL.VALUE < VR.VALUE THEN 'true' ELSE 'false' END WHEN OPERATOR = '>' THEN CASE WHEN VL.VALUE > VR.VALUE THEN 'true' ELSE 'false' END WHEN OPERATOR = '=' THEN CASE WHEN VL.VALUE = VR.VALUE THEN 'true' ELSE 'false' END ELSE NULL END VALUE FROM EXPRESSIONS E JOIN VARIABLES VR ON E.RIGHT_OPERAND = VR.NAME JOIN VARIABLES VL ON E.LEFT_OPERAND = VL.NAME

SELECT LEFT_OPERAND, OPERATOR, RIGHT_OPERAND, CASE WHEN OPERATOR = '=' AND LEFT_OP = RIGHT_OP THEN 'true' WHEN OPERATOR = '>' AND LEFT_OP > RIGHT_OP THEN 'true' WHEN OPERATOR = '<' AND LEFT_OP < RIGHT_OP THEN 'true' ELSE 'false' END AS VALUE FROM ( SELECT E.LEFT_OPERAND, V1.VALUE AS LEFT_OP, E.OPERATOR, E.RIGHT_OPERAND, V2.VALUE AS RIGHT_OP FROM EXPRESSIONS AS E INNER JOIN VARIABLES AS V1 ON E.LEFT_OPERAND = V1.NAME INNER JOIN VARIABLES AS V2 ON E.RIGHT_OPERAND = V2.NAME ) AS A

SELECT LEFT_OPERAND, E.OPERATOR, RIGHT_OPERAND, ( CASE WHEN E.OPERATOR = '>' AND V1.VALUE > V2.VALUE THEN 'true' WHEN E.OPERATOR = '=' AND V1.VALUE = V2.VALUE THEN 'true' WHEN E.OPERATOR = '<' AND V1.VALUE < V2.VALUE THEN 'true' ELSE 'false' END ) VALUE FROM EXPRESSIONS E JOIN VARIABLES V1 ON E.LEFT_OPERAND = V1.NAME JOIN VARIABLES V2 ON E.RIGHT_OPERAND = V2.NAME

WITH T1 AS ( SELECT LEFT_OPERAND, OPERATOR, RIGHT_OPERAND, V.VALUE AS LEFT_VALUE FROM EXPRESSIONS E LEFT JOIN VARIABLES V ON E.LEFT_OPERAND = V.NAME ) , T2 AS ( SELECT LEFT_OPERAND, OPERATOR, RIGHT_OPERAND, LEFT_VALUE, V.VALUE AS RIGHT_VALUE FROM T1 LEFT JOIN VARIABLES V ON T1.RIGHT_OPERAND = V.NAME ) SELECT LEFT_OPERAND, OPERATOR, RIGHT_OPERAND, CASE WHEN OPERATOR = '>' AND LEFT_VALUE > RIGHT_VALUE THEN 'true' WHEN OPERATOR = '<' AND LEFT_VALUE < RIGHT_VALUE THEN 'true' WHEN OPERATOR = '=' AND LEFT_VALUE = RIGHT_VALUE THEN 'true' ELSE 'false' END AS VALUE FROM T2

SELECT E.*, CASE WHEN OPERATOR = '>' AND V1.VALUE > V2.VALUE THEN 'true' WHEN OPERATOR = '>' AND V1.VALUE <= V2.VALUE THEN 'false' WHEN OPERATOR = '<' AND V1.VALUE < V2.VALUE THEN 'true' WHEN OPERATOR = '<' AND V1.VALUE >= V2.VALUE THEN 'false' WHEN OPERATOR = '=' AND V1.VALUE = V2.VALUE THEN 'true' WHEN OPERATOR = '=' AND V1.VALUE != V2.VALUE THEN 'false' END AS VALUE FROM EXPRESSIONS AS E JOIN VARIABLES AS V1 ON E.LEFT_OPERAND = V1.NAME JOIN VARIABLES AS V2 ON E.RIGHT_OPERAND = V2.NAME

SELECT E.LEFT_OPERAND, E.OPERATOR, E.RIGHT_OPERAND, CASE WHEN V_LEFT.VALUE < V_RIGHT.VALUE AND E.OPERATOR = '<' THEN 'true' WHEN V_LEFT.VALUE > V_RIGHT.VALUE AND E.OPERATOR = '>' THEN 'true' WHEN V_LEFT.VALUE = V_RIGHT.VALUE AND E.OPERATOR = '=' THEN 'true' ELSE 'false' END AS VALUE FROM EXPRESSIONS E LEFT JOIN VARIABLES V_LEFT ON E.LEFT_OPERAND = V_LEFT.NAME LEFT JOIN VARIABLES V_RIGHT ON E.RIGHT_OPERAND = V_RIGHT.NAME

SELECT LEFT_OPERAND, OPERATOR, RIGHT_OPERAND, (CASE WHEN OPERATOR = '>' THEN IF(T.L_VALUE > T.R_VALUE, 'true','false') WHEN OPERATOR = '<' THEN IF (T.L_VALUE < T.R_VALUE, 'true','false') WHEN OPERATOR = '=' THEN IF (T.L_VALUE = T.R_VALUE, 'true','false') END) AS VALUE FROM (SELECT LEFT_OPERAND, V1.VALUE AS L_VALUE, OPERATOR, RIGHT_OPERAND, V2.VALUE AS R_VALUE FROM EXPRESSIONS E LEFT JOIN VARIABLES V1 ON V1.NAME = E.LEFT_OPERAND LEFT JOIN VARIABLES V2 ON V2.NAME = E.RIGHT_OPERAND)T

SELECT E.LEFT_OPERAND , E.OPERATOR , E.RIGHT_OPERAND , CASE WHEN E.OPERATOR = '>' AND T1.VALUE > T2.VALUE THEN 'true' WHEN E.OPERATOR = '=' AND T1.VALUE = T2.VALUE THEN 'true' WHEN E.OPERATOR = '<' AND T1.VALUE < T2.VALUE THEN 'true' ELSE 'false' END AS VALUE FROM EXPRESSIONS E LEFT JOIN VARIABLES T1 ON E.LEFT_OPERAND = T1.NAME LEFT JOIN VARIABLES T2 ON E.RIGHT_OPERAND = T2.NAME

SELECT LEFT_OPERAND, OPERATOR, RIGHT_OPERAND, (CASE OPERATOR WHEN '>' THEN CASE WHEN VL.VALUE > VR.VALUE THEN 'true' ELSE 'false' END WHEN '<' THEN CASE WHEN VL.VALUE < VR.VALUE THEN 'true' ELSE 'false' END WHEN '=' THEN CASE WHEN VL.VALUE = VR.VALUE THEN 'true' ELSE 'false' END END ) AS VALUE FROM EXPRESSIONS E,VARIABLES VL , VARIABLES VR WHERE E.LEFT_OPERAND = VL.NAME AND E.RIGHT_OPERAND = VR.NAME

SELECT E.LEFT_OPERAND, E.OPERATOR, E.RIGHT_OPERAND, CASE WHEN (V1.VALUE > V2.VALUE) AND (E.OPERATOR = '>') THEN 'true' WHEN (V1.VALUE < V2.VALUE) AND (E.OPERATOR = '<') THEN 'true' WHEN (V1.VALUE = V2.VALUE) AND (E.OPERATOR = '=') THEN 'true' ELSE 'false' END AS VALUE FROM EXPRESSIONS E LEFT JOIN VARIABLES V1 ON E.LEFT_OPERAND = V1.NAME LEFT JOIN VARIABLES V2 ON E.RIGHT_OPERAND = V2.NAME

WITH VAR_EXPANDED AS ( SELECT A.NAME AS LEFT_OPERAND, '>' AS OPERATOR, B.NAME AS RIGHT_OPERAND, CASE WHEN A.VALUE > B.VALUE THEN 'true' ELSE 'false' END AS EVALUATED_VALUE FROM VARIABLES A JOIN VARIABLES B UNION SELECT A.NAME AS LEFT_OPERAND, '<' AS OPERATOR, B.NAME AS RIGHT_OPERAND, CASE WHEN A.VALUE < B.VALUE THEN 'true' ELSE 'false' END AS EVALUATED_VALUE FROM VARIABLES A JOIN VARIABLES B UNION SELECT A.NAME AS LEFT_OPERAND, '=' AS OPERATOR, B.NAME AS RIGHT_OPERAND, CASE WHEN A.VALUE = B.VALUE THEN 'true' ELSE 'false' END AS EVALUATED_VALUE FROM VARIABLES A JOIN VARIABLES B ) SELECT E.*, V.EVALUATED_VALUE AS VALUE FROM EXPRESSIONS E JOIN VAR_EXPANDED V ON E.LEFT_OPERAND = V.LEFT_OPERAND AND E.OPERATOR = V.OPERATOR AND E.RIGHT_OPERAND = V.RIGHT_OPERAND

SELECT LEFT_OPERAND, OPERATOR, RIGHT_OPERAND, IF( CASE WHEN OPERATOR = '=' THEN L.VALUE = R.VALUE WHEN OPERATOR = '>' THEN L.VALUE > R.VALUE ELSE L.VALUE < R.VALUE END, 'true', 'false') AS VALUE FROM EXPRESSIONS E LEFT JOIN VARIABLES L ON E.LEFT_OPERAND = L.NAME LEFT JOIN VARIABLES R ON E.RIGHT_OPERAND = R.NAME

SELECT LEFT_OPERAND,OPERATOR,RIGHT_OPERAND, CASE WHEN OPERATOR='>' THEN IF(LEFT_VALUE>RIGHT_VALUE,'true','false') WHEN OPERATOR='=' THEN IF(LEFT_VALUE=RIGHT_VALUE,'true','false') WHEN OPERATOR='<' THEN IF(LEFT_VALUE<RIGHT_VALUE,'true','false') END AS VALUE FROM (SELECT LEFT_OPERAND,OPERATOR,RIGHT_OPERAND,V1.VALUE AS LEFT_VALUE,V2.VALUE AS RIGHT_VALUE FROM EXPRESSIONS JOIN VARIABLES V1 ON EXPRESSIONS.LEFT_OPERAND = V1.NAME JOIN VARIABLES V2 ON EXPRESSIONS.RIGHT_OPERAND = V2.NAME) AS TMP

SELECT LEFT_OPERAND, OPERATOR, RIGHT_OPERAND, CASE WHEN OPERATOR = '<' AND LV.VALUE < RV.VALUE THEN 'true' WHEN OPERATOR = '>' AND LV.VALUE > RV.VALUE THEN 'true' WHEN OPERATOR = '=' AND LV.VALUE = RV.VALUE THEN 'true' ELSE 'false' END AS VALUE FROM EXPRESSIONS JOIN VARIABLES LV ON LEFT_OPERAND = LV.NAME JOIN VARIABLES RV ON RIGHT_OPERAND = RV.NAME

SELECT T2.LEFT_OPERAND, T2.OPERATOR ,T2.RIGHT_OPERAND, CASE WHEN OPERATOR = '=' AND VALUEDIFF = 0 THEN 'true' WHEN OPERATOR = '>' AND VALUEDIFF > 0 THEN 'true' WHEN OPERATOR = '<' AND VALUEDIFF < 0 THEN 'true' ELSE 'false' END AS VALUE FROM (SELECT T.*, C.VALUE AS RIGHT_VALUE, LEFT_VALUE-C.VALUE AS VALUEDIFF FROM (SELECT A.LEFT_OPERAND,B.VALUE AS LEFT_VALUE, A.OPERATOR,A.RIGHT_OPERAND FROM EXPRESSIONS A INNER JOIN VARIABLES B ON A.LEFT_OPERAND = B.NAME ) T INNER JOIN VARIABLES C ON T.RIGHT_OPERAND = C.NAME) T2

SELECT A.LEFT_OPERAND, A.OPERATOR, A.RIGHT_OPERAND, CASE WHEN A.OPERATOR = '>' AND B.VALUE > C.VALUE THEN 'true' WHEN A.OPERATOR = '<' AND B.VALUE < C.VALUE THEN 'true' WHEN A.OPERATOR = '=' AND B.VALUE = C.VALUE THEN 'true' ELSE 'false' END AS VALUE FROM EXPRESSIONS A JOIN VARIABLES B ON A.LEFT_OPERAND = B.NAME JOIN VARIABLES C ON C.NAME = A.RIGHT_OPERAND

WITH CTE AS (SELECT E.*, V.VALUE L, V2.VALUE R FROM EXPRESSIONS E JOIN VARIABLES V ON E.LEFT_OPERAND = V.NAME JOIN VARIABLES V2 ON E.RIGHT_OPERAND=V2.NAME) SELECT LEFT_OPERAND, OPERATOR, RIGHT_OPERAND, (CASE WHEN L<R AND OPERATOR='<' THEN 'true' WHEN L=R AND OPERATOR='=' THEN 'true' WHEN L>R AND OPERATOR='>' THEN 'true' ELSE 'false' END) VALUE FROM CTE

SELECT E.* , CASE WHEN E.OPERATOR = '>' AND V1.VALUE > V2.VALUE THEN 'true' WHEN E.OPERATOR = '=' AND V1.VALUE = V2.VALUE THEN 'true' WHEN E.OPERATOR = '<' AND V1.VALUE < V2.VALUE THEN 'true' ELSE 'false' END AS VALUE FROM EXPRESSIONS E JOIN VARIABLES V1 ON E.LEFT_OPERAND = V1.NAME JOIN VARIABLES V2 ON E.RIGHT_OPERAND = V2.NAME

WITH TEMP AS(SELECT E.LEFT_OPERAND,V1.VALUE AS LV ,E.OPERATOR,E.RIGHT_OPERAND,V2.VALUE AS RV FROM EXPRESSIONS E LEFT OUTER JOIN VARIABLES V1 ON E.LEFT_OPERAND = V1.NAME LEFT OUTER JOIN VARIABLES V2 ON E.RIGHT_OPERAND=V2.NAME) SELECT LEFT_OPERAND, OPERATOR, RIGHT_OPERAND, CASE WHEN OPERATOR = '>' AND LV>RV THEN 'true' WHEN OPERATOR = '<' AND LV<RV THEN 'true' WHEN OPERATOR = '=' AND LV=RV THEN 'true' ELSE 'false' END AS VALUE FROM TEMP

SELECT E.* , (CASE WHEN E.OPERATOR = '>' AND V1.VALUE > V2.VALUE THEN 'true' WHEN E.OPERATOR = '=' AND V1.VALUE = V2.VALUE THEN 'true' WHEN E.OPERATOR = '<' AND V1.VALUE < V2.VALUE THEN 'true' ELSE 'false' END ) AS VALUE FROM EXPRESSIONS E JOIN VARIABLES V1 ON E.LEFT_OPERAND = V1.NAME JOIN VARIABLES V2 ON E.RIGHT_OPERAND = V2.NAME

SELECT LEFT_OPERAND, OPERATOR, RIGHT_OPERAND, CASE WHEN OPERATOR = '>' THEN IF(V1.VALUE > V2.VALUE, 'true', 'false') WHEN OPERATOR = '=' THEN IF(V1.VALUE = V2.VALUE, 'true', 'false') ELSE IF(V1.VALUE < V2.VALUE, 'true', 'false') END AS VALUE FROM EXPRESSIONS JOIN VARIABLES V1 ON V1.NAME = LEFT_OPERAND JOIN VARIABLES V2 ON V2.NAME = RIGHT_OPERAND

SELECT E.LEFT_OPERAND, E.OPERATOR, E.RIGHT_OPERAND, CASE WHEN E.OPERATOR = '=' THEN IF(V.VALUE = V1.VALUE, 'true', 'false') WHEN E.OPERATOR = '>' THEN IF(V.VALUE > V1.VALUE, 'true', 'false') WHEN E.OPERATOR = '<' THEN IF(V.VALUE < V1.VALUE, 'true', 'false') END VALUE FROM EXPRESSIONS E LEFT JOIN VARIABLES V ON V.NAME = E.LEFT_OPERAND LEFT JOIN VARIABLES V1 ON V1.NAME = E.RIGHT_OPERAND

SELECT LEFT_OPERAND, OPERATOR, RIGHT_OPERAND, CASE WHEN OPERATOR = '>' THEN IF(L.VALUE > R.VALUE, 'true', 'false') WHEN OPERATOR = '<' THEN IF(L.VALUE < R.VALUE, 'true', 'false') ELSE IF(L.VALUE = R.VALUE, 'true', 'false') END VALUE FROM EXPRESSIONS INNER JOIN VARIABLES L ON LEFT_OPERAND = L.NAME INNER JOIN VARIABLES R ON RIGHT_OPERAND = R.NAME

SELECT LEFT_OPERAND, OPERATOR, RIGHT_OPERAND, CASE WHEN OPERATOR = '=' THEN IF(V1.VALUE = V2.VALUE, 'true', 'false') WHEN OPERATOR = '<' THEN IF(V1.VALUE < V2.VALUE, 'true', 'false') WHEN OPERATOR = '>' THEN IF(V1.VALUE > V2.VALUE, 'true', 'false') END AS VALUE FROM EXPRESSIONS JOIN VARIABLES V1 ON LEFT_OPERAND = V1.NAME JOIN VARIABLES V2 ON RIGHT_OPERAND = V2.NAME

SELECT G.LEFT_OPERAND, G.OPERATOR, G.RIGHT_OPERAND, CASE WHEN G.OPERATOR = '=' THEN IF(G.LEFT_VALUE = G.RIGHT_VALUE, 'true', 'false') WHEN G.OPERATOR = '>' THEN IF(G.LEFT_VALUE > G.RIGHT_VALUE, 'true', 'false') WHEN G.OPERATOR = '<' THEN IF(G.LEFT_VALUE < G.RIGHT_VALUE, 'true', 'false') END AS VALUE FROM ( SELECT E.*, V.VALUE AS LEFT_VALUE, V2.VALUE AS RIGHT_VALUE FROM EXPRESSIONS AS E JOIN VARIABLES AS V ON E.LEFT_OPERAND = V.NAME JOIN VARIABLES AS V2 ON E.RIGHT_OPERAND = V2.NAME ) AS G

WITH TMP AS ( SELECT E.LEFT_OPERAND, V1.VALUE AS LEFT_VALUE, E.OPERATOR, E.RIGHT_OPERAND, V2.VALUE AS RIGHT_VALUE FROM EXPRESSIONS AS E LEFT JOIN VARIABLES AS V1 ON E.LEFT_OPERAND = V1.NAME LEFT JOIN VARIABLES AS V2 ON E.RIGHT_OPERAND = V2.NAME ) SELECT T.LEFT_OPERAND, T.OPERATOR, T.RIGHT_OPERAND, ( CASE WHEN T.OPERATOR = '<' AND T.LEFT_VALUE < T.RIGHT_VALUE THEN 'true' WHEN T.OPERATOR = '=' AND T.LEFT_VALUE = T.RIGHT_VALUE THEN 'true' WHEN T.OPERATOR = '>' AND T.LEFT_VALUE > T.RIGHT_VALUE THEN 'true' ELSE 'false' END ) AS VALUE FROM TMP AS T

SELECT E.LEFT_OPERAND, E.OPERATOR, E.RIGHT_OPERAND, (CASE WHEN OPERATOR='>' AND A.VALUE>B.VALUE THEN 'true' WHEN OPERATOR='<' AND A.VALUE<B.VALUE THEN 'true' WHEN OPERATOR='=' AND A.VALUE=B.VALUE THEN 'true' ELSE 'false' END ) AS VALUE FROM EXPRESSIONS E LEFT JOIN VARIABLES A ON E.LEFT_OPERAND=A.NAME LEFT JOIN VARIABLES B ON E.RIGHT_OPERAND=B.NAME

SELECT E.LEFT_OPERAND, E.OPERATOR, E.RIGHT_OPERAND, CASE WHEN (E.OPERATOR = '>') AND V1.VALUE > V2.VALUE THEN 'true' WHEN (E.OPERATOR = '<') AND V1.VALUE < V2.VALUE THEN 'true' WHEN (E.OPERATOR = '=') AND V1.VALUE = V2.VALUE THEN 'true' ELSE 'false' END AS VALUE FROM EXPRESSIONS E JOIN VARIABLES V1 ON E.LEFT_OPERAND = V1.NAME JOIN VARIABLES V2 ON E.RIGHT_OPERAND = V2.NAME

WITH VARIABLES_JOIN AS ( SELECT LEFT_OPERAND , OPERATOR , RIGHT_OPERAND, B.VALUE AS LEFT_VALUE, C.VALUE AS RIGHT_VALUE FROM EXPRESSIONS A JOIN VARIABLES B ON A.LEFT_OPERAND=B.NAME JOIN VARIABLES C ON A.RIGHT_OPERAND =C.NAME ) SELECT LEFT_OPERAND , OPERATOR , RIGHT_OPERAND, CASE WHEN OPERATOR = '=' THEN CASE WHEN LEFT_VALUE=RIGHT_VALUE THEN 'true' ELSE 'false' END WHEN OPERATOR = '>' THEN CASE WHEN LEFT_VALUE>RIGHT_VALUE THEN 'true' ELSE 'false' END WHEN OPERATOR = '<' THEN CASE WHEN LEFT_VALUE<RIGHT_VALUE THEN 'true' ELSE 'false' END END AS VALUE FROM VARIABLES_JOIN

SELECT A.LEFT_OPERAND, A.OPERATOR, A.RIGHT_OPERAND, CASE WHEN B.VALUE > C.VALUE AND A.OPERATOR = '>' THEN 'true' WHEN B.VALUE = C.VALUE AND A.OPERATOR = '=' THEN 'true' WHEN B.VALUE < C.VALUE AND A.OPERATOR = '<' THEN 'true' ELSE 'false' END AS VALUE FROM EXPRESSIONS AS A LEFT JOIN VARIABLES AS B ON A.LEFT_OPERAND = B.NAME LEFT JOIN VARIABLES AS C ON A.RIGHT_OPERAND = C.NAME

SELECT EXP.*, CASE WHEN OPERATOR = '>' THEN IF(VAR1.VALUE > VAR2.VALUE, 'true', 'false') WHEN OPERATOR = '<' THEN IF(VAR2.VALUE > VAR1.VALUE, 'true', 'false') WHEN OPERATOR = '=' THEN IF(VAR2.VALUE = VAR1.VALUE, 'true', 'false') END AS VALUE FROM EXPRESSIONS AS EXP INNER JOIN VARIABLES AS VAR1 ON VAR1.NAME = EXP.LEFT_OPERAND INNER JOIN VARIABLES AS VAR2 ON VAR2.NAME = EXP.RIGHT_OPERAND

SELECT T1.LEFT_OPERAND AS LEFT_OPERAND, T1.OPERATOR AS OPERATOR, T1.RIGHT_OPERAND AS RIGHT_OPERAND, CASE WHEN T1.OPERATOR = '=' AND T2.VALUE = T3.VALUE THEN 'true' WHEN T1.OPERATOR = '>' AND T2.VALUE > T3.VALUE THEN 'true' WHEN T1.OPERATOR = '<' AND T2.VALUE < T3.VALUE THEN 'true' ELSE 'false' END AS VALUE FROM EXPRESSIONS T1 JOIN VARIABLES T2 ON T2.NAME = T1.LEFT_OPERAND JOIN VARIABLES T3 ON T3.NAME = T1.RIGHT_OPERAND

SELECT LEFT_OPERAND, OPERATOR, RIGHT_OPERAND, CASE WHEN OPERATOR='>' THEN IF(VL.VALUE>VR.VALUE, 'true','false') WHEN OPERATOR='<' THEN IF(VL.VALUE<VR.VALUE, 'true','false') WHEN OPERATOR='=' THEN IF(VL.VALUE=VR.VALUE, 'true','false') END AS VALUE FROM EXPRESSIONS E JOIN VARIABLES VL ON E.LEFT_OPERAND=VL.NAME JOIN VARIABLES VR ON E.RIGHT_OPERAND=VR.NAME

WITH CTE AS ( SELECT LEFT_OPERAND, T2.VALUE AS LEFT_VALUE, OPERATOR, RIGHT_OPERAND, T3.VALUE AS RIGHT_VALUE FROM EXPRESSIONS T1 LEFT JOIN VARIABLES T2 ON T1.LEFT_OPERAND = T2.NAME LEFT JOIN VARIABLES T3 ON T1.RIGHT_OPERAND = T3.NAME ) SELECT LEFT_OPERAND, OPERATOR, RIGHT_OPERAND, CASE WHEN OPERATOR = '>' AND LEFT_VALUE > RIGHT_VALUE THEN 'true' WHEN OPERATOR = '=' AND LEFT_VALUE = RIGHT_VALUE THEN 'true' WHEN OPERATOR = '<' AND LEFT_VALUE < RIGHT_VALUE THEN 'true' ELSE 'false' END AS VALUE FROM CTE

WITH TB AS ( SELECT E.*, V.VALUE AS LEFT_V, V1.VALUE AS RIGHT_V FROM EXPRESSIONS E LEFT JOIN VARIABLES V ON E.LEFT_OPERAND = V.NAME LEFT JOIN VARIABLES V1 ON E.RIGHT_OPERAND = V1.NAME) SELECT LEFT_OPERAND, OPERATOR, RIGHT_OPERAND, (CASE WHEN OPERATOR = '>' THEN IF(LEFT_V>RIGHT_V, 'true', 'false') WHEN OPERATOR = '=' THEN IF(LEFT_V = RIGHT_V, 'true','false') ELSE IF(LEFT_V < RIGHT_V, 'true', 'false') END) AS VALUE FROM TB

SELECT E.LEFT_OPERAND, E.OPERATOR, E.RIGHT_OPERAND, CASE WHEN E.OPERATOR = '>' THEN IF(V1.VALUE > V2.VALUE,'true','false') WHEN E.OPERATOR = '<' THEN IF(V1.VALUE < V2.VALUE,'true','false') WHEN E.OPERATOR = '=' THEN IF(V1.VALUE = V2.VALUE,'true','false') END VALUE FROM EXPRESSIONS E JOIN VARIABLES V1 ON E.LEFT_OPERAND = V1.NAME JOIN VARIABLES V2 ON E.RIGHT_OPERAND = V2.NAME

SELECT E.LEFT_OPERAND, E.OPERATOR, E.RIGHT_OPERAND, CASE WHEN E.OPERATOR='>' THEN IF(VL.VALUE>VR.VALUE,'true','false') WHEN E.OPERATOR='<' THEN IF(VL.VALUE<VR.VALUE,'true','false') ELSE IF(VL.VALUE=VR.VALUE,'true','false') END AS VALUE FROM EXPRESSIONS E JOIN VARIABLES VL JOIN VARIABLES VR ON E.LEFT_OPERAND=VL.NAME AND E.RIGHT_OPERAND=VR.NAME

SELECT LEFT_OPERAND, OPERATOR, RIGHT_OPERAND, (CASE WHEN OPERATOR = '=' THEN IF(VL.VALUE = VR.VALUE, 'true', 'false') WHEN OPERATOR = '>' THEN IF(VL.VALUE > VR.VALUE, 'true', 'false') WHEN OPERATOR = '<' THEN IF(VL.VALUE < VR.VALUE, 'true', 'false') END) AS VALUE FROM EXPRESSIONS LEFT JOIN VARIABLES VL ON VL.NAME = LEFT_OPERAND LEFT JOIN VARIABLES VR ON VR.NAME = RIGHT_OPERAND

SELECT LEFT_OPERAND,OPERATOR, RIGHT_OPERAND, (CASE WHEN OPERATOR ='>' AND V1.VALUE>V2.VALUE THEN 'true' WHEN OPERATOR = '<' AND V1.VALUE<V2.VALUE THEN 'true' WHEN OPERATOR ='=' AND V1.VALUE=V2.VALUE THEN 'true' ELSE 'false' END ) AS VALUE FROM EXPRESSIONS E1 LEFT JOIN VARIABLES V1 ON V1.NAME=E1.LEFT_OPERAND LEFT JOIN VARIABLES V2 ON V2.NAME=E1.RIGHT_OPERAND

SELECT LEFT_OPERAND ,OPERATOR ,RIGHT_OPERAND ,CASE WHEN B.VALUE > C.VALUE AND OPERATOR = '>' THEN 'true' WHEN B.VALUE < C.VALUE AND OPERATOR = '<' THEN 'true' WHEN B.VALUE = C.VALUE AND OPERATOR = '=' THEN 'true' ELSE 'false' END AS VALUE FROM EXPRESSIONS A JOIN VARIABLES B ON A.LEFT_OPERAND = B.NAME JOIN VARIABLES C ON A.RIGHT_OPERAND = C.NAME

WITH STEP1 AS ( SELECT LEFT_OPERAND, E.OPERATOR, RIGHT_OPERAND, CASE WHEN OPERATOR = '>' THEN VAR1.VALUE > VAR2.VALUE WHEN OPERATOR = '<' THEN VAR1.VALUE > VAR2.VALUE WHEN OPERATOR = '=' THEN VAR1.VALUE = VAR2.VALUE END AS CASE_ FROM EXPRESSIONS E LEFT JOIN VARIABLES VAR1 ON E.LEFT_OPERAND = VAR1.NAME LEFT JOIN VARIABLES VAR2 ON E.RIGHT_OPERAND=VAR2.NAME ) SELECT LEFT_OPERAND, OPERATOR, RIGHT_OPERAND, CASE WHEN CASE_ = 0 THEN 'false' ELSE 'true' END AS VALUE FROM STEP1

WITH RELATION AS ( SELECT LEFT_OPERAND, A.VALUE AS V1, OPERATOR, RIGHT_OPERAND, B.VALUE AS V2 FROM EXPRESSIONS E, VARIABLES A, VARIABLES B WHERE LEFT_OPERAND = A.NAME AND RIGHT_OPERAND = B.NAME ) SELECT LEFT_OPERAND, OPERATOR, RIGHT_OPERAND, CASE WHEN OPERATOR = '>' AND V1 > V2 THEN 'true' WHEN OPERATOR = '<' AND V1 < V2 THEN 'true' WHEN OPERATOR = '=' AND V1 = V2 THEN 'true' ELSE 'false' END AS VALUE FROM RELATION

SELECT A.LEFT_OPERAND, A.OPERATOR,A.RIGHT_OPERAND,(CASE WHEN OPERATOR='>' THEN (CASE WHEN (B.VALUE>C.VALUE) THEN 'true' ELSE 'false' END) WHEN OPERATOR='=' THEN (CASE WHEN (B.VALUE=C.VALUE) THEN 'true' ELSE 'false' END) WHEN OPERATOR='<' THEN (CASE WHEN (B.VALUE<C.VALUE) THEN 'true' ELSE 'false' END) END) AS VALUE FROM EXPRESSIONS A INNER JOIN VARIABLES B ON A.LEFT_OPERAND = B.NAME INNER JOIN VARIABLES C ON A.RIGHT_OPERAND = C.NAME

SELECT V1.NAME AS LEFT_OPERAND, OPERATOR, V2.NAME AS RIGHT_OPERAND, CASE WHEN OPERATOR = '>' AND V1.VALUE > V2.VALUE THEN 'true' WHEN OPERATOR = '=' AND V1.VALUE = V2.VALUE THEN 'true' WHEN OPERATOR = '<' AND V1.VALUE < V2.VALUE THEN 'true' ELSE 'false' END AS VALUE FROM EXPRESSIONS AS E LEFT JOIN VARIABLES AS V1 ON E.LEFT_OPERAND = V1.NAME LEFT JOIN VARIABLES AS V2 ON E.RIGHT_OPERAND = V2.NAME

SELECT V.LEFT_OPERAND, V.OPERATOR, V.RIGHT_OPERAND, CASE WHEN V.OPERATOR = '>' THEN IF(V.LVALUE>V.RVALUE, 'true', 'false') WHEN V.OPERATOR = '<' THEN IF(V.LVALUE<V.RVALUE, 'true', 'false') ELSE IF(V.LVALUE=V.RVALUE, 'true', 'false') END AS VALUE FROM (SELECT E.LEFT_OPERAND, E.OPERATOR, E.RIGHT_OPERAND, V1.VALUE AS LVALUE , V2.VALUE AS RVALUE FROM EXPRESSIONS AS E LEFT JOIN VARIABLES AS V1 ON E.LEFT_OPERAND = V1.NAME LEFT JOIN VARIABLES AS V2 ON E.RIGHT_OPERAND = V2.NAME) AS V

SELECT LEFT_OPERAND, OPERATOR,RIGHT_OPERAND, CASE WHEN OPERATOR = '=' AND V.VALUE = V2.VALUE THEN 'true' WHEN OPERATOR = '>' AND V.VALUE > V2.VALUE THEN 'true' WHEN OPERATOR = '<' AND V.VALUE < V2.VALUE THEN 'true' ELSE 'false' END AS VALUE FROM EXPRESSIONS E INNER JOIN VARIABLES V ON V.NAME=E.LEFT_OPERAND INNER JOIN VARIABLES V2 ON V2.NAME=E.RIGHT_OPERAND

SELECT E.LEFT_OPERAND, E.OPERATOR, E.RIGHT_OPERAND ,(CASE WHEN OPERATOR = '>' AND (L.VALUE > R.VALUE) THEN 'true' WHEN OPERATOR = '<' AND (L.VALUE < R.VALUE) THEN 'true' WHEN OPERATOR = '=' AND (L.VALUE = R.VALUE) THEN 'true' ELSE 'false' END ) VALUE FROM EXPRESSIONS E LEFT JOIN VARIABLES L ON E.LEFT_OPERAND = L.NAME LEFT JOIN VARIABLES R ON E.RIGHT_OPERAND = R.NAME

SELECT LEFT_OPERAND, OPERATOR, RIGHT_OPERAND, CASE WHEN OPERATOR = '>' THEN IF(L.VALUE > R.VALUE, 'true', 'false') WHEN OPERATOR = '<' THEN IF(L.VALUE < R.VALUE, 'true', 'false') ELSE IF(L.VALUE = R.VALUE, 'true', 'false') END AS VALUE FROM EXPRESSIONS E LEFT JOIN VARIABLES L ON E.LEFT_OPERAND = L.NAME LEFT JOIN VARIABLES R ON E.RIGHT_OPERAND = R.NAME

SELECT E.LEFT_OPERAND, E.OPERATOR, E.RIGHT_OPERAND, CASE WHEN (OPERATOR = '>' AND T1.VALUE > T2.VALUE) OR (OPERATOR = '=' AND T1.VALUE = T2.VALUE) OR (OPERATOR = '<' AND T1.VALUE < T2.VALUE) THEN 'true' ELSE 'false' END AS VALUE FROM EXPRESSIONS E JOIN VARIABLES T1 ON E.LEFT_OPERAND = T1.NAME JOIN VARIABLES T2 ON E.RIGHT_OPERAND = T2.NAME

SELECT E.*, CASE (CASE OPERATOR WHEN '>' THEN L.VALUE>R.VALUE WHEN '<' THEN L.VALUE<R.VALUE ELSE L.VALUE=R.VALUE END) WHEN 0 THEN 'false' ELSE 'true' END AS VALUE FROM EXPRESSIONS E JOIN VARIABLES L ON E.LEFT_OPERAND=L.NAME JOIN VARIABLES R ON E.RIGHT_OPERAND=R.NAME

WITH T1 AS (SELECT LEFT_OPERAND, OPERATOR, RIGHT_OPERAND, V.NAME AS V1, V.VALUE AS V1V FROM EXPRESSIONS LEFT JOIN VARIABLES V ON LEFT_OPERAND=NAME), T2 AS( SELECT LEFT_OPERAND, OPERATOR, RIGHT_OPERAND, V1, V1V, V.NAME AS V2, V.VALUE AS V2V FROM T1 LEFT JOIN VARIABLES V ON V.NAME=RIGHT_OPERAND ) SELECT LEFT_OPERAND, OPERATOR, RIGHT_OPERAND, CASE WHEN OPERATOR='=' AND V1V=V2V THEN 'true' WHEN OPERATOR='>' AND V1V>V2V THEN 'true' WHEN OPERATOR='<' AND V1V<V2V THEN 'true' ELSE 'false' END AS VALUE FROM T2

SELECT LEFT_OPERAND , OPERATOR , RIGHT_OPERAND, CASE WHEN OPERATOR ='>' AND L.VALUE > R.VALUE THEN 'true' WHEN OPERATOR ='>' AND L.VALUE <= R.VALUE THEN 'false' WHEN OPERATOR ='<' AND L.VALUE >= R.VALUE THEN 'false' WHEN OPERATOR ='<' AND L.VALUE < R.VALUE THEN 'true' WHEN OPERATOR ='=' AND L.VALUE=R.VALUE THEN 'true' WHEN OPERATOR ='=' AND L.VALUE!=R.VALUE THEN 'false' END AS VALUE FROM EXPRESSIONS E LEFT JOIN VARIABLES L ON E.LEFT_OPERAND = L.NAME LEFT JOIN VARIABLES R ON E.RIGHT_OPERAND = R.NAME

WITH CTE AS ( SELECT V.VALUE AS LEFT_, E.LEFT_OPERAND, E.OPERATOR, ROW_NUMBER()OVER() AS RN FROM VARIABLES AS V INNER JOIN EXPRESSIONS E ON V.NAME = E.LEFT_OPERAND ), CTE1 AS ( SELECT V.VALUE AS RIGHT_, E.RIGHT_OPERAND, ROW_NUMBER()OVER() AS RN FROM VARIABLES AS V INNER JOIN EXPRESSIONS E ON V.NAME = E.RIGHT_OPERAND ) SELECT CTE.LEFT_OPERAND, CTE.OPERATOR, CTE1.RIGHT_OPERAND, CASE WHEN CTE.OPERATOR = '=' THEN CASE WHEN CTE.LEFT_ = CTE1.RIGHT_ THEN 'true' ELSE 'false' END WHEN CTE.OPERATOR = '>' THEN CASE WHEN CTE.LEFT_ > CTE1.RIGHT_ THEN 'true' ELSE 'false' END WHEN CTE.OPERATOR = '<' THEN CASE WHEN CTE.LEFT_ < CTE1.RIGHT_ THEN 'true' ELSE 'false' END END AS VALUE FROM CTE INNER JOIN CTE1 ON CTE.RN = CTE1.RN

SELECT LEFT_OPERAND, OPERATOR , RIGHT_OPERAND ,CASE WHEN A.VALUE>B.VALUE AND OPERATOR='>' THEN 'true' WHEN A.VALUE<B.VALUE AND OPERATOR='<' THEN 'true' WHEN A.VALUE=B.VALUE AND OPERATOR='=' THEN 'true' ELSE 'false' END AS VALUE FROM EXPRESSIONS E JOIN VARIABLES A ON LEFT_OPERAND=A.NAME JOIN VARIABLES B ON RIGHT_OPERAND=B.NAME

SELECT LEFT_OPERAND, OPERATOR, RIGHT_OPERAND, (CASE WHEN OPERATOR = '>' THEN IF(V1.VALUE > V2.VALUE, 'true','false') WHEN OPERATOR = '<' THEN IF (V1.VALUE < V2.VALUE, 'true','false') WHEN OPERATOR = '=' THEN IF (V1.VALUE = V2.VALUE, 'true','false') END) AS VALUE FROM EXPRESSIONS E LEFT JOIN VARIABLES V1 ON V1.NAME = E.LEFT_OPERAND LEFT JOIN VARIABLES V2 ON V2.NAME = E.RIGHT_OPERAND

WITH CTE AS ( SELECT T0.VALUE AS LEFT_VALUE, T2.VALUE AS RIGHT_VALUE, T1.* FROM EXPRESSIONS T1 JOIN VARIABLES T0 ON T0.NAME = T1.LEFT_OPERAND JOIN VARIABLES T2 ON T2.NAME = T1.RIGHT_OPERAND ) SELECT LEFT_OPERAND, OPERATOR, RIGHT_OPERAND, CASE WHEN OPERATOR = '>' AND LEFT_VALUE > RIGHT_VALUE THEN 'true' WHEN OPERATOR = '<' AND LEFT_VALUE < RIGHT_VALUE THEN 'true' WHEN OPERATOR = '=' AND LEFT_VALUE = RIGHT_VALUE THEN 'true' ELSE 'false' END AS VALUE FROM CTE

SELECT E.LEFT_OPERAND,E.OPERATOR,E.RIGHT_OPERAND, CASE WHEN OPERATOR = '>' AND (SELECT VALUE FROM VARIABLES WHERE NAME = E.LEFT_OPERAND) > (SELECT VALUE FROM VARIABLES WHERE NAME = E.RIGHT_OPERAND) THEN 'true' WHEN OPERATOR = '<' AND (SELECT VALUE FROM VARIABLES WHERE NAME = E.LEFT_OPERAND) < (SELECT VALUE FROM VARIABLES WHERE NAME = E.RIGHT_OPERAND) THEN 'true' WHEN OPERATOR = '=' AND (SELECT VALUE FROM VARIABLES WHERE NAME = E.LEFT_OPERAND) = (SELECT VALUE FROM VARIABLES WHERE NAME = E.RIGHT_OPERAND) THEN 'true' ELSE 'false' END AS VALUE FROM EXPRESSIONS E

SELECT A.LEFT_OPERAND, A.OPERATOR, A.RIGHT_OPERAND, CASE WHEN A.OPERATOR = '<' AND B.VALUE < C.VALUE THEN 'true' WHEN A.OPERATOR = '=' AND B.VALUE = C.VALUE THEN 'true' WHEN A.OPERATOR = '>' AND B.VALUE > C.VALUE THEN 'true' ELSE 'false' END AS VALUE FROM EXPRESSIONS AS A LEFT JOIN VARIABLES AS B ON A.LEFT_OPERAND = B.NAME LEFT JOIN VARIABLES AS C ON A.RIGHT_OPERAND = C.NAME

SELECT A.*, CASE WHEN A.OPERATOR = '<' AND B.VALUE < C.VALUE THEN 'true' WHEN A.OPERATOR = '=' AND B.VALUE = C.VALUE THEN 'true' WHEN A.OPERATOR = '>' AND B.VALUE > C.VALUE THEN 'true' ELSE 'false' END AS VALUE FROM EXPRESSIONS A JOIN VARIABLES B ON A.LEFT_OPERAND = B.NAME JOIN VARIABLES C ON A.RIGHT_OPERAND = C.NAME

SELECT LEFT_OPERAND, OPERATOR, RIGHT_OPERAND, (CASE WHEN V1.VALUE > V2.VALUE AND OPERATOR = '>' THEN 'true' WHEN V1.VALUE < V2.VALUE AND OPERATOR = '<' THEN 'true' WHEN V1.VALUE = V2.VALUE AND OPERATOR = '=' THEN 'true' ELSE 'false' END) AS VALUE FROM VARIABLES V1 JOIN EXPRESSIONS E ON V1.NAME = E.LEFT_OPERAND JOIN VARIABLES V2 ON E.RIGHT_OPERAND = V2.NAME

SELECT LEFT_OPERAND, OPERATOR, RIGHT_OPERAND, CASE WHEN OPERATOR = '>' THEN IF((SELECT VALUE FROM VARIABLES WHERE NAME = LEFT_OPERAND) > (SELECT VALUE FROM VARIABLES WHERE NAME = RIGHT_OPERAND), 'true', 'false') WHEN OPERATOR = '<' THEN IF((SELECT VALUE FROM VARIABLES WHERE NAME = LEFT_OPERAND) < (SELECT VALUE FROM VARIABLES WHERE NAME = RIGHT_OPERAND), 'true', 'false') ELSE IF((SELECT VALUE FROM VARIABLES WHERE NAME = LEFT_OPERAND) = (SELECT VALUE FROM VARIABLES WHERE NAME = RIGHT_OPERAND), 'true', 'false') END AS VALUE FROM EXPRESSIONS

SELECT E.LEFT_OPERAND, E.OPERATOR, E.RIGHT_OPERAND, (CASE WHEN E.OPERATOR = '<' THEN IF(L.VALUE < R.VALUE, 'true', 'false') WHEN E.OPERATOR = '>' THEN IF(L.VALUE > R.VALUE, 'true', 'false') ELSE IF(L.VALUE = R.VALUE, 'true', 'false') END) AS VALUE FROM EXPRESSIONS E JOIN VARIABLES L ON E.LEFT_OPERAND = L.NAME JOIN VARIABLES R ON E.RIGHT_OPERAND = R.NAME

SELECT A.LEFT_OPERAND, A.OPERATOR, A.RIGHT_OPERAND, CASE A.OPERATOR WHEN '=' THEN IF(B.VALUE = C.VALUE, 'true', 'false') WHEN '>' THEN IF(B.VALUE > C.VALUE, 'true', 'false') WHEN '<' THEN IF(B.VALUE < C.VALUE, 'true', 'false') ELSE NULL END AS VALUE FROM EXPRESSIONS AS A JOIN VARIABLES AS B ON A.LEFT_OPERAND = B.NAME JOIN VARIABLES AS C ON A.RIGHT_OPERAND = C.NAME

SELECT E.LEFT_OPERAND, E.OPERATOR, E.RIGHT_OPERAND, CASE WHEN E.OPERATOR = '=' AND V1.VALUE = V2.VALUE THEN 'true' WHEN E.OPERATOR = '<' AND V1.VALUE < V2.VALUE THEN 'true' WHEN E.OPERATOR = '>' AND V1.VALUE > V2.VALUE THEN 'true' ELSE 'false' END AS VALUE FROM EXPRESSIONS E JOIN VARIABLES V1 ON V1.NAME = E.LEFT_OPERAND JOIN VARIABLES V2 ON V2.NAME = E.RIGHT_OPERAND

SELECT LEFT_OPERAND, OPERATOR, RIGHT_OPERAND, CASE WHEN OPERATOR = '<' THEN IF(VAR1.VALUE < VAR2.VALUE, 'true','false') WHEN OPERATOR = '>' THEN IF(VAR1.VALUE > VAR2.VALUE,'true','false') ELSE IF(VAR1.VALUE = VAR2.VALUE, 'true','false') END AS VALUE FROM EXPRESSIONS EXP JOIN VARIABLES VAR1 ON EXP.LEFT_OPERAND = VAR1.NAME JOIN VARIABLES VAR2 ON EXP.RIGHT_OPERAND = VAR2.NAME

SELECT E.*, CASE WHEN V1.VALUE>V2.VALUE AND OPERATOR='>' THEN 'true' WHEN V1.VALUE<V2.VALUE AND OPERATOR='<' THEN 'true' WHEN V1.VALUE=V2.VALUE AND OPERATOR='=' THEN 'true' ELSE 'false' END AS VALUE FROM EXPRESSIONS E JOIN VARIABLES V1 ON V1.NAME=E.LEFT_OPERAND JOIN VARIABLES V2 ON E.RIGHT_OPERAND=V2.NAME

E.LEFT_OPERAND, E.OPERATOR, E.RIGHT_OPERAND, CASE WHEN E.OPERATOR = '>' THEN CASE WHEN VL.VALUE > VR.VALUE THEN 'true' ELSE 'false' END WHEN E.OPERATOR = '<' THEN CASE WHEN VL.VALUE < VR.VALUE THEN 'true' ELSE 'false' END WHEN E.OPERATOR = '=' THEN CASE WHEN VL.VALUE = VR.VALUE THEN 'true' ELSE 'false' END END AS VALUE FROM EXPRESSIONS E JOIN VARIABLES VL ON E.LEFT_OPERAND = VL.NAME JOIN VARIABLES VR ON E.RIGHT_OPERAND = VR.NAME

SELECT E.*, IF((CASE WHEN OPERATOR ='>' THEN V1.VALUE>V2.VALUE WHEN OPERATOR='=' THEN V1.VALUE=V2.VALUE ELSE V1.VALUE<V2.VALUE END)=0,'false','true') AS VALUE FROM EXPRESSIONS E LEFT JOIN VARIABLES V1 ON V1.NAME = E.LEFT_OPERAND LEFT JOIN VARIABLES V2 ON V2.NAME = E.RIGHT_OPERAND

SELECT LEFT_OPERAND, OPERATOR, RIGHT_OPERAND, CASE WHEN OPERATOR = '=' AND LEFTVAL = RIGHTVAL THEN 'true' WHEN OPERATOR = '>' AND LEFTVAL > RIGHTVAL THEN 'true' WHEN OPERATOR = '<' AND RIGHTVAL > LEFTVAL THEN 'true' ELSE 'false' END AS VALUE FROM ( SELECT EXPRESSIONS.LEFT_OPERAND, EXPRESSIONS.OPERATOR, EXPRESSIONS.RIGHT_OPERAND, A.VALUE AS LEFTVAL, B.VALUE AS RIGHTVAL FROM EXPRESSIONS LEFT JOIN VARIABLES AS A ON EXPRESSIONS.LEFT_OPERAND = A.NAME LEFT JOIN VARIABLES AS B ON EXPRESSIONS.RIGHT_OPERAND = B.NAME) AS SUBQ

SELECT LEFT_OPERAND, OPERATOR, RIGHT_OPERAND, CASE WHEN OPERATOR = '>' AND V1.VALUE > V2.VALUE THEN 'true' WHEN OPERATOR = '=' AND V1.VALUE = V2.VALUE THEN 'true' WHEN OPERATOR = '<' AND V1.VALUE < V2.VALUE THEN 'true' ELSE 'false' END AS VALUE FROM EXPRESSIONS, VARIABLES AS V1, VARIABLES AS V2 WHERE LEFT_OPERAND = V1.NAME AND RIGHT_OPERAND = V2.NAME

SELECT LEFT_OPERAND, OPERATOR, RIGHT_OPERAND, CASE WHEN VALUE=1 THEN 'true' ELSE 'false' END AS VALUE FROM ( SELECT E.*, CASE WHEN OPERATOR='>' THEN (V1.VALUE>V2.VALUE) WHEN OPERATOR='<' THEN (V1.VALUE<V2.VALUE) ELSE (V1.VALUE=V2.VALUE) END AS VALUE FROM EXPRESSIONS E INNER JOIN VARIABLES V1 ON E.LEFT_OPERAND=V1.NAME INNER JOIN VARIABLES V2 ON E.RIGHT_OPERAND=V2.NAME ) A

SELECT E.*, CASE WHEN V1.VALUE > V2.VALUE AND OPERATOR = '>' THEN 'true' WHEN V1.VALUE < V2.VALUE AND OPERATOR = '<' THEN 'true' WHEN V1.VALUE = V2.VALUE AND OPERATOR = '=' THEN 'true' ELSE 'false' END AS VALUE FROM EXPRESSIONS E LEFT JOIN VARIABLES V1 ON E.LEFT_OPERAND = V1.NAME LEFT JOIN VARIABLES V2 ON E.RIGHT_OPERAND = V2.NAME

SELECT LEFT_OPERAND, OPERATOR, RIGHT_OPERAND, (CASE WHEN LFT>RIT AND OPERATOR = '>' THEN 'true' WHEN LFT=RIT AND OPERATOR = '=' THEN 'true' WHEN LFT<RIT AND OPERATOR = '<' THEN 'true' ELSE 'false' END) AS VALUE FROM (SELECT VL.VALUE AS LFT, VR.VALUE AS RIT, LEFT_OPERAND, RIGHT_OPERAND, OPERATOR FROM EXPRESSIONS LEFT JOIN VARIABLES VL ON VL.NAME = LEFT_OPERAND LEFT JOIN VARIABLES VR ON VR.NAME = RIGHT_OPERAND ) T

SELECT LEFT_OPERAND, OPERATOR, RIGHT_OPERAND, CASE WHEN OPERATOR = '>' AND VARIABLE1.VALUE > VARIABLE2.VALUE THEN 'true' WHEN OPERATOR = '<' AND VARIABLE1.VALUE < VARIABLE2.VALUE THEN 'true' WHEN OPERATOR = '=' AND VARIABLE1.VALUE = VARIABLE2.VALUE THEN 'true' ELSE 'false' END AS VALUE FROM EXPRESSIONS LEFT JOIN VARIABLES AS VARIABLE1 ON EXPRESSIONS.LEFT_OPERAND = VARIABLE1.NAME LEFT JOIN VARIABLES AS VARIABLE2 ON EXPRESSIONS.RIGHT_OPERAND = VARIABLE2.NAME

SELECT E.LEFT_OPERAND, E.OPERATOR, E.RIGHT_OPERAND, CASE WHEN E.OPERATOR = '<' AND V1.VALUE < V2.VALUE THEN 'true' WHEN E.OPERATOR = '=' AND V1.VALUE = V2.VALUE THEN 'true' WHEN E.OPERATOR = '>' AND V1.VALUE > V2.VALUE THEN 'true' ELSE 'false' END AS VALUE FROM EXPRESSIONS E LEFT JOIN VARIABLES V1 ON E.LEFT_OPERAND = V1.NAME LEFT JOIN VARIABLES V2 ON E.RIGHT_OPERAND = V2.NAME

SELECT A.LEFT_OPERAND, A.OPERATOR,A.RIGHT_OPERAND, CASE WHEN ( CASE WHEN A.OPERATOR = '>' THEN A.VALUE > B.VALUE WHEN A.OPERATOR = '=' THEN A.VALUE = B.VALUE ELSE A.VALUE<B.VALUE END) = 1 THEN 'true' ELSE 'false' END AS VALUE FROM ( SELECT * FROM EXPRESSIONS E JOIN VARIABLES O ON E.LEFT_OPERAND = O.NAME) A JOIN ( SELECT * FROM EXPRESSIONS E JOIN VARIABLES O ON E.RIGHT_OPERAND = O.NAME) B ON A.LEFT_OPERAND = B.LEFT_OPERAND AND A.OPERATOR= B.OPERATOR AND A.RIGHT_OPERAND= B.RIGHT_OPERAND

SELECT LEFT_OPERAND, OPERATOR, RIGHT_OPERAND, VALUE FROM (SELECT *, (@A := (SELECT VALUE FROM VARIABLES WHERE NAME = LEFT_OPERAND)), (@B := (SELECT VALUE FROM VARIABLES WHERE NAME = RIGHT_OPERAND)), IF((CASE OPERATOR WHEN '>' THEN @A > @B WHEN '<' THEN @A<@B ELSE @A = @B END),'true','false') VALUE FROM EXPRESSIONS) T

SELECT E.LEFT_OPERAND, E.OPERATOR, E.RIGHT_OPERAND, CASE WHEN OPERATOR = '=' AND V1.VALUE=V2.VALUE THEN 'true' WHEN OPERATOR = '>' AND V1.VALUE>V2.VALUE THEN 'true' WHEN OPERATOR = '<' AND V1.VALUE<V2.VALUE THEN 'true' ELSE 'false' END AS VALUE FROM EXPRESSIONS E INNER JOIN VARIABLES V1 ON E.LEFT_OPERAND = V1.NAME INNER JOIN VARIABLES V2 ON E.RIGHT_OPERAND = V2.NAME

SELECT E.LEFT_OPERAND, E.OPERATOR, E.RIGHT_OPERAND, IF(CASE E.OPERATOR WHEN '=' THEN L.VALUE = R.VALUE WHEN '>' THEN L.VALUE > R.VALUE WHEN '<' THEN L.VALUE < R.VALUE END = 1, 'true', 'false') AS VALUE FROM EXPRESSIONS E LEFT JOIN VARIABLES L ON E.LEFT_OPERAND = L.NAME LEFT JOIN VARIABLES R ON E.RIGHT_OPERAND = R.NAME

SELECT E.*, CASE WHEN E.OPERATOR = '>' AND V.VALUE > V2.VALUE THEN 'true' WHEN E.OPERATOR = '>' AND V.VALUE <= V2.VALUE THEN 'false' WHEN E.OPERATOR = '<' AND V.VALUE < V2.VALUE THEN 'true' WHEN E.OPERATOR = '<' AND V.VALUE >= V2.VALUE THEN 'false' WHEN E.OPERATOR = '=' AND V.VALUE = V2.VALUE THEN 'true' WHEN E.OPERATOR = '=' AND V.VALUE <> V2.VALUE THEN 'false' ELSE '' END AS VALUE FROM EXPRESSIONS AS E LEFT JOIN VARIABLES V ON E.LEFT_OPERAND = V.NAME LEFT JOIN VARIABLES V2 ON E.RIGHT_OPERAND = V2.NAME

SELECT LEFT_OPERAND, OPERATOR, RIGHT_OPERAND, CASE WHEN OPERATOR = '>' AND V1.VALUE > V2.VALUE THEN 'true' WHEN OPERATOR = '=' AND V1.VALUE = V2.VALUE THEN 'true' WHEN OPERATOR = '<' AND V1.VALUE < V2.VALUE THEN 'true' ELSE 'false' END AS VALUE FROM EXPRESSIONS E INNER JOIN VARIABLES V1 ON V1.NAME = E.LEFT_OPERAND INNER JOIN VARIABLES V2 ON V2.NAME = E.RIGHT_OPERAND

WITH TMP AS ( SELECT A.*, B.VALUE AS LEFT_VALUE, C.VALUE AS RIGHT_VALUE FROM EXPRESSIONS A LEFT JOIN VARIABLES B ON A.LEFT_OPERAND = B.NAME LEFT JOIN VARIABLES C ON A.RIGHT_OPERAND = C.NAME) SELECT LEFT_OPERAND, OPERATOR, RIGHT_OPERAND, CASE WHEN OPERATOR = '>' AND LEFT_VALUE > RIGHT_VALUE THEN 'true' WHEN OPERATOR = '<' AND LEFT_VALUE < RIGHT_VALUE THEN 'true' WHEN OPERATOR = '=' AND LEFT_VALUE = RIGHT_VALUE THEN 'true' ELSE 'false' END AS VALUE FROM TMP

SELECT E.LEFT_OPERAND, E.OPERATOR, E.RIGHT_OPERAND, CASE E.OPERATOR WHEN '>' THEN CASE WHEN LV.VALUE > RV.VALUE THEN 'true' ELSE 'false' END WHEN '<' THEN CASE WHEN LV.VALUE < RV.VALUE THEN 'true' ELSE 'false' END ELSE CASE WHEN LV.VALUE = RV.VALUE THEN 'true' ELSE 'false' END END AS VALUE FROM EXPRESSIONS E INNER JOIN VARIABLES LV ON E.LEFT_OPERAND = LV.NAME INNER JOIN VARIABLES RV ON E.RIGHT_OPERAND = RV.NAME

WITH T1 AS ( SELECT LEFT_OPERAND,OPERATOR, RIGHT_OPERAND, CASE WHEN OPERATOR = '>' THEN (SELECT VALUE FROM VARIABLES WHERE NAME = LEFT_OPERAND)>(SELECT VALUE FROM VARIABLES WHERE NAME = RIGHT_OPERAND) WHEN OPERATOR = '=' THEN (SELECT VALUE FROM VARIABLES WHERE NAME = LEFT_OPERAND)=(SELECT VALUE FROM VARIABLES WHERE NAME = RIGHT_OPERAND) WHEN OPERATOR = '<' THEN (SELECT VALUE FROM VARIABLES WHERE NAME = LEFT_OPERAND)<(SELECT VALUE FROM VARIABLES WHERE NAME = RIGHT_OPERAND) END AS OP FROM EXPRESSIONS ) SELECT LEFT_OPERAND,OPERATOR, RIGHT_OPERAND, CASE WHEN OP = 0 THEN 'false' ELSE 'true' END AS VALUE FROM T1

SELECT B.NAME AS LEFT_OPERAND, A.OPERATOR, C.NAME AS RIGHT_OPERAND, CASE WHEN A.OPERATOR ='>' AND B.VALUE>C.VALUE THEN 'true' WHEN A.OPERATOR ='<' AND B.VALUE<C.VALUE THEN 'true' WHEN A.OPERATOR ='=' AND B.VALUE=C.VALUE THEN 'true' ELSE 'false' END AS VALUE FROM EXPRESSIONS A LEFT JOIN VARIABLES B ON A.LEFT_OPERAND=B.NAME LEFT JOIN VARIABLES C ON A.RIGHT_OPERAND=C.NAME

SELECT E.LEFT_OPERAND, E.OPERATOR, E.RIGHT_OPERAND, CASE WHEN OPERATOR='<' AND V1.VALUE<V2.VALUE THEN 'true' WHEN OPERATOR='>' AND V1.VALUE>V2.VALUE THEN 'true' WHEN OPERATOR='=' AND V1.VALUE=V2.VALUE THEN 'true' ELSE 'false' END AS VALUE FROM EXPRESSIONS E JOIN VARIABLES V1 ON V1.NAME=E.LEFT_OPERAND JOIN VARIABLES V2 ON V2.NAME=E.RIGHT_OPERAND

WITH TMP AS (SELECT LEFT_VALUE, LEFT_OPERAND, OPERATOR, VALUE AS RIGHT_VALUE, RIGHT_OPERAND FROM (SELECT VALUE AS LEFT_VALUE, LEFT_OPERAND, OPERATOR, RIGHT_OPERAND FROM EXPRESSIONS JOIN VARIABLES WHERE EXPRESSIONS.LEFT_OPERAND = VARIABLES.NAME) A JOIN VARIABLES WHERE A.RIGHT_OPERAND = VARIABLES.NAME) SELECT LEFT_OPERAND, OPERATOR, RIGHT_OPERAND, IF((OPERATOR = '=') & (LEFT_VALUE=RIGHT_VALUE), 'true', IF ((OPERATOR = '>') & (LEFT_VALUE>RIGHT_VALUE), 'true', IF ((OPERATOR = '<') & (LEFT_VALUE<RIGHT_VALUE), 'true', 'false'))) AS VALUE FROM TMP

SELECT LEFT_OPERAND, OPERATOR, RIGHT_OPERAND, (CASE WHEN OPERATOR = '>' AND LV.VALUE > RV.VALUE THEN 'true' WHEN OPERATOR = '<' AND LV.VALUE < RV.VALUE THEN 'true' WHEN OPERATOR = '=' AND LV.VALUE = RV.VALUE THEN 'true' ELSE 'false' END) AS VALUE FROM EXPRESSIONS E LEFT JOIN VARIABLES LV ON E.LEFT_OPERAND = LV.NAME LEFT JOIN VARIABLES RV ON E.RIGHT_OPERAND = RV.NAME

SELECT E.LEFT_OPERAND, E.OPERATOR, E.RIGHT_OPERAND, CASE WHEN E.OPERATOR = '>' AND (V_LEFT.VALUE > V_RIGHT.VALUE) THEN 'true' WHEN E.OPERATOR = '<' AND (V_LEFT.VALUE < V_RIGHT.VALUE) THEN 'true' WHEN E.OPERATOR = '=' AND (V_LEFT.VALUE = V_RIGHT.VALUE) THEN 'true' ELSE 'false' END AS VALUE FROM EXPRESSIONS E INNER JOIN VARIABLES V_LEFT ON E.LEFT_OPERAND = V_LEFT.NAME INNER JOIN VARIABLES V_RIGHT ON E.RIGHT_OPERAND = V_RIGHT.NAME

SELECT LEFT_OPERAND, OPERATOR, RIGHT_OPERAND, CASE WHEN OPERATOR = '>' AND V1.VALUE > V2.VALUE THEN 'true' WHEN OPERATOR = '<' AND V1.VALUE < V2.VALUE THEN 'true' WHEN OPERATOR = '=' AND V1.VALUE = V2.VALUE THEN 'true' ELSE 'false' END VALUE FROM EXPRESSIONS E LEFT JOIN VARIABLES V1 ON V1.NAME = E.LEFT_OPERAND LEFT JOIN VARIABLES V2 ON V2.NAME = E.RIGHT_OPERAND

SELECT E.LEFT_OPERAND, E.OPERATOR, E.RIGHT_OPERAND, CASE WHEN E.OPERATOR='>' AND A.VALUE>B.VALUE THEN 'true' WHEN E.OPERATOR='<' AND A.VALUE<B.VALUE THEN 'true' WHEN E.OPERATOR='=' AND A.VALUE=B.VALUE THEN 'true' ELSE 'false' END AS VALUE FROM EXPRESSIONS E JOIN VARIABLES A ON E.LEFT_OPERAND=A.NAME JOIN VARIABLES B ON E.RIGHT_OPERAND=B.NAME

SELECT E.LEFT_OPERAND, E.OPERATOR, E.RIGHT_OPERAND, CASE WHEN (OPERATOR = '>' AND T1.VALUE > T2.VALUE) THEN 'true' WHEN (OPERATOR = '<' AND T1.VALUE < T2.VALUE) THEN 'true' WHEN (OPERATOR = '=' AND T1.VALUE = T2.VALUE) THEN 'true' ELSE 'false' END AS VALUE FROM EXPRESSIONS E JOIN VARIABLES T1 ON E.LEFT_OPERAND = T1.NAME JOIN VARIABLES T2 ON E.RIGHT_OPERAND = T2.NAME

SELECT LEFT_OPERAND, OPERATOR, RIGHT_OPERAND, CASE WHEN OPERATOR='>' THEN IF(A.VALUE>B.VALUE, 'true','false') WHEN OPERATOR='<' THEN IF(A.VALUE<B.VALUE, 'true','false') ELSE IF(A.VALUE=B.VALUE, 'true','false') END AS VALUE FROM EXPRESSIONS E JOIN VARIABLES A ON A.NAME=LEFT_OPERAND JOIN VARIABLES B ON B.NAME=RIGHT_OPERAND

SELECT E.*, CASE WHEN OPERATOR LIKE '>' THEN IF(V1.VALUE > V2.VALUE,'true','false') WHEN OPERATOR LIKE '<' THEN IF(V1.VALUE < V2.VALUE,'true','false') WHEN OPERATOR LIKE '=' THEN IF(V1.VALUE = V2.VALUE,'true','false') END AS VALUE FROM EXPRESSIONS E JOIN VARIABLES V1 ON E.LEFT_OPERAND = V1.NAME JOIN VARIABLES V2 ON E.RIGHT_OPERAND=V2.NAME

WITH T1 AS( SELECT CASE WHEN LEFT_OPERAND = V1.NAME THEN V1.VALUE END LEFT_VALUE, CASE WHEN RIGHT_OPERAND = V2.NAME THEN V2.VALUE END RIGHT_VALUE, E.* FROM EXPRESSIONS E LEFT JOIN VARIABLES V1 ON E.LEFT_OPERAND = V1.NAME LEFT JOIN VARIABLES V2 ON E.RIGHT_OPERAND = V2.NAME) SELECT LEFT_OPERAND, OPERATOR,RIGHT_OPERAND , CASE WHEN OPERATOR = '>' THEN IF(LEFT_VALUE>RIGHT_VALUE,'true','false') WHEN OPERATOR = '<' THEN IF(LEFT_VALUE<RIGHT_VALUE,'true','false') WHEN OPERATOR = '=' THEN IF(LEFT_VALUE = RIGHT_VALUE,'true','false') END VALUE FROM T1

WITH T AS ( SELECT LEFT_OPERAND, OPERATOR, RIGHT_OPERAND ,VALUE AS VALUE1 FROM EXPRESSIONS E INNER JOIN VARIABLES V ON E.LEFT_OPERAND = V.NAME ), T1 AS ( SELECT LEFT_OPERAND, OPERATOR, RIGHT_OPERAND ,VALUE AS VALUE2 FROM EXPRESSIONS E INNER JOIN VARIABLES V ON E.RIGHT_OPERAND = V.NAME ) SELECT LEFT_OPERAND, OPERATOR, RIGHT_OPERAND, CASE WHEN OPERATOR = '>' AND VALUE1 > VALUE2 THEN 'true' WHEN OPERATOR = '<' AND VALUE1 < VALUE2 THEN 'true' WHEN OPERATOR = '=' AND VALUE1 = VALUE2 THEN 'true' WHEN OPERATOR = '>' AND VALUE1 > VALUE2 THEN 'true' WHEN OPERATOR = '<' AND VALUE1 < VALUE2 THEN 'true' WHEN OPERATOR = '=' AND VALUE1 = VALUE2 THEN 'true' ELSE 'false' END AS VALUE FROM T INNER JOIN T1 USING (LEFT_OPERAND, OPERATOR, RIGHT_OPERAND)

SELECT E.LEFT_OPERAND, E.OPERATOR, E.RIGHT_OPERAND, (CASE WHEN OPERATOR = '>' AND V1.VALUE > V2.VALUE THEN 'true' WHEN OPERATOR = '<' AND V1.VALUE < V2.VALUE THEN 'true' WHEN OPERATOR = '=' AND V1.VALUE = V2.VALUE THEN 'true' ELSE 'false' END) AS VALUE FROM EXPRESSIONS E JOIN VARIABLES V1 ON V1.NAME = E.LEFT_OPERAND JOIN VARIABLES V2 ON V2.NAME = E.RIGHT_OPERAND

SELECT LEFT_OPERAND, OPERATOR, RIGHT_OPERAND, CASE WHEN OPERATOR = '>' AND V1.VALUE - V2.VALUE >0 THEN 'true' WHEN OPERATOR = '=' AND V1.VALUE - V2.VALUE =0 THEN 'true' WHEN OPERATOR = '<' AND V1.VALUE - V2.VALUE <0 THEN 'true' ELSE 'false' END AS VALUE FROM EXPRESSIONS INNER JOIN VARIABLES V1 ON EXPRESSIONS.LEFT_OPERAND = V1.NAME INNER JOIN VARIABLES V2 ON EXPRESSIONS.RIGHT_OPERAND = V2.NAME

SELECT LEFT_OPERAND, OPERATOR, RIGHT_OPERAND, CASE WHEN OPERATOR = '>' THEN IF ((B.VALUE) > (C.VALUE), 'true', 'false') WHEN OPERATOR = '<' THEN IF ((B.VALUE) < (C.VALUE), 'true', 'false') WHEN OPERATOR = '=' THEN IF ((B.VALUE) = (C.VALUE), 'true', 'false') END AS VALUE FROM EXPRESSIONS AS A JOIN VARIABLES AS B ON A.LEFT_OPERAND = B.NAME JOIN VARIABLES AS C ON A.RIGHT_OPERAND = C.NAME

SELECT EXPRESSIONS.LEFT_OPERAND,EXPRESSIONS.OPERATOR,EXPRESSIONS.RIGHT_OPERAND, (CASE WHEN OPERATOR = '>' AND V1.VALUE > V2.VALUE THEN 'true' WHEN OPERATOR = '<' AND V1.VALUE < V2.VALUE THEN 'true' WHEN OPERATOR = '=' AND V1.VALUE = V2.VALUE THEN 'true' ELSE 'false' END) AS VALUE FROM EXPRESSIONS JOIN VARIABLES AS V1 ON V1.NAME = EXPRESSIONS.LEFT_OPERAND JOIN VARIABLES AS V2 ON V2.NAME = EXPRESSIONS.RIGHT_OPERAND

SELECT M.LEFT_OPERAND, M.OPERATOR, M.RIGHT_OPERAND, CASE WHEN M.OPERATOR='<' AND (L < V2.VALUE) THEN 'true' WHEN M.OPERATOR='=' AND (L = V2.VALUE) THEN 'true' WHEN M.OPERATOR='>' AND (L>V2.VALUE) THEN 'true' ELSE 'false' END AS VALUE FROM (SELECT E.LEFT_OPERAND, E.OPERATOR, E.RIGHT_OPERAND, V1.VALUE AS L FROM EXPRESSIONS AS E LEFT JOIN VARIABLES AS V1 ON E.LEFT_OPERAND=V1.NAME) AS M LEFT JOIN VARIABLES AS V2 ON M.RIGHT_OPERAND=V2.NAME

SELECT LEFT_OPERAND, OPERATOR, RIGHT_OPERAND, CASE WHEN OPERATOR = '=' THEN IF(LEFT_VALUE = RIGHT_VALUE, 'true', 'false') WHEN OPERATOR = '<' THEN IF(LEFT_VALUE < RIGHT_VALUE, 'true', 'false') WHEN OPERATOR = '>' THEN IF(LEFT_VALUE > RIGHT_VALUE, 'true', 'false') END AS VALUE FROM (SELECT E.*, V1.VALUE AS LEFT_VALUE, V2.VALUE AS RIGHT_VALUE FROM EXPRESSIONS AS E JOIN VARIABLES AS V1 ON E.LEFT_OPERAND = V1.NAME JOIN VARIABLES AS V2 ON E.RIGHT_OPERAND = V2.NAME) AS T

SELECT E.LEFT_OPERAND, E.OPERATOR, E.RIGHT_OPERAND, ( CASE WHEN OPERATOR = '<' AND A.VALUE < B.VALUE THEN 'true' WHEN OPERATOR = '>' AND A.VALUE > B.VALUE THEN 'true' WHEN OPERATOR = '=' AND A.VALUE = B.VALUE THEN 'true' ELSE 'false' END )AS VALUE FROM EXPRESSIONS E LEFT JOIN VARIABLES A ON A.NAME = E.LEFT_OPERAND LEFT JOIN VARIABLES B ON B.NAME = E.RIGHT_OPERAND

SELECT LEFT_OPERAND, OPERATOR, RIGHT_OPERAND, (CASE WHEN OPERATOR = '>' THEN IF (V1.VALUE > V2.VALUE, 'true', 'false') WHEN OPERATOR = '=' THEN IF (V1.VALUE = V2.VALUE, 'true', 'false') WHEN OPERATOR = '<' THEN IF (V1.VALUE < V2.VALUE, 'true', 'false') END) AS VALUE FROM EXPRESSIONS LEFT JOIN VARIABLES V1 ON EXPRESSIONS.LEFT_OPERAND = V1.NAME LEFT JOIN VARIABLES V2 ON EXPRESSIONS.RIGHT_OPERAND = V2.NAME

SELECT LEFT_OPERAND,OPERATOR,RIGHT_OPERAND, CASE WHEN (V1.VALUE > V2.VALUE AND E.OPERATOR = '>') OR (V1.VALUE = V2.VALUE AND E.OPERATOR = '=') OR (V1.VALUE < V2.VALUE AND E.OPERATOR = '<') THEN 'true' ELSE 'false' END AS VALUE FROM EXPRESSIONS E JOIN VARIABLES V1 ON E.LEFT_OPERAND = V1.NAME JOIN VARIABLES V2 ON E.RIGHT_OPERAND = V2.NAME

SELECT E.*, CASE WHEN (OPERATOR ='<' AND V1.VALUE < V2.VALUE) OR (OPERATOR ='>' AND V1.VALUE > V2.VALUE) OR (OPERATOR ='=' AND V1.VALUE = V2.VALUE) THEN 'true' ELSE 'false' END AS VALUE FROM EXPRESSIONS E JOIN VARIABLES V1 ON E.LEFT_OPERAND = V1.NAME JOIN VARIABLES V2 ON E.RIGHT_OPERAND = V2.NAME

SELECT E.LEFT_OPERAND AS LEFT_OPERAND, E.OPERATOR AS OPERATOR, E.RIGHT_OPERAND AS RIGHT_OPERAND, CASE WHEN E.OPERATOR = '=' AND V.VALUE = V2.VALUE THEN 'true' WHEN E.OPERATOR = '>' AND V.VALUE > V2.VALUE THEN 'true' WHEN E.OPERATOR = '<' AND V.VALUE < V2.VALUE THEN 'true' ELSE 'false' END AS VALUE FROM EXPRESSIONS E JOIN VARIABLES V ON E.LEFT_OPERAND = V.NAME JOIN VARIABLES V2 ON E.RIGHT_OPERAND = V2.NAME

SELECT A.*, (CASE WHEN B.VALUE > C.VALUE AND A.OPERATOR = '>' THEN 'true' WHEN B.VALUE < C.VALUE AND A.OPERATOR = '<' THEN 'true' WHEN B.VALUE = C.VALUE AND A.OPERATOR = '=' THEN 'true' ELSE 'false' END) AS VALUE FROM EXPRESSIONS A INNER JOIN VARIABLES B ON A.LEFT_OPERAND = B.NAME INNER JOIN VARIABLES C ON A.RIGHT_OPERAND = C.NAME

WITH FORMULA AS ( SELECT (SELECT V.VALUE FROM VARIABLES V WHERE V.NAME = E.LEFT_OPERAND) LEFT_VALUE, (SELECT V.VALUE FROM VARIABLES V WHERE V.NAME = E.RIGHT_OPERAND) RIGHT_VALUE, E.LEFT_OPERAND LEFT_OPERAND, E.RIGHT_OPERAND RIGHT_OPERAND, E.OPERATOR OP FROM EXPRESSIONS E) SELECT LEFT_OPERAND, OP AS OPERATOR, RIGHT_OPERAND, CASE WHEN OP = '>' THEN IF(LEFT_VALUE > RIGHT_VALUE, 'true', 'false') WHEN OP = '<' THEN IF(LEFT_VALUE < RIGHT_VALUE, 'true', 'false') WHEN OP = '=' THEN IF(LEFT_VALUE = RIGHT_VALUE, 'true', 'false') ELSE 'false' END VALUE FROM FORMULA

SELECT T1.LEFT_OPERAND, T1.OPERATOR, T1.RIGHT_OPERAND, (CASE WHEN OPERATOR = '=' AND T2.VALUE = T3.VALUE THEN 'true' WHEN OPERATOR = '>' AND T2.VALUE > T3.VALUE THEN 'true' WHEN OPERATOR = '<' AND T2.VALUE < T3.VALUE THEN 'true' ELSE 'false' END) AS VALUE FROM (EXPRESSIONS AS T1 INNER JOIN VARIABLES AS T2 ON T1.LEFT_OPERAND = T2.NAME) INNER JOIN VARIABLES AS T3 ON T1.RIGHT_OPERAND = T3.NAME

SELECT E.LEFT_OPERAND, E.OPERATOR, E.RIGHT_OPERAND, CASE WHEN E.OPERATOR = '>' THEN IF(V1.VALUE > V2.VALUE,'true','false') WHEN E.OPERATOR = '<' THEN IF(V1.VALUE < V2.VALUE,'true','false') WHEN E.OPERATOR = '=' THEN IF(V1.VALUE = V2.VALUE,'true','false') END VALUE FROM EXPRESSIONS E LEFT JOIN VARIABLES V1 ON E.LEFT_OPERAND = V1.NAME LEFT JOIN VARIABLES V2 ON E.RIGHT_OPERAND = V2.NAME

WITH TEMP AS (SELECT E.*, V.VALUE AS LEFT_NUMBER, V2.VALUE AS RIGHT_NUMBER FROM EXPRESSIONS E LEFT JOIN VARIABLES V ON E.LEFT_OPERAND = V.NAME LEFT JOIN VARIABLES V2 ON E.RIGHT_OPERAND = V2.NAME) SELECT T.LEFT_OPERAND, T.OPERATOR, T.RIGHT_OPERAND, CASE WHEN T.OPERATOR = '>' AND T.LEFT_NUMBER > T.RIGHT_NUMBER THEN 'true' WHEN T.OPERATOR = '<' AND T.LEFT_NUMBER < T.RIGHT_NUMBER THEN 'true' WHEN T.OPERATOR = '=' AND T.LEFT_NUMBER = T.RIGHT_NUMBER THEN 'true' ELSE 'false' END AS VALUE FROM TEMP T

SELECT E.LEFT_OPERAND, E.OPERATOR, E.RIGHT_OPERAND, CASE WHEN E.OPERATOR = '=' THEN IF(V1.VALUE = V2.VALUE, 'true', 'false') WHEN E.OPERATOR = '>' THEN IF(V1.VALUE > V2.VALUE, 'true', 'false') ELSE IF(V1.VALUE < V2.VALUE, 'true', 'false') END AS VALUE FROM EXPRESSIONS E LEFT JOIN VARIABLES V1 ON E.LEFT_OPERAND = V1.NAME LEFT JOIN VARIABLES V2 ON E.RIGHT_OPERAND = V2.NAME

SELECT LEFT_OPERAND, OPERATOR, RIGHT_OPERAND, CASE WHEN V1.VALUE = V2.VALUE AND OPERATOR = '=' THEN 'true' WHEN V1.VALUE > V2.VALUE AND OPERATOR = '>' THEN 'true' WHEN V1.VALUE < V2.VALUE AND OPERATOR = '<' THEN 'true' ELSE 'false' END AS VALUE FROM EXPRESSIONS E LEFT JOIN VARIABLES V1 ON E.LEFT_OPERAND = V1.NAME LEFT JOIN VARIABLES V2 ON E.RIGHT_OPERAND = V2.NAME

SELECT E.LEFT_OPERAND, E.OPERATOR, E.RIGHT_OPERAND, CASE WHEN E.OPERATOR = '<' THEN IF(V1.VALUE < V2.VALUE, 'true', 'false') WHEN E.OPERATOR = '>' THEN IF(V1.VALUE > V2.VALUE, 'true', 'false') ELSE IF(V1.VALUE = V2.VALUE, 'true', 'false') END AS VALUE FROM EXPRESSIONS E JOIN VARIABLES V1 ON V1.NAME=E.LEFT_OPERAND JOIN VARIABLES V2 ON V2.NAME=E.RIGHT_OPERAND

SELECT LEFT_OPERAND, OPERATOR, RIGHT_OPERAND, (CASE WHEN OPERATOR = '<' THEN CASE WHEN V1.VALUE < V2.VALUE THEN 'true' ELSE 'false' END WHEN OPERATOR = '>' THEN CASE WHEN V1.VALUE > V2.VALUE THEN 'true' ELSE 'false' END ELSE CASE WHEN V1.VALUE = V2.VALUE THEN 'true' ELSE 'false' END END) AS VALUE FROM EXPRESSIONS E, VARIABLES V1, VARIABLES V2 WHERE V1.NAME = E.LEFT_OPERAND AND V2.NAME = E.RIGHT_OPERAND

SELECT LEFT_OPERAND, OPERATOR, RIGHT_OPERAND, IF(VAL = 0, 'false', 'true') AS VALUE FROM (WITH TEMP_TABLE AS ( SELECT LEFT_OPERAND, OPERATOR, RIGHT_OPERAND, LEFT_VAL, VALUE AS RIGHT_VAL FROM VARIABLES V INNER JOIN ( SELECT LEFT_OPERAND, OPERATOR, RIGHT_OPERAND, VALUE AS LEFT_VAL, NAME FROM EXPRESSIONS INNER JOIN VARIABLES ON NAME = LEFT_OPERAND) AS T ON V.NAME = T.RIGHT_OPERAND) SELECT LEFT_OPERAND, OPERATOR, RIGHT_OPERAND, CASE WHEN OPERATOR = '>' THEN (LEFT_VAL > RIGHT_VAL) WHEN OPERATOR = '<' THEN (LEFT_VAL < RIGHT_VAL) ELSE (LEFT_VAL = RIGHT_VAL) END AS VAL FROM TEMP_TABLE) AS D

SELECT LEFT_OPERAND, OPERATOR, RIGHT_OPERAND, CASE WHEN OPERATOR = '=' AND L.VALUE = R.VALUE THEN 'true' WHEN OPERATOR = '=' AND L.VALUE != R.VALUE THEN 'false' WHEN OPERATOR = '>' AND L.VALUE > R.VALUE THEN 'true' WHEN OPERATOR = '>' AND L.VALUE <= R.VALUE THEN 'false' WHEN OPERATOR = '<' AND L.VALUE < R.VALUE THEN 'true' WHEN OPERATOR = '<' AND L.VALUE >= R.VALUE THEN 'false' END AS VALUE FROM EXPRESSIONS JOIN VARIABLES L ON EXPRESSIONS.LEFT_OPERAND = L.NAME JOIN VARIABLES R ON EXPRESSIONS.RIGHT_OPERAND = R.NAME

WITH FULL_EXPRESSIONS AS ( SELECT E.LEFT_OPERAND , V1.VALUE AS LEFT_VALUE , E.OPERATOR , V2.VALUE AS RIGHT_VALUE , E.RIGHT_OPERAND FROM EXPRESSIONS E INNER JOIN VARIABLES V1 ON E.LEFT_OPERAND = V1.NAME INNER JOIN VARIABLES V2 ON E.RIGHT_OPERAND = V2.NAME ) SELECT LEFT_OPERAND , OPERATOR , RIGHT_OPERAND , CASE WHEN OPERATOR = '=' THEN IF(LEFT_VALUE = RIGHT_VALUE, 'true', 'false') WHEN OPERATOR = '>' THEN IF(LEFT_VALUE > RIGHT_VALUE, 'true', 'false') WHEN OPERATOR = '<' THEN IF(LEFT_VALUE < RIGHT_VALUE, 'true', 'false') END AS VALUE FROM FULL_EXPRESSIONS

SELECT LEFT_OPERAND, OPERATOR, RIGHT_OPERAND, CASE WHEN E.OPERATOR = '>' THEN IF(V1.VALUE > V2.VALUE, 'true', 'false') WHEN E.OPERATOR = '<' THEN IF(V1.VALUE < V2.VALUE, 'true', 'false') WHEN E.OPERATOR = '=' THEN IF(V1.VALUE = V2.VALUE, 'true', 'false') END AS VALUE FROM EXPRESSIONS AS E LEFT JOIN VARIABLES AS V1 ON E.LEFT_OPERAND = V1.NAME LEFT JOIN VARIABLES AS V2 ON E.RIGHT_OPERAND = V2.NAME

SELECT TB1.LEFT_OPERAND, TB1.OPERATOR, TB1.RIGHT_OPERAND, CASE WHEN OPERATOR = '>' AND TB1.LEFT_VALUE > V2.VALUE THEN 'true' WHEN OPERATOR = '<' AND TB1.LEFT_VALUE < V2.VALUE THEN 'true' WHEN OPERATOR = '=' AND TB1.LEFT_VALUE = V2.VALUE THEN 'true' ELSE 'false' END AS VALUE FROM ( SELECT E.LEFT_OPERAND, V1.VALUE AS LEFT_VALUE, E.OPERATOR, E.RIGHT_OPERAND FROM VARIABLES V1 JOIN EXPRESSIONS E ON V1.NAME = E.LEFT_OPERAND ) TB1 JOIN VARIABLES V2 ON V2.NAME = TB1.RIGHT_OPERAND

SELECT A.LEFT_OPERAND, A.OPERATOR, A.RIGHT_OPERAND, (CASE WHEN A.OPERATOR = '<' AND V1.VALUE < V2.VALUE THEN 'true' WHEN A.OPERATOR = '=' AND V1.VALUE = V2.VALUE THEN 'true' WHEN A.OPERATOR = '>' AND V1.VALUE > V2.VALUE THEN 'true' ELSE 'false' END) AS VALUE FROM EXPRESSIONS A LEFT JOIN VARIABLES V1 ON A.LEFT_OPERAND = V1.NAME LEFT JOIN VARIABLES V2 ON A.RIGHT_OPERAND = V2.NAME

SELECT E.LEFT_OPERAND , E.OPERATOR , E.RIGHT_OPERAND, CASE WHEN OPERATOR LIKE '>' AND V1.VALUE > V2.VALUE THEN 'true' WHEN OPERATOR LIKE '<' AND V1.VALUE < V2.VALUE THEN 'true' WHEN OPERATOR LIKE '=' AND V1.VALUE = V2.VALUE THEN 'true' ELSE 'false' END AS VALUE FROM EXPRESSIONS E JOIN VARIABLES V1 ON V1.NAME = E.LEFT_OPERAND JOIN VARIABLES V2 ON V2.NAME = E.RIGHT_OPERAND

SELECT LEFT_OPERAND, OPERATOR, RIGHT_OPERAND, CASE WHEN OPERATOR='>'AND V1.VALUE > V2.VALUE THEN 'true' WHEN OPERATOR='<' AND V1.VALUE < V2.VALUE THEN 'true' WHEN OPERATOR='=' AND V1.VALUE= V2.VALUE THEN 'true' ELSE 'false' END AS VALUE FROM EXPRESSIONS JOIN VARIABLES V1 ON EXPRESSIONS.LEFT_OPERAND = V1.NAME JOIN VARIABLES V2 ON EXPRESSIONS.RIGHT_OPERAND = V2.NAME

SELECT E.LEFT_OPERAND, E.OPERATOR, E.RIGHT_OPERAND, CASE WHEN OPERATOR='<' AND V1.VALUE<V2.VALUE THEN 'true' WHEN OPERATOR='>' AND V1.VALUE>V2.VALUE THEN 'true' WHEN OPERATOR='=' AND V1.VALUE=V2.VALUE THEN 'true' ELSE 'false' END AS VALUE FROM EXPRESSIONS E JOIN VARIABLES V1 ON E.LEFT_OPERAND=V1.NAME JOIN VARIABLES V2 ON E.RIGHT_OPERAND=V2.NAME

SELECT LEFT_OPERAND, OPERATOR, RIGHT_OPERAND, CASE WHEN OPERATOR = '>' AND (LEFTVAL>RIGHTVAL) THEN 'true' WHEN OPERATOR = '=' AND (LEFTVAL=RIGHTVAL) THEN 'true' WHEN OPERATOR = '<' AND( LEFTVAL<RIGHTVAL) THEN 'true' ELSE 'false' END VALUE FROM (SELECT LEFT_OPERAND, OPERATOR, RIGHT_OPERAND, V1.VALUE AS LEFTVAL, V2.VALUE AS RIGHTVAL FROM EXPRESSIONS E LEFT JOIN VARIABLES V1 ON E.LEFT_OPERAND = V1.NAME LEFT JOIN VARIABLES V2 ON E.RIGHT_OPERAND = V2.NAME) T

SELECT LEFT_OPERAND, OPERATOR, RIGHT_OPERAND, CASE WHEN OPERATOR = '=' AND V.VALUE = V2.VALUE THEN 'true' WHEN OPERATOR = '>' AND V.VALUE > V2.VALUE THEN 'true' WHEN OPERATOR = '<' AND V.VALUE < V2.VALUE THEN 'true' ELSE 'false' END AS VALUE FROM EXPRESSIONS E JOIN VARIABLES V ON V.NAME = E.LEFT_OPERAND JOIN VARIABLES V2 ON V2.NAME = E.RIGHT_OPERAND

SELECT E.*, CASE WHEN E.OPERATOR = '<' AND LEFT_V.VALUE < RIGHT_V.VALUE THEN 'true' WHEN E.OPERATOR = '=' AND LEFT_V.VALUE = RIGHT_V.VALUE THEN 'true' WHEN E.OPERATOR = '>' AND LEFT_V.VALUE > RIGHT_V.VALUE THEN 'true' ELSE 'false' END AS VALUE FROM EXPRESSIONS E JOIN VARIABLES LEFT_V ON E.LEFT_OPERAND = LEFT_V.NAME JOIN VARIABLES RIGHT_V ON E.RIGHT_OPERAND = RIGHT_V.NAME

SELECT S1.LEFT_OPERAND, S1.OPERATOR, S1.RIGHT_OPERAND, CASE WHEN (S1.OPERATOR = '>' AND S1.VALUE_LEFT > S1.VALUE_RIGHT) THEN 'true' WHEN (S1.OPERATOR = '<' AND S1.VALUE_LEFT < S1.VALUE_RIGHT) THEN 'true' WHEN (S1.OPERATOR = '=' AND S1.VALUE_LEFT = S1.VALUE_RIGHT) THEN 'true' ELSE 'false' END AS VALUE FROM (SELECT E.*, V.VALUE AS VALUE_LEFT, V1.VALUE AS VALUE_RIGHT FROM EXPRESSIONS E JOIN VARIABLES V ON V.NAME = E.LEFT_OPERAND JOIN VARIABLES V1 ON V1.NAME = E.RIGHT_OPERAND) S1

SELECT E.LEFT_OPERAND,E.OPERATOR,E.RIGHT_OPERAND, CASE WHEN OPERATOR = '>' AND V1.VALUE > V2.VALUE THEN 'true' WHEN OPERATOR = '<' AND V1.VALUE < V2.VALUE THEN 'true' WHEN OPERATOR = '=' AND V1.VALUE = V2.VALUE THEN 'true' ELSE 'false' END AS VALUE FROM EXPRESSIONS E LEFT JOIN VARIABLES V1 ON E.LEFT_OPERAND = V1.NAME LEFT JOIN VARIABLES V2 ON E.RIGHT_OPERAND = V2.NAME

SELECT E.LEFT_OPERAND, E.OPERATOR, E.RIGHT_OPERAND, CASE WHEN E.OPERATOR LIKE '=' AND V1.VALUE = V2.VALUE THEN 'true' WHEN E.OPERATOR LIKE '>' AND V1.VALUE > V2.VALUE THEN 'true' WHEN E.OPERATOR LIKE '<' AND V1.VALUE < V2.VALUE THEN 'true' ELSE 'false' END AS VALUE FROM EXPRESSIONS E LEFT JOIN VARIABLES V1 ON V1.NAME = E.LEFT_OPERAND LEFT JOIN VARIABLES V2 ON V2.NAME = E.RIGHT_OPERAND

WITH CTE AS (SELECT V.VALUE AS V1, E.LEFT_OPERAND, E.OPERATOR, E.RIGHT_OPERAND, V2.VALUE AS V2 FROM VARIABLES V RIGHT JOIN EXPRESSIONS E ON V.NAME = E.LEFT_OPERAND LEFT JOIN VARIABLES V2 ON V2.NAME = E.RIGHT_OPERAND) SELECT CTE.LEFT_OPERAND, CTE.OPERATOR, CTE.RIGHT_OPERAND, CASE WHEN CTE.V1 = CTE.V2 AND CTE.OPERATOR = '=' THEN 'true' WHEN CTE.V1 > CTE.V2 AND CTE.OPERATOR = '>' THEN 'true' WHEN CTE.V1 < CTE.V2 AND CTE.OPERATOR = '<' THEN 'true' ELSE 'false' END AS VALUE FROM CTE

WITH A AS ( SELECT LEFT_OPERAND, OPERATOR, RIGHT_OPERAND, CASE WHEN V1.VALUE>V2.VALUE THEN '>' WHEN V1.VALUE<V2.VALUE THEN '<' ELSE '=' END AS OPERATOR1 FROM EXPRESSIONS E INNER JOIN VARIABLES V1 ON V1.NAME=LEFT_OPERAND INNER JOIN VARIABLES V2 ON V2.NAME=RIGHT_OPERAND) SELECT LEFT_OPERAND, OPERATOR, RIGHT_OPERAND, IF(OPERATOR=OPERATOR1, 'true', 'false') AS VALUE FROM A

SELECT LEFT_OPERAND,OPERATOR,RIGHT_OPERAND, ( CASE WHEN E.OPERATOR = '=' AND V1.VALUE = V2.VALUE THEN 'true' WHEN E.OPERATOR = '>' AND V1.VALUE > V2.VALUE THEN 'true' WHEN E.OPERATOR = '<' AND V1.VALUE < V2.VALUE THEN 'true' ELSE 'false' END ) AS VALUE FROM EXPRESSIONS AS E JOIN VARIABLES AS V1 ON E.LEFT_OPERAND = V1.NAME JOIN VARIABLES AS V2 ON E.RIGHT_OPERAND = V2.NAME

SELECT E.LEFT_OPERAND, E.OPERATOR, E.RIGHT_OPERAND, CASE WHEN OPERATOR = '>' THEN IF(V1.VALUE > V2.VALUE, 'true', 'false') WHEN OPERATOR = '<' THEN IF(V1.VALUE < V2.VALUE, 'true', 'false') ELSE IF(V1.VALUE = V2.VALUE, 'true', 'false') END AS VALUE FROM EXPRESSIONS E LEFT JOIN VARIABLES V1 ON V1.NAME = E.LEFT_OPERAND LEFT JOIN VARIABLES V2 ON V2.NAME = E.RIGHT_OPERAND

SELECT A.LEFT_OPERAND, A.OPERATOR, A.RIGHT_OPERAND, CASE WHEN A.OPERATOR = '>' AND B.VALUE > C.VALUE THEN 'true' WHEN A.OPERATOR = '<' AND B.VALUE < C.VALUE THEN 'true' WHEN A.OPERATOR = '=' AND B.VALUE = C.VALUE THEN 'true' ELSE 'false' END AS VALUE FROM EXPRESSIONS A LEFT JOIN VARIABLES B ON A.LEFT_OPERAND = B.NAME LEFT JOIN VARIABLES C ON A.RIGHT_OPERAND = C.NAME

SELECT LEFT_OPERAND, OPERATOR, RIGHT_OPERAND, (CASE WHEN OPERATOR = '=' AND A.VALUE = B.VALUE THEN 'true' WHEN OPERATOR = '>' AND A.VALUE > B.VALUE THEN 'true' WHEN OPERATOR = '<' AND A.VALUE < B.VALUE THEN 'true' ELSE 'false' END) AS VALUE FROM EXPRESSIONS X JOIN VARIABLES A ON X.LEFT_OPERAND = A.NAME JOIN VARIABLES B ON X.RIGHT_OPERAND = B.NAME

SELECT ES.LEFT_OPERAND, ES.OPERATOR, ES.RIGHT_OPERAND, CASE WHEN OPERATOR = '>' AND V1.VALUE > V2.VALUE THEN 'true' WHEN OPERATOR = '<' AND V1.VALUE < V2.VALUE THEN 'true' WHEN OPERATOR = '=' AND V1.VALUE = V2.VALUE THEN 'true' ELSE 'false' END AS VALUE FROM EXPRESSIONS AS ES, VARIABLES AS V1, VARIABLES AS V2 WHERE ES.LEFT_OPERAND = V1.NAME AND ES.RIGHT_OPERAND = V2.NAME

SELECT E.LEFT_OPERAND, E.OPERATOR, E.RIGHT_OPERAND, CASE WHEN E.OPERATOR = '>' AND V1.VALUE > V2.VALUE THEN 'true' WHEN E.OPERATOR = '<' AND V1.VALUE < V2.VALUE THEN 'true' WHEN E.OPERATOR = '=' AND V1.VALUE = V2.VALUE THEN 'true' ELSE 'false' END AS VALUE FROM EXPRESSIONS E JOIN VARIABLES V1 ON V1.NAME = E.LEFT_OPERAND JOIN VARIABLES V2 ON V2.NAME = E.RIGHT_OPERAND

WITH BASE AS (SELECT A.* , B.VALUE AS V1, C.VALUE AS V2 FROM EXPRESSIONS A LEFT JOIN VARIABLES B ON A.LEFT_OPERAND=B.NAME LEFT JOIN VARIABLES C ON A.RIGHT_OPERAND=C.NAME) SELECT LEFT_OPERAND, OPERATOR, RIGHT_OPERAND , CASE WHEN OPERATOR='='THEN IF (V1=V2, 'true','false') WHEN OPERATOR='<' THEN IF (V1<V2, 'true','false') WHEN OPERATOR='>' THEN IF (V1>V2, 'true','false') END AS VALUE FROM BASE

SELECT LEFT_OPERAND, OPERATOR, RIGHT_OPERAND, CASE WHEN E.OPERATOR = '>' AND V1.VALUE > V2.VALUE THEN 'true' WHEN E.OPERATOR = '=' AND V1.VALUE = V2.VALUE THEN 'true' WHEN E.OPERATOR = '<' AND V1.VALUE < V2.VALUE THEN 'true' ELSE 'false' END AS VALUE FROM EXPRESSIONS E JOIN VARIABLES V1 ON E.LEFT_OPERAND = V1.NAME JOIN VARIABLES V2 ON E.RIGHT_OPERAND = V2.NAME

SELECT LEFT_OPERAND, OPERATOR, RIGHT_OPERAND, CASE WHEN OPERATOR = '=' THEN IF(V1.VALUE = V2.VALUE, 'true', 'false' ) WHEN OPERATOR = '>' THEN IF(V1.VALUE > V2.VALUE, 'true', 'false' ) WHEN OPERATOR = '<' THEN IF(V1.VALUE < V2.VALUE, 'true', 'false' ) END AS VALUE FROM EXPRESSIONS E LEFT JOIN VARIABLES V1 ON V1.NAME = E.LEFT_OPERAND LEFT JOIN VARIABLES V2 ON V2.NAME = E.RIGHT_OPERAND

SELECT LEFT_OPERAND, OPERATOR, RIGHT_OPERAND, (CASE WHEN OPERATOR = '>' AND V1.VALUE > V2.VALUE THEN 'true' WHEN OPERATOR = '=' AND V1.VALUE = V2.VALUE THEN 'true' WHEN OPERATOR = '<' AND V1.VALUE < V2.VALUE THEN 'true' ELSE 'false' END ) AS VALUE FROM EXPRESSIONS AS E JOIN VARIABLES AS V1 ON V1.NAME = LEFT_OPERAND JOIN VARIABLES AS V2 ON V2.NAME = RIGHT_OPERAND

SELECT LEFT_OPERAND, OPERATOR, RIGHT_OPERAND, CASE WHEN OPERATOR = '<' THEN IF(L.VALUE < R.VALUE, 'true', 'false') WHEN OPERATOR = '>' THEN IF(L.VALUE > R.VALUE, 'true', 'false') WHEN OPERATOR = '=' THEN IF(L.VALUE = R.VALUE, 'true', 'false') END AS VALUE FROM EXPRESSIONS E LEFT JOIN VARIABLES L ON E.LEFT_OPERAND = L.NAME LEFT JOIN VARIABLES R ON E.RIGHT_OPERAND = R.NAME

SELECT LEFT_OPERAND, OPERATOR, RIGHT_OPERAND, CASE WHEN OPERATOR = '=' AND V1.VALUE = V2.VALUE THEN 'true' WHEN OPERATOR = '>' AND V1.VALUE > V2.VALUE THEN 'true' WHEN OPERATOR = '<' AND V1.VALUE < V2.VALUE THEN 'true' ELSE 'false' END AS VALUE FROM EXPRESSIONS E1 JOIN VARIABLES V1 ON E1.LEFT_OPERAND = V1.NAME JOIN VARIABLES V2 ON E1.RIGHT_OPERAND = V2.NAME ORDER BY 1,2,3 DESC

SELECT LEFT_OPERAND, OPERATOR, RIGHT_OPERAND, CASE WHEN OPERATOR = '=' AND V1.VALUE = V2.VALUE THEN 'true' WHEN OPERATOR = '<' AND V1.VALUE < V2.VALUE THEN 'true' WHEN OPERATOR = '>' AND V1.VALUE > V2.VALUE THEN 'true' ELSE 'false' END AS VALUE FROM EXPRESSIONS E, VARIABLES V1, VARIABLES V2 WHERE LEFT_OPERAND = V1.NAME AND RIGHT_OPERAND = V2.NAME

SELECT A.LEFT_OPERAND, A.OPERATOR, A.RIGHT_OPERAND, CASE WHEN A.OPERATOR = '>' AND A.LEFT_VALUE > V2.VALUE THEN 'true' WHEN A.OPERATOR = '=' AND A.LEFT_VALUE = V2.VALUE THEN 'true' WHEN A.OPERATOR = '<' AND A.LEFT_VALUE < V2.VALUE THEN 'true' ELSE 'false' END AS VALUE FROM ( SELECT E1.LEFT_OPERAND, E1.OPERATOR, E1.RIGHT_OPERAND, V1.VALUE AS LEFT_VALUE FROM EXPRESSIONS E1 LEFT JOIN VARIABLES V1 ON E1.LEFT_OPERAND = V1.NAME ) A LEFT JOIN VARIABLES V2 ON A.RIGHT_OPERAND = V2.NAME

SELECT E.LEFT_OPERAND, E.OPERATOR, E.RIGHT_OPERAND, CASE WHEN E.OPERATOR = '=' AND V1.VALUE = V2.VALUE THEN 'true' WHEN E.OPERATOR = '>' AND V1.VALUE > V2.VALUE THEN 'true' WHEN E.OPERATOR = '<' AND V1.VALUE < V2.VALUE THEN 'true' ELSE 'false' END AS VALUE FROM EXPRESSIONS E INNER JOIN VARIABLES V1 ON V1.NAME = E.LEFT_OPERAND INNER JOIN VARIABLES V2 ON V2.NAME = E.RIGHT_OPERAND

SELECT A.LEFT_OPERAND, A.OPERATOR, A.RIGHT_OPERAND, CASE WHEN OPERATOR = '>' AND A.LEFT_VALUE > A.RIGHT_VALUE THEN 'true' WHEN OPERATOR = '<' AND A.LEFT_VALUE < A.RIGHT_VALUE THEN 'true' WHEN OPERATOR = '=' AND A.LEFT_VALUE = A.RIGHT_VALUE THEN 'true' ELSE 'false' END AS VALUE FROM (SELECT E.*, V1.VALUE AS LEFT_VALUE, V2.VALUE AS RIGHT_VALUE FROM EXPRESSIONS E JOIN VARIABLES V1 ON E.LEFT_OPERAND = V1.NAME JOIN VARIABLES V2 ON E.RIGHT_OPERAND = V2.NAME) A

SELECT LEFT_OPERAND, OPERATOR,RIGHT_OPERAND, CASE WHEN OPERATOR='<' AND VL<VR THEN 'true' WHEN OPERATOR='>' AND VL>VR THEN 'true' WHEN OPERATOR = '=' AND VL=VR THEN 'true' ELSE 'false' END AS VALUE FROM (SELECT E.LEFT_OPERAND, V.VALUE AS VL,E.RIGHT_OPERAND, V2.VALUE AS VR, E.OPERATOR FROM EXPRESSIONS AS E JOIN VARIABLES AS V ON V.NAME=E.LEFT_OPERAND JOIN VARIABLES AS V2 ON V2.NAME=E.RIGHT_OPERAND) AS CTE

WITH FULL_TABLE AS( SELECT TMP1.*,TMP2.RIGHT_VALUE FROM ( SELECT A.*,B.VALUE AS LEFT_VALUE FROM EXPRESSIONS AS A LEFT JOIN VARIABLES AS B ON A.LEFT_OPERAND=B.NAME ) AS TMP1 LEFT JOIN ( SELECT A.*,B.VALUE AS RIGHT_VALUE FROM EXPRESSIONS AS A LEFT JOIN VARIABLES AS B ON A.RIGHT_OPERAND=B.NAME) AS TMP2 ON TMP1.LEFT_OPERAND=TMP2.LEFT_OPERAND AND TMP1.OPERATOR=TMP2.OPERATOR AND TMP1.RIGHT_OPERAND=TMP2.RIGHT_OPERAND) SELECT LEFT_OPERAND, OPERATOR, RIGHT_OPERAND, CASE WHEN OPERATOR='>' AND LEFT_VALUE > RIGHT_VALUE THEN 'true' WHEN OPERATOR='<' AND LEFT_VALUE < RIGHT_VALUE THEN 'true' WHEN OPERATOR='=' AND LEFT_VALUE = RIGHT_VALUE THEN 'true' ELSE 'false' END AS VALUE FROM FULL_TABLE

WITH CTE AS( SELECT LEFT_OPERAND, OPERATOR, VALUE AS LEFT_VALUE FROM EXPRESSIONS A LEFT JOIN VARIABLES B ON A.LEFT_OPERAND=B.NAME), CTE2 AS (SELECT LEFT_OPERAND,RIGHT_OPERAND, OPERATOR, VALUE AS RIGHT_VALUE FROM EXPRESSIONS A LEFT JOIN VARIABLES B ON A.RIGHT_OPERAND=B.NAME) SELECT DISTINCT CTE.LEFT_OPERAND, CTE.OPERATOR, CTE2.RIGHT_OPERAND, CASE WHEN LEFT_VALUE>RIGHT_VALUE AND CTE.OPERATOR='>' THEN 'true' WHEN LEFT_VALUE=RIGHT_VALUE AND CTE.OPERATOR='=' THEN 'true' WHEN LEFT_VALUE<RIGHT_VALUE AND CTE.OPERATOR='<' THEN 'true' ELSE 'false' END AS VALUE FROM CTE JOIN CTE2 ON CTE.LEFT_OPERAND=CTE2.LEFT_OPERAND AND CTE.OPERATOR=CTE2.OPERATOR

SELECT LEFT_OPERAND, OPERATOR, RIGHT_OPERAND, CASE WHEN OPERATOR = '>' THEN IF(LEFT_VALUE > RIGHT_VALUE, 'true', 'false') WHEN OPERATOR = '=' THEN IF(LEFT_VALUE = RIGHT_VALUE, 'true', 'false') ELSE IF(LEFT_VALUE < RIGHT_VALUE, 'true', 'false') END AS VALUE FROM( SELECT LEFT_OPERAND, V1.VALUE AS LEFT_VALUE, OPERATOR, RIGHT_OPERAND, V2.VALUE AS RIGHT_VALUE FROM EXPRESSIONS JOIN VARIABLES V1 ON EXPRESSIONS.LEFT_OPERAND = V1.NAME JOIN VARIABLES V2 ON EXPRESSIONS.RIGHT_OPERAND = V2.NAME )T

SELECT E.LEFT_OPERAND,E.OPERATOR,E.RIGHT_OPERAND, CASE WHEN OPERATOR='=' THEN IF(T1.VALUE=T2.VALUE,'true','false') WHEN OPERATOR='>' THEN IF(T1.VALUE>T2.VALUE,'true','false') WHEN OPERATOR='<' THEN IF(T1.VALUE<T2.VALUE,'true','false') END AS VALUE FROM EXPRESSIONS E JOIN VARIABLES T1 ON T1.NAME=E.LEFT_OPERAND JOIN VARIABLES T2 ON T2.NAME=E.RIGHT_OPERAND
