SELECT E.*, CASE WHEN (E.OPERATOR = '>' AND VL.VALUE > VR.VALUE) THEN 'true' WHEN (E.OPERATOR = '<' AND VL.VALUE < VR.VALUE) THEN 'true' WHEN (E.OPERATOR = '=' AND VL.VALUE= VR.VALUE) THEN 'true' ELSE 'false' END AS VALUE FROM EXPRESSIONS E , VARIABLES VR , VARIABLES VL WHERE E.LEFT_OPERAND = VL.NAME AND E.RIGHT_OPERAND = VR.NAME

SELECT E.*, (CASE WHEN OPERATOR = '>' AND V1.VALUE > V2.VALUE THEN 'true' WHEN OPERATOR = '<' AND V1.VALUE < V2.VALUE THEN 'true' WHEN OPERATOR = '=' AND V1.VALUE = V2.VALUE THEN 'true' ELSE 'false' END) AS VALUE FROM VARIABLES V1, VARIABLES V2, EXPRESSIONS E WHERE V1.NAME = E.LEFT_OPERAND AND V2.NAME = E.RIGHT_OPERAND

WITH CTE AS ( SELECT LEFT_OPERAND, OPERATOR, RIGHT_OPERAND, V1.VALUE AS LEFT_VALUE, V2.VALUE AS RIGHT_VALUE FROM EXPRESSIONS E LEFT JOIN VARIABLES V1 ON E.LEFT_OPERAND= V1.NAME INNER JOIN VARIABLES V2 ON E.RIGHT_OPERAND=V2.NAME ) SELECT LEFT_OPERAND, OPERATOR, RIGHT_OPERAND, CASE WHEN OPERATOR = '<' AND LEFT_VALUE<RIGHT_VALUE THEN 'true' WHEN OPERATOR = '>' AND LEFT_VALUE>RIGHT_VALUE THEN 'true' WHEN OPERATOR = '=' AND LEFT_VALUE=RIGHT_VALUE THEN 'true' ELSE 'false' END AS VALUE FROM CTE

WITH T1 AS( SELECT LEFT_OPERAND, RIGHT_OPERAND, T11.VALUE AS LEFT_NUM, T12.VALUE AS RIGHT_NUM, OPERATOR FROM EXPRESSIONS JOIN VARIABLES T11 ON T11.NAME = EXPRESSIONS.LEFT_OPERAND JOIN VARIABLES T12 ON T12.NAME = EXPRESSIONS.RIGHT_OPERAND ) SELECT LEFT_OPERAND, OPERATOR, RIGHT_OPERAND, CASE WHEN (OPERATOR = '=' AND LEFT_NUM = RIGHT_NUM) OR (OPERATOR = '>' AND LEFT_NUM > RIGHT_NUM) OR (OPERATOR = '<' AND LEFT_NUM < RIGHT_NUM) THEN 'true' ELSE 'false' END AS VALUE FROM T1

SELECT LEFT_OPERAND, OPERATOR, RIGHT_OPERAND, (CASE WHEN OPERATOR = '=' THEN IF(A.VALUE = B.VALUE,'true','false') WHEN OPERATOR = '>' THEN IF(A.VALUE > B.VALUE,'true','false') WHEN OPERATOR = '<' THEN IF(A.VALUE < B.VALUE,'true','false') END) AS VALUE FROM EXPRESSIONS X LEFT JOIN VARIABLES A ON X.LEFT_OPERAND = A.NAME LEFT JOIN VARIABLES B ON X.RIGHT_OPERAND = B.NAME

WITH X AS ( SELECT V1.VALUE AS LEFT_VALUE, V2.VALUE AS RIGHT_VALUE, LEFT_OPERAND , OPERATOR , RIGHT_OPERAND FROM VARIABLES V1, EXPRESSIONS E, VARIABLES V2 WHERE E.LEFT_OPERAND = V1.NAME AND E.RIGHT_OPERAND = V2.NAME) SELECT LEFT_OPERAND , OPERATOR , RIGHT_OPERAND , CASE WHEN OPERATOR = '=' AND LEFT_VALUE=RIGHT_VALUE THEN 'true' WHEN OPERATOR = '<' AND LEFT_VALUE<RIGHT_VALUE THEN 'true' WHEN OPERATOR = '>' AND LEFT_VALUE>RIGHT_VALUE THEN 'true' ELSE 'false' END AS VALUE FROM X

SELECT A.LEFT_OPERAND, A.OPERATOR, A.RIGHT_OPERAND, CASE WHEN OPERATOR = '=' AND B.VALUE = C.VALUE OR OPERATOR = '<' AND B.VALUE < C.VALUE OR OPERATOR = '>' AND B.VALUE > C.VALUE THEN 'true' ELSE 'false' END AS VALUE FROM EXPRESSIONS A LEFT OUTER JOIN VARIABLES B ON A.LEFT_OPERAND = B.NAME LEFT OUTER JOIN VARIABLES C ON A.RIGHT_OPERAND = C.NAME

SELECT E.LEFT_OPERAND, OPERATOR, E.RIGHT_OPERAND, (CASE WHEN OPERATOR = '>' AND V1.VALUE > V2.VALUE THEN 'true' WHEN OPERATOR = '<' AND V1.VALUE< V2.VALUE THEN 'true' WHEN OPERATOR = '=' AND V1.VALUE= V2.VALUE THEN 'true' ELSE 'false' END) AS VALUE FROM EXPRESSIONS E LEFT JOIN VARIABLES V1 ON E.LEFT_OPERAND = V1.NAME LEFT JOIN VARIABLES V2 ON E.RIGHT_OPERAND = V2.NAME

WITH TEMP AS ( SELECT E.LEFT_OPERAND , V.VALUE AS LEFT_VALUE , E.OPERATOR , E.RIGHT_OPERAND , V2.VALUE AS RIGHT_VALUE FROM EXPRESSIONS AS E LEFT JOIN VARIABLES AS V ON V.NAME = E.LEFT_OPERAND LEFT JOIN VARIABLES AS V2 ON V2.NAME = E.RIGHT_OPERAND ) SELECT LEFT_OPERAND , OPERATOR , RIGHT_OPERAND , CASE WHEN LEFT_VALUE > RIGHT_VALUE AND OPERATOR = '>' THEN 'true' WHEN LEFT_VALUE = RIGHT_VALUE AND OPERATOR = '=' THEN 'true' WHEN LEFT_VALUE < RIGHT_VALUE AND OPERATOR = '<' THEN 'true' ELSE 'false' END AS VALUE FROM TEMP

WITH CTE AS ( SELECT E.*, V1.VALUE AS LEFT_VALUE , V2.VALUE AS RIGHT_VALUE FROM EXPRESSIONS E INNER JOIN VARIABLES V1 ON E.LEFT_OPERAND = V1.NAME INNER JOIN VARIABLES V2 ON E.RIGHT_OPERAND = V2.NAME ) SELECT LEFT_OPERAND, OPERATOR, RIGHT_OPERAND, CASE WHEN OPERATOR = '=' THEN IF(LEFT_VALUE=RIGHT_VALUE, 'true', 'false') WHEN OPERATOR = '>' THEN IF(LEFT_VALUE>RIGHT_VALUE, 'true', 'false') WHEN OPERATOR = '<' THEN IF(LEFT_VALUE<RIGHT_VALUE, 'true', 'false') END AS VALUE FROM CTE ORDER BY 1, 2

SELECT LEFT_OPERAND, OPERATOR, RIGHT_OPERAND, CASE WHEN OPERATOR = '>' THEN IF(V1.VALUE > V2.VALUE, 'true', 'false') WHEN OPERATOR = '=' THEN IF(V1.VALUE = V2.VALUE, 'true', 'false') ELSE IF(V1.VALUE < V2.VALUE, 'true', 'false') END AS VALUE FROM EXPRESSIONS E INNER JOIN VARIABLES V1 ON E.LEFT_OPERAND = V1.NAME INNER JOIN VARIABLES V2 ON E.RIGHT_OPERAND = V2.NAME

SELECT E.LEFT_OPERAND, E.OPERATOR, E.RIGHT_OPERAND, (CASE WHEN E.OPERATOR = '<' AND TB1.VALUE < TB2.VALUE THEN 'true' WHEN E.OPERATOR = '>' AND TB1.VALUE > TB2.VALUE THEN 'true' WHEN E.OPERATOR = '=' AND TB1.VALUE = TB2.VALUE THEN 'true' ELSE 'false' END) AS VALUE FROM EXPRESSIONS E JOIN VARIABLES AS TB1 ON TB1.NAME = E.LEFT_OPERAND JOIN VARIABLES AS TB2 ON TB2.NAME = E.RIGHT_OPERAND

SELECT LEFT_OPERAND, OPERATOR, RIGHT_OPERAND, CASE OPERATOR WHEN '<' THEN IF(LV.VALUE < RV.VALUE, 'true', 'false') WHEN '>' THEN IF(LV.VALUE > RV.VALUE, 'true', 'false') ELSE IF(LV.VALUE = RV.VALUE, 'true', 'false') END AS VALUE FROM EXPRESSIONS JOIN VARIABLES LV ON LEFT_OPERAND = LV.NAME JOIN VARIABLES RV ON RIGHT_OPERAND = RV.NAME

WITH C1 AS ( SELECT E.*, V.VALUE AS LEFT_V FROM EXPRESSIONS E LEFT JOIN VARIABLES V ON E.LEFT_OPERAND = V.NAME ), C2 AS ( SELECT E.*, V.VALUE AS RIGHT_V FROM EXPRESSIONS E LEFT JOIN VARIABLES V ON E.RIGHT_OPERAND = V.NAME ) SELECT C1.LEFT_OPERAND, C1.OPERATOR, C1.RIGHT_OPERAND, (CASE WHEN C1.OPERATOR = '>' AND C1.LEFT_V > C2.RIGHT_V THEN 'true' WHEN C1.OPERATOR = '>' AND C1.LEFT_V < C2.RIGHT_V THEN 'false' WHEN C1.OPERATOR = '<' AND C1.LEFT_V < C2.RIGHT_V THEN 'true' WHEN C1.OPERATOR = '<' AND C1.LEFT_V > C2.RIGHT_V THEN 'false' WHEN C1.OPERATOR = '=' AND C1.LEFT_V = C2.RIGHT_V THEN 'true' ELSE 'false' END) AS VALUE FROM C1 LEFT JOIN C2 ON C1.LEFT_OPERAND = C2.LEFT_OPERAND AND C1.OPERATOR = C2.OPERATOR AND C1.RIGHT_OPERAND = C2.RIGHT_OPERAND

WITH VALS AS ( SELECT LEFT_OPERAND, V.VALUE L_VALUE, OPERATOR, RIGHT_OPERAND, V1.VALUE R_VALUE FROM EXPRESSIONS E JOIN VARIABLES V ON V.NAME=E.LEFT_OPERAND LEFT JOIN VARIABLES V1 ON V1.NAME = E.RIGHT_OPERAND ) SELECT LEFT_OPERAND, OPERATOR, RIGHT_OPERAND, CASE WHEN OPERATOR='>' AND L_VALUE>R_VALUE THEN 'true' WHEN OPERATOR='<' AND L_VALUE<R_VALUE THEN 'true' WHEN OPERATOR='=' AND L_VALUE=R_VALUE THEN 'true' ELSE 'false' END AS VALUE FROM VALS

SELECT E.LEFT_OPERAND, E.OPERATOR, E.RIGHT_OPERAND , CASE WHEN E.OPERATOR = '<' AND E.LEFT_OPERAND = L.NAME AND E.RIGHT_OPERAND = R.NAME THEN CASE WHEN L.VALUE < R.VALUE THEN 'true' ELSE 'false' END WHEN E.OPERATOR = '<' AND E.LEFT_OPERAND = L.NAME AND E.RIGHT_OPERAND = R.NAME THEN CASE WHEN R.VALUE < L.VALUE THEN 'true' ELSE 'false' END WHEN E.OPERATOR = '>' AND E.LEFT_OPERAND = L.NAME AND E.RIGHT_OPERAND = R.NAME THEN CASE WHEN L.VALUE > R.VALUE THEN 'true' ELSE 'false' END WHEN E.OPERATOR = '>' AND E.LEFT_OPERAND = L.NAME AND E.RIGHT_OPERAND = R.NAME THEN CASE WHEN R.VALUE > L.VALUE THEN 'true' ELSE 'false' END WHEN E.OPERATOR = '=' THEN CASE WHEN E.LEFT_OPERAND = E.RIGHT_OPERAND AND L.VALUE = L.VALUE THEN 'true' WHEN E.LEFT_OPERAND <> E.RIGHT_OPERAND AND L.VALUE = R.VALUE THEN 'true' ELSE 'false' END ELSE 'false' END AS VALUE FROM EXPRESSIONS E LEFT OUTER JOIN VARIABLES L ON E.LEFT_OPERAND = L.NAME LEFT OUTER JOIN VARIABLES R ON E.RIGHT_OPERAND = R.NAME

WITH CTE AS (SELECT *, (CASE WHEN OPERATOR='>' THEN ((SELECT VALUE FROM VARIABLES WHERE NAME=A.LEFT_OPERAND)> (SELECT VALUE FROM VARIABLES WHERE NAME=A.RIGHT_OPERAND)) WHEN OPERATOR='<' THEN ((SELECT VALUE FROM VARIABLES WHERE NAME=A.LEFT_OPERAND)< (SELECT VALUE FROM VARIABLES WHERE NAME=A.RIGHT_OPERAND)) WHEN OPERATOR='=' THEN ((SELECT VALUE FROM VARIABLES WHERE NAME=A.LEFT_OPERAND)= (SELECT VALUE FROM VARIABLES WHERE NAME=A.RIGHT_OPERAND)) END) AS VALUE FROM EXPRESSIONS A) SELECT LEFT_OPERAND, OPERATOR, RIGHT_OPERAND, (CASE WHEN VALUE=0 THEN 'false' ELSE 'true' END) AS VALUE FROM CTE

WITH CTE AS (SELECT LEFT_OPERAND, V1.VALUE AS LEF, OPERATOR, RIGHT_OPERAND, V2.VALUE AS RIG FROM EXPRESSIONS E INNER JOIN VARIABLES V1 ON V1.NAME = E.LEFT_OPERAND INNER JOIN VARIABLES V2 ON V2.NAME = E.RIGHT_OPERAND) SELECT LEFT_OPERAND, OPERATOR, RIGHT_OPERAND, CASE WHEN LEF>RIG AND OPERATOR = '>' THEN 'true' WHEN LEF<RIG AND OPERATOR = '<' THEN 'true' WHEN LEF=RIG AND OPERATOR = '=' THEN 'true' ELSE 'false' END AS VALUE FROM CTE

SELECT EX.LEFT_OPERAND ,EX.OPERATOR ,EX.RIGHT_OPERAND ,CASE WHEN OPERATOR='<' AND VAR1.VALUE < VAR2.VALUE THEN 'true' WHEN OPERATOR='>' AND VAR1.VALUE > VAR2.VALUE THEN 'true' WHEN OPERATOR='=' AND VAR1.VALUE=VAR2.VALUE THEN 'true' ELSE 'false' END AS VALUE FROM EXPRESSIONS EX LEFT JOIN VARIABLES VAR1 ON EX.LEFT_OPERAND=VAR1.NAME LEFT JOIN VARIABLES VAR2 ON EX.RIGHT_OPERAND=VAR2.NAME

SELECT LEFT_OPERAND, OPERATOR, RIGHT_OPERAND, CASE WHEN OPERATOR = '>' AND V1.VALUE > V2.VALUE THEN 'true' WHEN OPERATOR = '<' AND V1.VALUE < V2.VALUE THEN 'true' WHEN OPERATOR = '=' AND V1.VALUE = V2.VALUE THEN 'true' ELSE 'false' END AS VALUE FROM EXPRESSIONS E JOIN VARIABLES V1 ON V1.NAME = E.LEFT_OPERAND JOIN VARIABLES V2 ON V2.NAME = E.RIGHT_OPERAND

SELECT A.LEFT_OPERAND, A.OPERATOR, A.RIGHT_OPERAND, CASE WHEN OPERATOR = '=' THEN IF(B.VALUE = C.VALUE, 'true','false') WHEN OPERATOR = '<' THEN IF(B.VALUE < C.VALUE, 'true','false') WHEN OPERATOR = '>' THEN IF (B.VALUE > C.VALUE, 'true', 'false') END AS VALUE FROM EXPRESSIONS A JOIN VARIABLES B ON A.LEFT_OPERAND = B.NAME JOIN VARIABLES C ON A.RIGHT_OPERAND = C.NAME

SELECT E.LEFT_OPERAND , E.OPERATOR , E.RIGHT_OPERAND, CASE WHEN E.OPERATOR ='>' THEN CASE WHEN (V1.VALUE > V2.VALUE ) THEN 'true' ELSE 'false' END WHEN E.OPERATOR ='<' THEN CASE WHEN (V1.VALUE < V2.VALUE ) THEN 'true' ELSE 'false' END WHEN E.OPERATOR ='=' THEN CASE WHEN (V1.VALUE = V2.VALUE ) THEN 'true' ELSE 'false' END END AS VALUE FROM EXPRESSIONS E JOIN VARIABLES V1 ON (E.LEFT_OPERAND =V1.NAME) JOIN VARIABLES V2 ON (E.RIGHT_OPERAND =V2.NAME)

SELECT E.LEFT_OPERAND, E.OPERATOR, E.RIGHT_OPERAND, CASE WHEN E.OPERATOR = '=' THEN IF(V.VALUE = VR.VALUE ,'true','false') WHEN E.OPERATOR = '>' THEN IF(V.VALUE > VR.VALUE ,'true','false') WHEN E.OPERATOR = '<' THEN IF(V.VALUE < VR.VALUE ,'true','false') END VALUE FROM EXPRESSIONS E LEFT JOIN VARIABLES V ON V.NAME = E.LEFT_OPERAND LEFT JOIN VARIABLES VR ON VR.NAME = E.RIGHT_OPERAND

SELECT LEFT_OPERAND, OPERATOR, RIGHT_OPERAND, (CASE WHEN (OPERATOR='=' AND V1.VALUE=V2.VALUE) OR (OPERATOR='>' AND V1.VALUE>V2.VALUE) OR (OPERATOR='<' AND V1.VALUE<V2.VALUE) THEN 'true' ELSE 'false' END) AS VALUE FROM EXPRESSIONS JOIN VARIABLES V1 ON LEFT_OPERAND=V1.NAME JOIN VARIABLES V2 ON RIGHT_OPERAND=V2.NAME

WITH T AS( SELECT E.*, V1.VALUE - V2.VALUE AS DELTA FROM EXPRESSIONS E JOIN VARIABLES V1 ON E.LEFT_OPERAND = V1.NAME JOIN VARIABLES V2 ON E.RIGHT_OPERAND = V2.NAME ORDER BY RIGHT_OPERAND DESC, OPERATOR ) SELECT LEFT_OPERAND, OPERATOR, RIGHT_OPERAND, CASE WHEN (OPERATOR = '>' AND DELTA > 0) THEN 'true' WHEN (OPERATOR = '>' AND DELTA <= 0) THEN 'false' WHEN (OPERATOR = '<' AND DELTA >= 0) THEN 'false' WHEN (OPERATOR = '<' AND DELTA < 0) THEN 'true' WHEN (OPERATOR = '=' AND DELTA = 0) THEN 'true' WHEN (OPERATOR = '=' AND DELTA <> 0) THEN 'false' ELSE NULL END AS VALUE FROM T

SELECT A.LEFT_OPERAND, A.OPERATOR, A.RIGHT_OPERAND, CASE WHEN A.LEFT_VALUE = A.RIGHT_VALUE AND A.OPERATOR = '=' THEN 'true' WHEN A.LEFT_VALUE > A.RIGHT_VALUE AND A.OPERATOR = '>' THEN 'true' WHEN A.LEFT_VALUE < A.RIGHT_VALUE AND A.OPERATOR = '<' THEN 'true' ELSE 'false' END AS VALUE FROM (SELECT E.LEFT_OPERAND, VA.VALUE AS LEFT_VALUE, E.OPERATOR, E.RIGHT_OPERAND, VB.VALUE AS RIGHT_VALUE FROM EXPRESSIONS E JOIN VARIABLES VA ON E.LEFT_OPERAND = VA.NAME JOIN VARIABLES VB ON E.RIGHT_OPERAND = VB.NAME) A

SELECT E.LEFT_OPERAND ,E.OPERATOR ,E.RIGHT_OPERAND ,CASE WHEN E.OPERATOR ='<' THEN IF(V.VALUE <V1.VALUE ,'true','false') WHEN E.OPERATOR ='>' THEN IF(V.VALUE >V1.VALUE ,'true','false') WHEN E.OPERATOR ='=' THEN IF(V.VALUE =V1.VALUE ,'true','false') END AS VALUE FROM EXPRESSIONS AS E LEFT JOIN VARIABLES AS V ON (V.NAME=E.LEFT_OPERAND) LEFT JOIN VARIABLES AS V1 ON (V1.NAME=E.RIGHT_OPERAND)

SELECT LEFT_OPERAND, OPERATOR, RIGHT_OPERAND, (CASE WHEN OPERATOR='>' THEN IF(V1.VALUE > V2.VALUE, 'true', 'false') WHEN OPERATOR='<' THEN IF(V1.VALUE < V2.VALUE, 'true', 'false') WHEN OPERATOR='=' THEN IF(V1.VALUE = V2.VALUE, 'true', 'false') END) AS VALUE FROM VARIABLES V1 INNER JOIN EXPRESSIONS E ON V1.NAME=E.LEFT_OPERAND INNER JOIN VARIABLES V2 ON E.RIGHT_OPERAND=V2.NAME

SELECT LEFT_OPERAND, OPERATOR, RIGHT_OPERAND, CASE WHEN OPERATOR = '>' AND V1.VALUE > V2.VALUE THEN 'true' WHEN OPERATOR = '<' AND V1.VALUE < V2.VALUE THEN 'true' WHEN OPERATOR = '=' AND V1.VALUE = V2.VALUE THEN 'true' ELSE 'false' END AS VALUE FROM EXPRESSIONS EXP LEFT JOIN VARIABLES V1 ON V1.NAME = EXP.LEFT_OPERAND LEFT JOIN VARIABLES V2 ON V2.NAME = EXP.RIGHT_OPERAND

SELECT LEFT_OPERAND, OPERATOR, RIGHT_OPERAND, CASE WHEN OPERATOR='>' THEN IF(A.VALUE>B.VALUE, 'true', 'false') WHEN OPERATOR='<' THEN IF(A.VALUE<B.VALUE, 'true', 'false') WHEN OPERATOR='=' THEN IF(A.VALUE=B.VALUE, 'true', 'false') END AS VALUE FROM EXPRESSIONS INNER JOIN VARIABLES A ON A.NAME=EXPRESSIONS.LEFT_OPERAND INNER JOIN VARIABLES B ON B.NAME=EXPRESSIONS.RIGHT_OPERAND

SELECT A.LEFT_OPERAND, A.OPERATOR, A.RIGHT_OPERAND, CASE WHEN OPERATOR = '=' AND B.VALUE = C.VALUE THEN 'true' WHEN OPERATOR = '>' AND B.VALUE > C.VALUE THEN 'true' WHEN OPERATOR = '<' AND B.VALUE < C.VALUE THEN 'true' ELSE 'false' END AS VALUE FROM EXPRESSIONS A LEFT JOIN VARIABLES B ON A.LEFT_OPERAND = B.NAME LEFT JOIN VARIABLES C ON A.RIGHT_OPERAND = C.NAME

SELECT L.LEFT_OPERAND, L.OPERATOR, R.RIGHT_OPERAND, CASE WHEN L.OPERATOR='>' AND (L.VALUE>R.VALUE) THEN 'true' WHEN L.OPERATOR='<' AND (L.VALUE<R.VALUE) THEN 'true' WHEN L.OPERATOR='=' AND (L.VALUE=R.VALUE) THEN 'true' ELSE 'false' END AS VALUE FROM (SELECT E.LEFT_OPERAND, V.VALUE, E.OPERATOR, E.RIGHT_OPERAND FROM VARIABLES V, EXPRESSIONS E WHERE 1=1 AND V.NAME=E.LEFT_OPERAND) L, (SELECT E.RIGHT_OPERAND, V.VALUE, E.OPERATOR, E.LEFT_OPERAND FROM VARIABLES V, EXPRESSIONS E WHERE 1=1 AND V.NAME=E.RIGHT_OPERAND) R WHERE 1=1 AND L.LEFT_OPERAND=R.LEFT_OPERAND AND L.RIGHT_OPERAND=R.RIGHT_OPERAND AND L.OPERATOR=R.OPERATOR

SELECT LEFT_OPERAND,OPERATOR,RIGHT_OPERAND ,CASE WHEN A.VALUE < B.VALUE AND OPERATOR='<' THEN 'true' WHEN A.VALUE > B.VALUE AND OPERATOR='>' THEN 'true' WHEN A.VALUE = B.VALUE AND OPERATOR='=' THEN 'true' ELSE 'false' END AS VALUE FROM EXPRESSIONS INNER JOIN VARIABLES A ON LEFT_OPERAND=A.NAME INNER JOIN VARIABLES B ON RIGHT_OPERAND=B.NAME

SELECT LEFT_OPERAND, OPERATOR, RIGHT_OPERAND, CASE WHEN (CASE WHEN OPERATOR = '<' THEN LEFT_VALUE < RIGHT_VALUE WHEN OPERATOR = '>' THEN LEFT_VALUE > RIGHT_VALUE ELSE LEFT_VALUE = RIGHT_VALUE END) = 1 THEN 'true' ELSE 'false' END AS VALUE FROM ( SELECT LEFT_OPERAND, T2.VALUE AS LEFT_VALUE, OPERATOR, RIGHT_OPERAND, T3.VALUE AS RIGHT_VALUE FROM EXPRESSIONS T1 LEFT JOIN VARIABLES T2 ON T1.LEFT_OPERAND = T2.NAME LEFT JOIN VARIABLES T3 ON T1.RIGHT_OPERAND = T3.NAME) SUBQ1

SELECT E.LEFT_OPERAND, E.OPERATOR, E.RIGHT_OPERAND, ( CASE WHEN E.OPERATOR = '>' THEN CASE WHEN V1.VALUE > V2.VALUE THEN 'true' ELSE 'false' END WHEN E.OPERATOR = '<' THEN CASE WHEN V1.VALUE < V2.VALUE THEN 'true' ELSE 'false' END ELSE CASE WHEN V1.VALUE = V2.VALUE THEN 'true' ELSE 'false' END END ) AS VALUE FROM EXPRESSIONS E INNER JOIN VARIABLES V1 ON E.LEFT_OPERAND = V1.NAME INNER JOIN VARIABLES V2 ON E.RIGHT_OPERAND = V2.NAME

SELECT LEFT_OPERAND, OPERATOR, RIGHT_OPERAND, CASE WHEN OPERATOR LIKE '=' AND LEFT_OPERAND_VALUE = RIGHT_OPERAND_VALUE THEN 'true' WHEN OPERATOR LIKE '>' AND LEFT_OPERAND_VALUE > RIGHT_OPERAND_VALUE THEN 'true' WHEN OPERATOR LIKE '<' AND LEFT_OPERAND_VALUE < RIGHT_OPERAND_VALUE THEN 'true' ELSE 'false' END AS VALUE FROM ( SELECT A.LEFT_OPERAND, A.OPERATOR, A.RIGHT_OPERAND, A.VALUE AS LEFT_OPERAND_VALUE, B.VALUE AS RIGHT_OPERAND_VALUE FROM ( SELECT * FROM EXPRESSIONS E LEFT JOIN VARIABLES V ON LEFT_OPERAND = NAME ) A JOIN ( SELECT * FROM EXPRESSIONS E LEFT JOIN VARIABLES V ON RIGHT_OPERAND = NAME ) B ON A.LEFT_OPERAND = B.LEFT_OPERAND AND A.OPERATOR = B.OPERATOR AND A.RIGHT_OPERAND = B.RIGHT_OPERAND ) C

WITH CTE AS (SELECT *, (SELECT V.VALUE FROM VARIABLES V WHERE V.NAME = E.LEFT_OPERAND) AS LEFT_VALUE, (SELECT V.VALUE FROM VARIABLES V WHERE V.NAME = E.RIGHT_OPERAND) AS RIGHT_VALUE FROM EXPRESSIONS E) SELECT CTE.LEFT_OPERAND, CTE.OPERATOR, CTE.RIGHT_OPERAND, CASE WHEN OPERATOR = '>' THEN CASE WHEN LEFT_VALUE > RIGHT_VALUE THEN 'true' ELSE 'false' END WHEN OPERATOR = '<' THEN CASE WHEN LEFT_VALUE < RIGHT_VALUE THEN 'true' ELSE 'false' END WHEN OPERATOR = '=' THEN CASE WHEN LEFT_VALUE = RIGHT_VALUE THEN 'true' ELSE 'false' END END AS VALUE FROM CTE

SELECT LEFT_OPERAND, OPERATOR, RIGHT_OPERAND, (CASE WHEN E.OPERATOR = '>' AND V1.VALUE > V2.VALUE THEN 'true' WHEN E.OPERATOR = '<' AND V1.VALUE < V2.VALUE THEN 'true' WHEN E.OPERATOR = '=' AND V1.VALUE = V2.VALUE THEN 'true' ELSE 'false' END ) AS VALUE FROM EXPRESSIONS E LEFT JOIN VARIABLES V1 ON E.LEFT_OPERAND = V1.NAME LEFT JOIN VARIABLES V2 ON E.RIGHT_OPERAND = V2.NAME

SELECT LEFT_OPERAND, OPERATOR, RIGHT_OPERAND, CASE WHEN E.OPERATOR = '>' AND (SELECT VALUE FROM VARIABLES WHERE NAME = E.LEFT_OPERAND) > (SELECT VALUE FROM VARIABLES WHERE NAME = E.RIGHT_OPERAND) THEN 'true' WHEN E.OPERATOR = '=' AND (SELECT VALUE FROM VARIABLES WHERE NAME = E.LEFT_OPERAND) = (SELECT VALUE FROM VARIABLES WHERE NAME = E.RIGHT_OPERAND) THEN 'true' WHEN E.OPERATOR = '<' AND (SELECT VALUE FROM VARIABLES WHERE NAME = E.LEFT_OPERAND) < (SELECT VALUE FROM VARIABLES WHERE NAME = E.RIGHT_OPERAND) THEN 'true' ELSE 'false' END AS VALUE FROM EXPRESSIONS E

SELECT A.LEFT_OPERAND, A.OPERATOR, A.RIGHT_OPERAND, CASE WHEN (OPERATOR ='<' AND B.VALUE<C.VALUE) OR (OPERATOR ='=' AND B.VALUE=C.VALUE) OR (OPERATOR ='>' AND B.VALUE>C.VALUE) THEN 'true' ELSE 'false' END AS VALUE FROM EXPRESSIONS A JOIN VARIABLES B ON A.LEFT_OPERAND = B.NAME JOIN VARIABLES C ON A.RIGHT_OPERAND=C.NAME

SELECT V1.NAME AS LEFT_OPERAND, E.OPERATOR, V2.NAME AS RIGHT_OPERAND, CASE WHEN OPERATOR = '=' THEN IF(V1.VALUE = V2.VALUE, 'true', 'false' ) WHEN OPERATOR = '<' THEN IF(V1.VALUE < V2.VALUE, 'true', 'false' ) WHEN OPERATOR = '>' THEN IF(V1.VALUE > V2.VALUE, 'true', 'false' ) END AS VALUE FROM EXPRESSIONS E LEFT JOIN VARIABLES V1 ON V1.NAME = E.LEFT_OPERAND LEFT JOIN VARIABLES V2 ON V2.NAME = E.RIGHT_OPERAND

SELECT E.LEFT_OPERAND,OPERATOR,E.RIGHT_OPERAND, CASE WHEN OPERATOR='>' AND V1.VALUE>V2.VALUE THEN 'true' WHEN OPERATOR='=' AND V1.VALUE=V2.VALUE THEN 'true' WHEN OPERATOR='<' AND V1.VALUE<V2.VALUE THEN 'true' ELSE 'false' END AS VALUE FROM EXPRESSIONS E LEFT JOIN VARIABLES V1 ON V1.NAME=E.LEFT_OPERAND LEFT JOIN VARIABLES V2 ON V2.NAME=E.RIGHT_OPERAND

WITH T1 AS (SELECT V.VALUE AS LEFT_VALUE, V2.VALUE AS RIGHT_VALUE, E.* FROM EXPRESSIONS E INNER JOIN VARIABLES V ON V.NAME = E.LEFT_OPERAND INNER JOIN VARIABLES V2 ON V2.NAME = E.RIGHT_OPERAND) SELECT LEFT_OPERAND, OPERATOR, RIGHT_OPERAND, CASE WHEN OPERATOR = '>' AND LEFT_VALUE > RIGHT_VALUE THEN 'true' WHEN OPERATOR = '<' AND LEFT_VALUE < RIGHT_VALUE THEN 'true' WHEN OPERATOR = '=' AND LEFT_VALUE = RIGHT_VALUE THEN 'true' ELSE 'false' END VALUE FROM T1

SELECT E.*, (CASE WHEN (OPERATOR='>' AND L.VALUE>R.VALUE) OR (OPERATOR='=' AND L.VALUE=R.VALUE) OR (OPERATOR='<' AND L.VALUE<R.VALUE) THEN 'true' ELSE 'false' END) AS VALUE FROM EXPRESSIONS E LEFT JOIN VARIABLES L ON E.LEFT_OPERAND = L.NAME LEFT JOIN VARIABLES R ON E.RIGHT_OPERAND = R.NAME
